    rin "有一朵雲。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3714
translate zh_hant a3_emi_up_down_and_up_again_6d92def0:

    # emi "A cloud?"
    emi "雲？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3719
translate zh_hant a3_emi_up_down_and_up_again_a14f4291:

    # "Rin nods."
    "琳點了點頭。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3724
translate zh_hant a3_emi_up_down_and_up_again_3aef4a3d:

    # rin "I was watching it from my window, but it didn't stay in my window."
    rin "我剛才在我的窗口看，但它很快就飄走了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3729
translate zh_hant a3_emi_up_down_and_up_again_ddbc276a:

    # rin "So I need to use your window."
    rin "所以我要借用妳的窗戶。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3734
translate zh_hant a3_emi_up_down_and_up_again_96ee1481:

    # "Emi shifts a little, causing me to cough in order to cover up a giggle of my own."
    "笑美稍微動了一下，讓我得咳嗽來掩飾自己的竊笑。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3736
translate zh_hant a3_emi_up_down_and_up_again_6fb9aa14:

    # emi "How long do you need the window for?"
    emi "妳需要用窗戶多久？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3738
translate zh_hant a3_emi_up_down_and_up_again_a60fd612:

    # emi "We're uh."
    emi "我們、呃……"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3743
translate zh_hant a3_emi_up_down_and_up_again_ce17125c:

    # emi "Busy."
    emi "在忙。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3745
translate zh_hant a3_emi_up_down_and_up_again_22a49f30:

    # "This time I can't contain my laughter."
    "這次我忍不住笑了出來。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3750
translate zh_hant a3_emi_up_down_and_up_again_f32d8185:

    # "Rin ignores both Emi and me and peers out the window."
    "琳無視笑美和我，凝視著窗外。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3755
translate zh_hant a3_emi_up_down_and_up_again_3afa2cce:

    # "Her shoulders slump, and she looks disappointed."
    "她的肩膀垮了下來，看起來有些失望。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3757
translate zh_hant a3_emi_up_down_and_up_again_81383cfa:

    # rin "Hmm."
    rin "嗯……"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3759
translate zh_hant a3_emi_up_down_and_up_again_66bb81ef:

    # rin "It changed into something else."
    rin "它變成別的形狀了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3761
translate zh_hant a3_emi_up_down_and_up_again_320a131a:

    # rin "Disappointing."
    rin "真掃興。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3766
translate zh_hant a3_emi_up_down_and_up_again_b5eceb3e:

    # "Emi is having trouble keeping a straight face."
    "笑美很難保持嚴肅的表情。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3768
translate zh_hant a3_emi_up_down_and_up_again_2063b8fe:

    # emi "Sorry to hear that, Rin."
    emi "真遺憾，琳。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3773
translate zh_hant a3_emi_up_down_and_up_again_f132638c:

    # emi "Could we have a little privacy now, please?"
    emi "現在可以給我們一點隱私了嗎？拜託？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3789
translate zh_hant a3_emi_up_down_and_up_again_8195ae23:

    # "Rin shrugs, as if to say 'Can you?' and hooks her foot around the door, pulling it closed behind her."
    "琳聳了聳肩，像是在說「隨便你們」，然後用腳勾住房門，把它帶上。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3794
translate zh_hant a3_emi_up_down_and_up_again_0f2a173e:

    # "We both dissolve into raucous laughter, unable to deal with Rin's bizarrely timed visit any other way."
    "我們倆都爆笑出聲，無法用其他方式應對琳那時詭異的來訪。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3796
translate zh_hant a3_emi_up_down_and_up_again_d4335c11:

    # "After our laughter dies down, I look to Emi. We're both a total mess."
    "笑聲平息後，我看向笑美。我們倆都狼狽不堪。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3800
translate zh_hant a3_emi_up_down_and_up_again_b1afde36:

    # hi "Well."
    hi "嗯。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3805
translate zh_hant a3_emi_up_down_and_up_again_3de31db1:

    # "Emi raises an eyebrow."
    "笑美挑起一邊眉毛。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3807
translate zh_hant a3_emi_up_down_and_up_again_9ea2d850:

    # emi "Well?"
    emi "嗯？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3809
translate zh_hant a3_emi_up_down_and_up_again_755b0e12:

    # hi "Again?"
    hi "再來一次？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3814
translate zh_hant a3_emi_up_down_and_up_again_1b844624:

    # "Emi grins and laughs, and then she nods."
    "笑美咧嘴一笑，然後點了點頭。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3819
translate zh_hant a3_emi_up_down_and_up_again_ab45c742:

    # emi "We should probably ditch the clothes, this time."
    emi "這次我們應該先把衣服脫掉。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3837
translate zh_hant a3_emi_storage_space_b0a49044:

    # "The sunlight breaks through my window shortly before my alarm ruins the morning silence."
    "陽光灑進我的窗戶，不久後，我的鬧鐘就打破了早晨的寧靜。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3841
translate zh_hant a3_emi_storage_space_6441d2ec:

    # "I feel sore."
    "我感覺渾身痠痛。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3843
translate zh_hant a3_emi_storage_space_921e7b26:

    # "The events of the previous evening suddenly intrude upon my consciousness, and I find myself blushing."
    "昨晚發生的事突然闖入我的意識，我發現自己臉紅了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3845
translate zh_hant a3_emi_storage_space_2938d594:

    # "That was an eventful evening - and it explains perfectly the soreness in my lower back."
    "真是奇妙的一晚啊……也難怪我的腰會這麼痠疼。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3847
translate zh_hant a3_emi_storage_space_982d5491:

    # "The walk back, as I recall, had been rather tense."
    "我記得回宿舍房間的路並不好走。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3849
translate zh_hant a3_emi_storage_space_5e17ace9:

    # "My trousers having been… soiled, I had washed them off in the bathroom before going back to my room."
    "我的褲子被……弄髒了，所以我得在回房間前先去洗手間清理乾淨。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3851
translate zh_hant a3_emi_storage_space_20d625c9:

    # "But there was still a fairly obvious-looking stain on the front."
    "但前面還是有一塊相當明顯的污漬。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3853
translate zh_hant a3_emi_storage_space_aa1576ff:

    # "Fortunately for me, the only person I ran into on my way back was Kenji."
    "幸運的是，我回去的路上只遇到健二一個人。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3855
translate zh_hant a3_emi_storage_space_b2f85952:

    # "And he didn't notice a thing."
    "而他什麼都沒注意到。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3857
translate zh_hant a3_emi_storage_space_ea286f07:

    # "Well, apart from my being in the general vicinity."
    "嗯，除了我本人就在附近這件事之外。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3859
translate zh_hant a3_emi_storage_space_2d4fb63f:

    # "Of course he'd asked how the night went, and whether or not I'd learned anything of importance."
    "當然，他問了昨晚過得怎麼樣，還有我是否得知了什麼重要的事。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3861
translate zh_hant a3_emi_storage_space_096d69be:

    # "I don't even know if I opened my mouth to answer; I was too tired to care."
    "我甚至不確定自己有沒有開口回答；我累得根本不想理他。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3863
translate zh_hant a3_emi_storage_space_73e005e2:

    # "And this morning, I'll admit that I'm feeling pretty worn out."
    "而今天早上，我得承認我感覺相當疲憊。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3865
translate zh_hant a3_emi_storage_space_08f7aeea:

    # "Still, Emi had promised to meet me at the track, and I'd hate to disappoint."
    "但是，笑美跟我約好了要在操場上見面，我可不能放她鴿子。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3871
translate zh_hant a3_emi_storage_space_776a3a29:

    # "She is indeed waiting for me when I arrive."
    "我到的時候，她果然已經在等我了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3873
translate zh_hant a3_emi_storage_space_720857e0:

    # "Doing her best to look cheery, despite the fact that she's sitting in a wheelchair."
    "儘管她坐在輪椅上，還是盡力讓自己看起來很開朗。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3875
translate zh_hant a3_emi_storage_space_3a30e736:

    # "I wave to her and begin stretching."
    "我向她揮揮手，開始做伸展運動。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3877
translate zh_hant a3_emi_storage_space_54901257:

    # hi "You're early."
    hi "妳來得真早。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3882
translate zh_hant a3_emi_storage_space_f2c6c02e:

    # "Emi frowns and shakes her head."
    "笑美皺起眉頭，搖了搖頭。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3887
translate zh_hant a3_emi_storage_space_741054c6:

    # emi "Ridiculous."
    emi "胡說什麼啊。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3889
translate zh_hant a3_emi_storage_space_2301af8a:

    # emi "{b}You're{/b} late."
    emi "{b}你{/b}遲到了才對！"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3894
translate zh_hant a3_emi_storage_space_7103fe05:

    # emi "Overslept, Hisao?"
    emi "睡過頭啦，久夫？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3899
translate zh_hant a3_emi_storage_space_13f12191:

    # emi "All tuckered out?"
    emi "累壞啦？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3901
translate zh_hant a3_emi_storage_space_2e19cb18:

    # "Well, at least she seems more like her old self."
    "嗯，至少她看起來比較像平常的她了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3903
translate zh_hant a3_emi_storage_space_6fcc4204:

    # "And as expected, she doesn't seem that shy about mentioning our… previous activities."
    "而且不出所料，她提起我們之前的……活動時，似乎一點也不害羞。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3905
translate zh_hant a3_emi_storage_space_fc860247:

    # hi "Hey, you're lucky I could show up at all."
    hi "喂，我能出現妳就該偷笑了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3907
translate zh_hant a3_emi_storage_space_ae6848bd:

    # hi "All that cardiovascular activity last night, I nearly thought I'd have to see the nurse afterwards."
    hi "昨晚那麼激烈的有氧運動之後，我還以為我得去找校醫檢查一下呢。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3912
translate zh_hant a3_emi_storage_space_7c50dbf4:

    # "Emi laughs out loud, then her face suddenly becomes concerned."
    "笑美大笑出聲，然後臉上突然露出擔憂的神情。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3919
translate zh_hant a3_emi_storage_space_6921cc44:

    # emi "Hey, that's not uh…"
    emi "喂，那不是……呃……"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3921
translate zh_hant a3_emi_storage_space_5bfda2a6:

    # emi "I mean, you're not…"
    emi "我的意思是，你不是……"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3923
translate zh_hant a3_emi_storage_space_b7415c48:

    # hi "Go on, spit it out."
    hi "直接說出來吧。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3928
translate zh_hant a3_emi_storage_space_e036cc69:

    # emi "It's just that it would be hard to explain if you had an episode while we were…"
    emi "只是……如果我們在……的時候你突然發作，會很難解釋。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3930
translate zh_hant a3_emi_storage_space_04be15a3:

    # hi "Oh."
    hi "哦。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3932
translate zh_hant a3_emi_storage_space_338867b4:

    # hi "{b}Oh.{/b}"
    hi "{b}哦。{/b}"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3934
translate zh_hant a3_emi_storage_space_98cbe744:

    # "Now that she mentions it, it really is a legitimate concern."
    "她這麼一提，這確實挺嚴重的。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3936
translate zh_hant a3_emi_storage_space_0e0ad784:

    # "I certainly hadn't thought of it last night, of course - other, more pressing concerns had been at hand."
    "昨天晚上我的確沒想那麼多……當然，因為那時思緒被別的事情佔了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3938
translate zh_hant a3_emi_storage_space_0abd664d:

    # hi "Well, I don't think anything we, er, {b}do{/b} is going to be any more of a strain than these morning runs, and I handle those fine, so…"
    hi "嗯，我不認為我們，呃，{b}做{/b}的任何事會比晨跑負擔更大，而晨跑我都OK，所以……"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3943
translate zh_hant a3_emi_storage_space_71c60631:

    # "Emi considers this point."
    "笑美思考著這個論點。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3948
translate zh_hant a3_emi_storage_space_e852e6ce:

    # "A devious light appears in her eyes."
    "她眼中閃過一絲狡黠的光芒。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3952
translate zh_hant a3_emi_storage_space_c4648bf1:

    # emi "Say…"
    emi "欸……"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3954
translate zh_hant a3_emi_storage_space_34d1d59d:

    # hi "Hmm?"
    hi "嗯？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3959
translate zh_hant a3_emi_storage_space_86d34890:

    # "The light vanishes, and Emi grins ruefully at me."
    "那道光消失了，笑美可憐巴巴地看向我。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3961
translate zh_hant a3_emi_storage_space_05b9bacb:

    # "I can't help but feel vaguely suspicious."
    "我不禁感到有點可疑。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3966
translate zh_hant a3_emi_storage_space_ace437d0:

    # emi "I seem to have forgotten a pair of gloves."
    emi "我好像忘了帶手套了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3968
translate zh_hant a3_emi_storage_space_6d1f773c:

    # hi "What do you need gloves for?"
    hi "妳要手套做什麼？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3973
translate zh_hant a3_emi_storage_space_cf91a250:

    # "Emi indicates the chair upon which she is seated."
    "笑美指了指自己屁股下的輪椅。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3975
translate zh_hant a3_emi_storage_space_b60d5737:

    # emi "For this, of course!"
    emi "當然是為了這個啊！"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3980
translate zh_hant a3_emi_storage_space_71da3265:

    # emi "Sure, regular moving around is all well and good without 'em, but I want to be able to get a good workout."
    emi "當然，平常移動不用手套也沒問題，但我想好好運動一下。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3985
translate zh_hant a3_emi_storage_space_e977dc2f:

    # emi "And to get that kind of speed, you gotta have gloves if you don't want blisters."
    emi "要達到那種速度，如果你不想長水泡，就得戴手套。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3987
translate zh_hant a3_emi_storage_space_95703a7f:

    # hi "So what, are you wussing out on me then? Do I have to go it alone?"
    hi "所以呢，妳是要臨陣退縮了嗎？難道要我一個人跑？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3992
translate zh_hant a3_emi_storage_space_d22f94dc:

    # "Emi thinks for a minute - or pretends to think."
    "笑美想了一分鐘——或者說假裝在想。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3997
translate zh_hant a3_emi_storage_space_074a017f:

    # emi "Hmm… if I remember right, there's a spare pair or two in the track shed."
    emi "嗯……如果我沒記錯，操場器材室裡還有一兩副備用的。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3999
translate zh_hant a3_emi_storage_space_24f5aea1:

    # "So she does seriously want to do it, then."
    "所以她還真的想做啊。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4001
translate zh_hant a3_emi_storage_space_43394219:

    # "But in her normal school uniform? I'd have expected her to wear her gym outfit for something like this."
    "但穿著普通的學校制服？我還以為她會穿運動服做這種事。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4003
translate zh_hant a3_emi_storage_space_764f243d:

    # hi "Wait, what are they doing there?"
    hi "等等，那裡怎麼會有手套？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4008
translate zh_hant a3_emi_storage_space_b13bd09c:

    # "Emi looks askance at me."
    "笑美斜眼看著我。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4010
translate zh_hant a3_emi_storage_space_939aa7b6:

    # emi "Seriously? You can't think of why a shed full of track supplies at a school for the disabled would have racing gloves?"
    emi "你開玩笑？你真心覺得一個堆滿了殘疾運動用品的地方會沒有比賽用手套？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4012
translate zh_hant a3_emi_storage_space_dda2dfd1:

    # "Well, when she puts it that way, I suppose that makes perfect sense."
    "嗯，她這麼一說，我想這完全合理。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4014
translate zh_hant a3_emi_storage_space_619e3982:

    # hi "Hey, I'm still getting used to this place. Give me a break, huh?"
    hi "嘿，我還在適應這個地方。饒我一馬，好嗎？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4019
translate zh_hant a3_emi_storage_space_ec071e50:

    # emi "I guess I can let it slide this time."
    emi "這次我就放過你吧。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4024
translate zh_hant a3_emi_storage_space_ba2494ad:

    # emi "Now come on, I'll need your help."
    emi "好了，快來，我需要你幫忙。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4026
translate zh_hant a3_emi_storage_space_4920876b:

    # "I can't imagine what for, but then again I didn't have a clue why racing gloves would be in the shed, so I'm not willing to press the issue."
    "我想像不出要幫什麼忙，但話說回來，我也不知道為什麼器材室裡會有競速手套，所以我也不想追問。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4031
translate zh_hant a3_emi_storage_space_1f3d2374:

    # "Emi navigates her way to the shed easily enough, though I can hear her grumbling under her breath."
    "笑美輕而易舉地操控輪椅到了器材室門口，不過我能聽見她在低聲抱怨。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4033
translate zh_hant a3_emi_storage_space_4d69f9eb:

    # "It's actually kinda cute."
    "其實還挺可愛的。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4035
translate zh_hant a3_emi_storage_space_96f87b13:

    # "I hurry a little to reach the door first. Opening it will be easier for me than for her."
    "我趕緊快走幾步，先到門口。我開門會比她容易。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4047
translate zh_hant a3_emi_storage_space_f5938f8a:

    # "The door opens, and Emi starts to wheel inside, only to come to a sudden halt at the doorway."
    "門開了，笑美開始推著輪椅進去，卻在門口突然停了下來。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4049
