    "兩個人現在的處境真的是荒唐到無以復加了。忽然意識到這點的我忍不住笑了出來。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4649
translate zh_hant a3_emi_storage_space_e5057317:

    # "Emi shakes her head and begins laughing with me."
    "笑美無奈地搖搖頭，也隨我一同笑了起來。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4654
translate zh_hant a3_emi_storage_space_963cdfac:

    # emi "Hey, Hisao."
    emi "嘿，久夫。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4656
translate zh_hant a3_emi_storage_space_eb28cbfe:

    # hi "Yeah?"
    hi "嗯？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4661
translate zh_hant a3_emi_storage_space_6216f2c7:

    # emi "We're never doing this again, right?"
    emi "我們再也不玩這個了，對吧？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4663
translate zh_hant a3_emi_storage_space_aecdf82b:

    # hi "Yeah, I think my curiosity is satisfied on this one."
    hi "嗯，我想我的好奇心已經滿足了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4665
translate zh_hant a3_emi_storage_space_aa9844f1:

    # "Emi nods, satisfied."
    "笑美滿意地點了點頭。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4670
translate zh_hant a3_emi_storage_space_481d5cf5:

    # emi "Good."
    emi "很好。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4675
translate zh_hant a3_emi_storage_space_8bc82d1b:

    # emi "I think we should maybe stick to the basics, don't you?"
    emi "我想我們或許應該堅持基本款，你不覺得嗎？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4680
translate zh_hant a3_emi_storage_space_31d8bfd1:

    # emi "I mean most of this is new to me anyway."
    emi "我的意思是，反正這些體驗對我來說大部分都是新的。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4682
translate zh_hant a3_emi_storage_space_3d5f610e:

    # hi "What d'you mean, 'most?'"
    hi "妳說「大部分」是什麼意思？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4687
translate zh_hant a3_emi_storage_space_83777923:

    # "Emi grins impishly."
    "笑美頑皮地咧嘴一笑。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4692
translate zh_hant a3_emi_storage_space_6966fd3b:

    # emi "I'll never tell."
    emi "我才不告訴你呢。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4694
translate zh_hant a3_emi_storage_space_b2610fa2:

    # "An unpleasant thought strikes me."
    "一個不愉快的念頭閃過我的腦海。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4696
translate zh_hant a3_emi_storage_space_4d470ed0:

    # "Even more unpleasant is the thought of having to ask Emi about it."
    "更不愉快的是，想到必須問笑美這件事。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4698
translate zh_hant a3_emi_storage_space_3597ce2b:

    # "Still, after what we've just done, it should be a cakewalk."
    "當然，和我們剛才做完的那件事相比，這應該是小菜一碟。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4700
translate zh_hant a3_emi_storage_space_754c83f2:

    # hi "Hey, is there a sink?"
    hi "那個，附近有洗手台嗎？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4702
translate zh_hant a3_emi_storage_space_187f1b35:

    # hi "I'd kinda like to, er."
    hi "我有點想，呃。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4704
translate zh_hant a3_emi_storage_space_df86629d:

    # hi "Wash off a little."
    hi "洗一下。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4709
translate zh_hant a3_emi_storage_space_e01added:

    # "Emi's jaw drops."
    "笑美的下巴都掉了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4711
translate zh_hant a3_emi_storage_space_545bac40:

    # emi "In the {b}sink{/b}?"
    emi "在{b}洗手台{/b}？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4713
translate zh_hant a3_emi_storage_space_eabbdf8f:

    # hi "Well, there's not really anywhere else to do it, is there?"
    hi "嗯，也沒有別的地方可以洗了，不是嗎？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4715
translate zh_hant a3_emi_storage_space_f1ec7d01:

    # hi "And it uh… I want to avoid a smell."
    hi "而且，呃……我不想留下味道。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4717
translate zh_hant a3_emi_storage_space_50259fd4:

    # hi "That the nurse might notice."
    hi "那種校醫可能會注意到的味道。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4719
translate zh_hant a3_emi_storage_space_f01c246e:

    # "This is the most awkward conversation I have ever had."
    "哈哈，這是我有史以來最尷尬的對話。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4724
translate zh_hant a3_emi_storage_space_460a04ca:

    # emi "You're right."
    emi "嗯，也對。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4729
translate zh_hant a3_emi_storage_space_24991221:

    # emi "Yeah, there's uh… It's on the back wall."
    emi "嗯，有……呃……在後面的牆上。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4734
translate zh_hant a3_emi_storage_space_f6728865:

    # emi "There might be some soap, too."
    emi "可能還有肥皂。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4736
translate zh_hant a3_emi_storage_space_9d5a9627:

    # hi "Thanks."
    hi "謝了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4741
translate zh_hant a3_emi_storage_space_46cb89e2:

    # "There is in fact a little hand soap, which is better than nothing."
    "事實上確實有一小塊洗手皂，聊勝於無。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4743
translate zh_hant a3_emi_storage_space_9af7a75a:

    # "No towel, though. Guess I'll just have to drip dry."
    "不過沒有毛巾。看來我只能自然風乾了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4748
translate zh_hant a3_emi_storage_space_7d70c90c:

    # emi "All finished?"
    emi "都好了嗎？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4750
translate zh_hant a3_emi_storage_space_e91de213:

    # hi "Yeah, that'll do for now. It's not like I'm not going to take a shower after we see the nurse."
    hi "嗯，暫時這樣吧。反正看完校醫後我也會去洗澡。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4755
translate zh_hant a3_emi_storage_space_a7b1dbc7:

    # emi "Glad to hear it."
    emi "很好。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4760
translate zh_hant a3_emi_storage_space_385c5ef7:

    # emi "Now help me find my clothes. You tossed 'em somewhere."
    emi "現在幫我找我的衣服。你把它們扔到哪裡去了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4762
translate zh_hant a3_emi_storage_space_94dd802e:

    # hi "Hey, you were no better! How am I supposed to explain that hole in my shirt, hmm?"
    hi "喂，妳也沒好到哪裡去！我襯衫上的那個洞要怎麼解釋，嗯？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4767
translate zh_hant a3_emi_storage_space_867f58dd:

    # emi "Heh, sorry. I got a little excited earlier."
    emi "嘿嘿，抱歉。我剛才有點激動。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4772
translate zh_hant a3_emi_storage_space_dfbe3333:

    # "It takes some time, but finally we're both more or less clothed."
    "花了一些時間，但最後我們倆都差不多穿好衣服了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4774
translate zh_hant a3_emi_storage_space_da98bbd5:

    # "There's a frantic moment where neither of us knows where Emi's wheelchair is, but I recall it going through the door and rescue it."
    "突然發覺笑美的輪椅不見了，我們都慌了一下。最後還是我想起來，它之前滑到門外去了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4779
translate zh_hant a3_emi_storage_space_1e0122b8:

    # emi "Now be more careful going through the door this time, would you?"
    emi "嗯，這次推我過門檻時，能不能小心點？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4784
translate zh_hant a3_emi_storage_space_785ad4f0:

    # emi "Bumps are not my friend right now."
    emi "碰撞現不太適合我。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4786
translate zh_hant a3_emi_storage_space_354b4369:

    # hi "I am so sorry we tried this."
    hi "真的十分抱歉，我們居然嘗試了這種事。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4791
translate zh_hant a3_emi_storage_space_ea9ae646:

    # "Emi shrugs and grins."
    "笑美笑著聳了聳肩。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4796
translate zh_hant a3_emi_storage_space_94eea15a:

    # emi "Well, it was worth a shot, right?"
    emi "嗯，總得試試，對吧？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4801
translate zh_hant a3_emi_storage_space_afcb7576:

    # emi "And anyway, it was good exercise, right?"
    emi "而且，這也是很好的運動，對吧？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4803
translate zh_hant a3_emi_storage_space_16a626a9:

    # "Can't argue that."
    "這點無法反駁。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4808
translate zh_hant a3_emi_storage_space_41fc34fe:

    # "As we make our way up to the nurse's office, I notice that Emi keeps shifting uncomfortably in her seat."
    "在我們前往保健室的路上，我注意到笑美在座位上一直不舒服地扭來扭去。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4813
translate zh_hant a3_emi_storage_space_bb65d52f:

    # emi "God, this feels weird."
    emi "天啊，這感覺好怪。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4818
translate zh_hant a3_emi_storage_space_388250e4:

    # emi "Good thing I'm in a wheelchair, Hisao."
    emi "幸好我坐輪椅，久夫。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4820
translate zh_hant a3_emi_storage_space_e2ba6edd:

    # hi "Why's that?"
    hi "為什麼？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4825
translate zh_hant a3_emi_storage_space_08291299:

    # emi "Because, now I don't have to explain to the nurse why I'm walking funny."
    emi "因為，現在我不用向校醫解釋為什麼我走路姿勢很奇怪了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4827
translate zh_hant a3_emi_storage_space_04be15a3_1:

    # hi "Oh."
    hi "哦。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4829
translate zh_hant a3_emi_storage_space_5ca5d24f:

    # hi "We're never doing this again."
    hi "我們以後真的再也不做這個了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4835
translate zh_hant a3_emi_storage_space_02bef0d4:

    # "The nurse is at least kind enough to not comment on the marks that Emi left on my shoulders."
    "校醫至少還算好心，沒有對笑美在我肩膀上留下的痕跡發表評論。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4837
translate zh_hant a3_emi_storage_space_1f349f10:

    # "Nor does he say a word about Emi's constant shifting about in her wheelchair."
    "他也沒有對笑美在輪椅上不停地動來動去說一句話。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4839
translate zh_hant a3_emi_storage_space_62bffd36:

    # "Either he didn't notice, or he didn't want to notice."
    "也許他沒有注意到；也許他不想注意到。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4841
translate zh_hant a3_emi_storage_space_146fb3e5:

    # "All the same, I'm going to have to make sure he didn't slip cyanide into my medication for a little while."
    "不管怎樣，接下來一陣子我得小心他有沒有在我的藥裡下毒。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4843
translate zh_hant a3_emi_storage_space_3cc1908e:

    # "Just to be safe."
    "以防萬一。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4849
translate zh_hant a3_emi_storage_space_42b773dc:

    # "I shower for longer than usual, just to be sure I'm clean of our little 'experiment', and then collapse on my bed."
    "我洗澡的時間比平常久，只是為了確保我們的小「實驗」都洗乾淨了，然後筋疲力盡地倒在我的床上。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4851
translate zh_hant a3_emi_storage_space_01db6386:

    # "Class is in twenty minutes, so I can probably afford a nap."
    "二十分鐘後上課，所以我大概可以眯一下。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4867
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_36c7cc88:

    # "Knock knock."
    "「叩叩。」"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4869
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_ada81d10:

    # "Who's there?"
    "誰啊？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4873
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_36c7cc88_1:

    # "Knock knock."
    "「叩叩。」"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4875
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_9be89841:

    # "That's not how the joke goes at all."
    "喂，這不好笑。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4879
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_36c7cc88_2:

    # "Knock knock."
    "「叩叩。」"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4881
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_d7b9ac77:

    # "I already said who's there!"
    "我已經問過誰在那裡了！"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4883
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_6a728f92:

    # "More importantly, what time is it?"
    "更重要的是，現在幾點了？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4885
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_4234adba:

    # "Even more importantly, what day…?"
    "更更重要的是，今天是星期幾……？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4890
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_ede673b2:

    # "I am suddenly catapulted into wakefulness by both the fact that the knocking still hasn't stopped and the fact that it's noon."
    "敲門聲還沒停，而且現在已經是中午了，這兩件事讓我瞬間驚醒。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4892
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_d07f306f:

    # "On a school day."
    "……等等，今天學校有課的吧。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4894
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_eccf38d0:

    # "Now fully awake, I can remember why I was napping."
    "現在完全清醒了，我想起了我為什麼在打盹。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4896
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_d39389b3:

    # "Better not give that excuse to Mutou."
    "還是別把真實原因告訴武藤老師吧。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4898
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_88064df2:

    # "'Sorry I wasn't in class, I was experimenting sexually with my girlfriend and it tired me out.'"
    "「抱歉我沒去上課，我跟我女朋友在進行性方面的實驗，結果太累了。」"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4900
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_fa3995a1:

    # "Yeah, that'll go over well."
    "呵呵，老師一定會欣然接受的。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4904
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_aa237850:

    # "I wonder how long this knocking is going to continue."
    "不知道這敲門聲還要持續多久。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4906
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_cc01b477:

    # "Guess I ought to answer the door."
    "看來我該去開門了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4914
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_4cfef8a6:

    # "I'm strangely unsurprised to see Kenji on the other side."
    "門外的人是健二；唉，意料之中。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4916
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_ad894c14:

    # "Though it appears that Kenji is surprised to see me."
    "不過健二看到我倒是很驚訝。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4918
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_3ce83633:

    # ke "What the hell are you doing here, man?"
    ke "臥槽，你在這幹嘛，哥們？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4922
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_23b79223:

    # hi "Well, I was sleeping."
    hi "嗯，我剛在睡覺。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4927
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_26b6cce6:

    # "Kenji nods in understanding."
    "健二理解地點了點頭。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4932
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_e7904e52:

    # ke "Knocked out. I see."
    ke "被打暈了，是吧？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4937
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_ce8aa452:

    # ke "I told you to be careful around that Ibarazaki chick, man."
    ke "早告訴過你了，在那個茨崎娘們身邊要小心，哥們。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4939
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_9c411c39:

    # ke "This is the sort of thing that happens when you aren't cautious."
    ke "一不小心，就會遇到這種事的。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4941
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_cafdb3d1:

    # "He makes an attempt to look at the back of my head."
    "他試圖湊到我的腦後，為我檢查傷勢。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4946
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_61eee3ff:

    # ke "Did she hit you with something?"
    ke "她是把你擊暈的？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4948
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_6a5f0793:

    # ke "Or was it a drug?"
    ke "還是用藥？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4950
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_b982ff7c:

    # hi "Stop trying to touch me."
    hi "離我遠點，別碰我。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4954
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_a6824861:

    # "Kenji produces a flashlight and shines it in my eyes."
    "健二拿出一支手電筒照我的眼睛。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4956
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_16bf989e:

    # ke "You got a concussion?"
    ke "你有腦震盪嗎？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4958
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_6be5434a:

    # hi "I wasn't knocked out!"
    hi "我不是被打暈的！"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4963
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_b2f7bed3:

    # ke "Maybe you just don't remember."
    ke "也許你只是喪失記憶了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4965
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_5bb0d2f0:

    # "This conversation isn't going anywhere."
    "這談話真他喵的毫無意義。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4967
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_75e88ba6:

    # hi "No, I just had a tiring morning and fell asleep."
    hi "不，我只是早上太累了就睡著了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4972
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_e5fdb6b1:

    # ke "Whatever, man."
    ke "隨便你啦，哥們。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4974
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_4f8a51f3:

    # ke "If you want to be in denial about this, I guess I can't stop you."
    ke "如果你想逃避現實，我想我也阻止不了你。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4976
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_1c9944e2:

    # ke "But you gotta watch out for that girl, man. She's not safe."
    ke "但是你要小心那娘們啊，哥們。她很危險。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4978
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_81d99227:

    # hi "What?"
    hi "什麼？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4983
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_a66b43d7:

    # ke "She's not safe to be around; she's one of their most sinister agents!"
    ke "在她身邊很危險；她是她們最陰險的特務之一！"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4985
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_e433b7d6:

    # ke "If you're not careful, there's no telling what could happen!"
    ke "不小心點的話，天知道會發生什麼！"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4987
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_25e2e6a2:

    # ke "She's brought down stronger men than you, you know!"
    ke "要知道，她毀滅過多少比你強的男人！"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4989
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_26c8c721:

    # hi "What the hell are you talking about?"
    hi "你他喵的到底在講什麼？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4991
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_c787088b:

    # hi "She's not an agent of anything, and she didn't knock me out, okay?"
    hi "她不是特務，她也沒有把我擊暈，懂？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4993
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_2a046ede:

    # hi "I also highly doubt that she's brought down anyone at all."
    hi "另外，我也對她「毀滅」過任何人的說法高度懷疑。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4998
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_1201f791:

    # "Kenji looks almost offended."
    "健二看起來幾乎像是受到了傷害。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5000
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_eeb65699:

    # "I have no idea why."
    "真是無可理喻。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5002
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_7b58ace4:

    # ke "You don't believe me?"
    ke "你不相信我？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5004
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_6be38258:

    # ke "That's cold, man. Real cold."
    ke "真是無情啊，哥們。寒風刺骨般的無情啊"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5006
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_b6ad9978:

    # ke "I'm just trying to look out for you. That's what friends do, you know."
    ke "我只是想幫你，提醒你而已。要知道，我們可是朋友啊。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5008
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_283cb9db:

    # "We're friends? I had no idea."
    "我們是朋友？我完全不知道。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5010
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_bbd88d33:

    # "Then again, I wonder if Kenji knows what being a friend even entails."
    "不過話說回來；我想，也許健二根本就不知道「朋友」是怎樣一個概念。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5012
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_659590c7:

    # "I feel something like pity for him, standing there before me."
    "看著站在我面前的他，我對他產生了一種類似同情的感覺。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5014
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_fe7d9328:

    # "Maybe he does think he's looking out for me."
    "說不定他真的以為是在幫我呢。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5016
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_ee322606:

    # hi "I know, I know."
    hi "我懂，我懂。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5018
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_deb9f489:

    # hi "I'm sorry about that. Thanks for the warning."
    hi "剛才很抱歉。謝謝你的警告。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5020
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_43f9c875:

    # "I hold out my hand as a sign of peace."
    "為了表示友好，我伸出了手。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5025
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_e10ffa66:

    # "Kenji shakes it gingerly, like my hand could possibly be on fire."
    "健二小心翼翼地握了握，好像我的手可能著火了一樣。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5027
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_fba1f204:

    # "There's an awkward silence for a few seconds before Kenji remembers that he's still shaking my hand."
    "兩個人在沉默中度過了幾秒，直到健二發覺他還握著我的手，才開口打破了尷尬。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5032
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_92102e59:

    # ke "Anyway, I need a favor."
    ke "總之，我需要你幫個忙。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5034
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_35f070c9:

    # hi "What kind of favor? I'm out of money…"
    hi "什麼忙？我沒錢了……"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5036
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_e61017de:

    # ke "No you aren't. You've got money kept in your desk drawer under a black notebook. For emergencies."
    ke "不，你有。你把錢放在書桌抽屜裡一本黑色筆記本下面。用來應急的。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5038
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_53261128:

    # hi "Did you ransack my room?"
    hi "你他喵的搜過我房間？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5043
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_42f44f98:

    # ke "That's not important."
    ke "這不是重點。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5045
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_00d80355:

    # ke "I don't need money, anyway."
    ke "再說，我也不需要錢。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5047
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_acf8d06a:

    # "He adopts a very serious tone."
    "他的語氣變得非常嚴肅。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5052
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_9459ec53:

    # ke "I'm about to undertake a major op."
    ke "我即將執行一項重大行動。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5054
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_ca66085d:

    # ke "It'll blow the whole conspiracy wide open if I'm right."
    ke "如果成功的話，會讓整個陰謀水落石出。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5056
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_e6838a23:

    # ke "But it's dangerous, so I need you to do something for me in case I don't come back."
    ke "但這很危險，所以萬一我回不來，我需要你為我做件事。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5058
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_0bd44345:

    # hi "Uh, sure man. Anything."
    hi "呃，當然了，哥們。什麼都行。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5060
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_d32c5b53:

    # "What the hell is he planning on doing?"
    "他到底打算做什麼？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5062
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_970e2f0e:

    # "Should I be telling someone about this?"
    "我該不該告訴誰這件事？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5067
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_f2cd404c:

    # ke "If I go missing, wait three days and then mail my journal off to the newspapers."
    ke "如果我失蹤了，等三天，然後把我的日記寄給報社。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5069
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_e5cdf549:

    # ke "It's hidden in my room under a false bottom in one of my desk drawers."
    ke "我把它藏在我房間裡一個抽屜裡的祕密夾層裡。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5071
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_2811e377:

    # hi "How do I get into your room? I don't have a key."
    hi "我要怎麼進你房間？我沒有鑰匙。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5076
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_4ccd4ebb:

    # "Kenji looks at me like I'm crazy."
    "健二看著我，好像我瘋了一樣。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5078
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_d91ba613:

    # ke "So pick the lock. You know how to do that, right?"
    ke "那就把鎖撬開。鎖你總該會撬吧？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5080
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_05a8d001:

    # ke "It's an important skill to learn at a young age!"
    ke "這是從小就應該學習的重要技能！"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5082
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_6f64cd6b:

    # hi "Uh, yeah, of course I know how."
    hi "呃，對啊，當然了，我當然會。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5084
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_7849b4a2:

    # hi "I'll be sure to uh, do that for you. If you go missing."
    hi "我一定會，呃，記得幫你的。如果你失蹤的話。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5086
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_33f7a431:

    # "I don't think I want to read Kenji's journal."
    "天啊，我不想讀健二的日記啊。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5088
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_0c5fc582:

    # "Either way, Kenji seems pretty happy that I've agreed to do this thing for him."
    "不管怎樣，我答應幫健二這個忙，他看起來挺開心的。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5093
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_41c37203:

    # ke "Great, man. Great."
    ke "好極了，哥們。好極了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5095
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_043e8c7d:

    # ke "I'll see you around, I got stuff to do."
    ke "那麼回頭見了，我還有事要做。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5106
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_f5f58461:

    # "And he's gone, dashing down the hallway."
    "他匆匆地消失在走廊的盡頭。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5108
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_5129771b:

    # "He made it seem so final."
    "他搞得好像是最後一面。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5110
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_a3ce0ca6:

    # "I hope I don't have to carry out his final wishes."
    "希望我不用去執行他的遺願。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5117
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_a9bb434d:

    # "Shaking my head, I close my door and walk back to my bed."
    "我搖搖頭，關上門，走回床邊。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5119
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_d6f6fa03:

    # "Guess I should go to class, if only to catch the last half of the day."
    "也許我該去上課；雖然說今天已經過去一半了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5121
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_6ef2a43c:

    # "But I've come this far without going to class today…"
    "但是今天即使沒上學，也發生了這麼多事……"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5123
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_ef13de15:

    # "And I did want to read more of that Hawking book Mutou lent me…"
    "而且我還想多看一點武藤老師借我的那本霍金的書……"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5125
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_2fa20249:

    # "I'm sure he'll understand."
    "我相信他會理解的。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5131
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_36c7cc88_3:

    # "Knock knock."
    "「叩叩」。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5133
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_5954ec69:

    # "This time the noise jerks my attention away from my book."
    "這次的聲音把我的注意力從書本上拉了回來。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5135
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_9b3d9f1c:

    # "An experience not unlike being woken up."
    "那種感覺跟被吵醒沒什麼兩樣。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5137
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_02adfd54:

    # hi "Who's there?"
    hi "誰啊？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5139
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_3a1b4370:

    # emi "Me! Aren't you glad?"
    emi "是我！開心嗎？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5143
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_fb28bbcd:

    # "The voice is muffled through the door, but unmistakably Emi's."
    "門外的聲音有些模糊，但毫無疑問是笑美。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5151
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_c12af0b0:

    # "I hop up and open the door, smiling broadly."
    "情不自禁地笑著，我一躍而起，打開了門。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5153
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_2afd0b37:

    # hi "Hey! Nice to see you again!"
    hi "嗨！很高興又見到妳！"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5158
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_5afc69b2:

    # "Emi grins back, staring up at me from her wheelchair."
    "笑美也回以微笑，從輪椅上抬頭看著我。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5163
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_52476555:

    # emi "Yeah, you would have seen me earlier, but the damned elevator wasn't working."
    emi "對啊，你本來可以早點看到我的，但是那該死的電梯壞了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5168
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_3cb51e6b:

    # emi "Had to wait for them to fix it."
    emi "我只好等他們修好才上來。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5173
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_762f0477:

    # emi "You'd think they could keep it in better order, but nooo…"
    emi "區區一臺電梯，你還會以為他們能好好維護呢。但是他們就是不~~"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5175
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_765be802:

    # "I chuckle a bit at her vexed expression and invite her in."
    "看著她惱火的表情，我輕笑了一下，請她進來。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5180
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_ff046799:

    # "She wheels in easily, and with my help she hops onto my bed."
    "她輕鬆地滑進來，在我的幫助下，她跳上了我的床。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5191
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_8ca22c00:

    # emi "There. Much more comfortable than that stupid chair."
    emi "嘿咻。這比那該死的輪椅舒服多了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5196
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_2c2bba33:

    # "A sigh of contentment hangs in the air, and for a minute we both just stare at one another."
    "一種溫馨的氣氛飄散在空氣中，兩個人都默默地注視著對方。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5198
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_143b7f78:

    # "It's at that point that I notice the circles under Emi's eyes."
    "就在那時，我注意到了笑美眼下的黑眼圈。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5200
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_b3d6e3d1:

    # "They're not that dark, but they definitely weren't there before."
    "還並不是太嚴重。但我敢發誓，她前幾天還沒有眼圈的。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5202
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_e4824304:

    # "Before I can ask about them, Emi fixes me with a mischievous stare."
    "在我能開口詢問之前，笑美用頑皮的眼神盯住了我。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5207
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_f31b9ee3:

    # emi "So, I couldn't help but notice you weren't at lunch today."
    emi "那麼，你今天沒來一起吃午飯耶。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5209
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_88c1e9e5:

    # emi "In fact, I don't think I saw you at all."
    emi "事實上，我好像根本沒看到你。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5214
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_d656a3c4:

    # emi "What happened, hmmm?"
    emi "發生什麼事了，嗯？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5216
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_c17f12a3:

    # hi "Fell asleep."
    hi "睡著了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5218
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_8cd2ec60:

    # hi "I actually didn't wake up until lunch, and only then because Kenji woke me up."
    hi "我其實一直睡到午餐時間，而且還是因為健二把我吵醒才醒的。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5223
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_61c4be7f:

    # emi "What had you so tired, hmm?"
    emi "是什麼讓你這麼累啊，嗯？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5225
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_9e892c89:

    # hi "Strenuous workout this morning. Slightly uncomfortable, too."
    hi "今天早上做了劇烈運動。而且還有點不舒服。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5230
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_62d822a9:

    # "Emi coughs, a half-laughing, half-embarrassed noise."
    "笑美半是尷尬、半是好笑地咳嗽了一聲。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5235
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_2eac2033:

    # emi "Remind me not to do that again."
    emi "提醒我別再做那件事了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5237
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_ddb2d867:

    # hi "No problem. It wasn't exactly great for me either, to be honest."
    hi "沒問題。老實說，對我來說也不是什麼偉大的體驗。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5239
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_8c7eefda:

    # hi "We'll just avoid that from now on."
    hi "我們以後就避免那樣做吧。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5241
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_d8d91260:

    # hi "Are you, er, still sore?"
    hi "妳，呃，還會痛嗎？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5246
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_66521350:

    # "Emi stares at me in disbelief."
    "笑美難以置信地瞪著我。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5248
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_d09bb0b6:

    # hi "What? It's a legitimate question!"
    hi "幹嘛？這是個很正當的問題！"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5253
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_0b980092:

    # emi "Of all the questions I never thought I'd be asked, that's one of them."
    emi "在我從來沒有想過會需要回答的問題中，這絕對是其中一個。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5255
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_69b357c6:

    # hi "Well, I didn't ever expect to have to ask it, so we're even."
    hi "嗯，我也從沒想過會需要問這個問題，所以我們扯平了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5260
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_6365c18a:

    # "Emi laughs at this."
    "笑美撲哧地笑了出來。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5262
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_535b2535:

    # emi "I guess so, huh?"
    emi "我想也是。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5269
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_372466a1:

    # emi "Well, since you asked, yes. I'm still a little sore."
    emi "那個，既然你問到了：是的，我還有點疼。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5274
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_d01669d1:

    # emi "We're never doing that again."
    emi "我們再也不做那件事了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5276
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_d6300218:

    # hi "No arguments from here."
    hi "雙手贊成。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5278
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_b45e1213:

    # "A yawn escapes her, and I raise an eyebrow."
    "她打了一個哈欠，我挑起了一邊眉毛。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5280
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_af2a3f6c:

    # hi "Tired?"
    hi "累了？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5285
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_d7c791f1:

    # "Emi nods sleepily."
    "笑美睡眼惺忪地點了點頭。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5292
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_3cc0a177:

    # emi "Haven't slept well."
    emi "沒睡好。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5294
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_483a5bc0:

    # "Not sleeping well?"
    "睡得不好？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5296
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_2912deeb:

    # "I can tell that she didn't mean to tell me this either, because she gives a little start like she's just been caught lying and hastens to add,"
    "看得出來，她是一不小心說漏嘴，才會告訴我這件事的。像一個謊言被戳破的孩子般，笑美的身體顫了一下，並急忙開口補救。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5301
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_4b858ba0:

    # emi "It's not a big deal, though."
    emi "不過沒什麼事的。真的。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5303
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_4ce06568:

    # hi "What's the trouble?"
    hi "有什麼麻煩嗎？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5308
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_9fae0703:

    # "Emi shrugs and refuses to elaborate."
    "笑美聳聳肩，拒絕多談。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5310
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_a2e9ae3c:

    # hi "Stressed over exams?"
    hi "考試壓力大？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5312
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_4a26b5b9:

    # "Another shrug, but after a pause, Emi nods hesitantly."
    "又一次聳肩。不過，稍微停頓後，笑美還是猶豫地點了點頭。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5317
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_61e60cb6:

    # emi "Er, yeah, I guess."
    emi "啊嗯，是吧，差不多吧。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5319
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_ddb807b2:

    # emi "Actually, that's why I stopped by."
    emi "其實，這就是我來找你的原因。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5321
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_81c42474:

    # "She begins to look more and more miserable."
    "她逐漸地變得有些坐立不安。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5323
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_63402bd2:

    # "Not so you'd notice, of course; but her eyes are on her lap, she's fidgeting and her voice is quiet."
    "不是十分明顯；但她還是目光下垂，手指不安分地扭來扭去，說話聲音也變得越來越細。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5328
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_0fdd2087:

    # emi "We uh, we need to stop hanging out so much."
    emi "我們……嗯……我們還是不要這麼經常在一起了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5330
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_f423f75f:

    # hi "Huh? Why?"
    hi "蛤？為什麼？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5332
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_3ac317a1:

    # "Emi takes a deep breath, like she's been practicing this."
    "彷彿早就為這一刻排練過似的，笑美深深地吸了一口氣。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5337
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_c04cf982:

    # emi "Because you're too much fun to be around."
    emi "因為跟你在一起太好玩了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5339
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_085fe9f4:

    # emi "And I can't concentrate when you're near me."
    emi "而且你在我身邊的時候，我沒辦法專心。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5341
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_2866f355:

    # emi "With exams coming up soon, I just… can't have that distraction."
    emi "考試快到了，我只是……不能有那樣的分心。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5346
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_6acc5e78:

    # emi "Otherwise my grades will be pretty lousy, I'm afraid."
    emi "不然恐怕我的成績會很差。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5348
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_d932e811:

    # hi "I could help you study…"
    hi "我能幫妳複習啊……"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5353
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_fe056e26:

    # "She smiles at me, clearly unhappy with the situation."
    "她對我微笑，顯然對這種情況很不滿意。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5355
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_200947a5:

    # emi "I'd love it if you could, but we wouldn't actually study, would we?"
    emi "如果你可以的話我會很開心，但我們根本不會真的唸書，對吧？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5360
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_c50afd93:

    # emi "I mean even now, I'm trying to have a conversation with you but I kinda just want to, uh…"
    emi "我的意思是，即使是現在，我試著要跟你說話，但我有點只想，呃……"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5365
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_bc2aee1d:

    # emi "Not converse."
    emi "做些談話以外的事。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5367
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_9a287fc4:

    # hi "Ah."
    hi "啊。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5369
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_b9a0d704:

    # hi "Overwhelmed by my rugged manliness. I understand."
    hi "被我粗獷的男子氣概征服了。我懂。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5374
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_d7e48670:

    # "That earns me a grin, at least."
    "至少這句話讓她笑了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5376
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_4a72a162:

    # "Emi shakes her head."
    "笑美搖了搖頭。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5381
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_1fde6504:

    # emi "Idiot. You're full of yourself."
    emi "笨蛋。你太自以為是了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5383
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_09d262ec:

    # hi "Well, I am pretty irresistible."
    hi "嗯，我確實是蠻有魅力的。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5388
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_65476528:

    # emi "Er, more or less. I guess."
    emi "呃，或多或少吧。我想。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5393
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_4b32e83a:

    # emi "So that's the situation, Hisao."
    emi "所以情況就是這樣，久夫。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5395
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_e517647a:

    # emi "I have too much fun around you, and if I'm going to go into exams prepared, I need to be alone."
    emi "我在你身邊玩得太開心了，如果我要準備好考試，我需要專心一個人。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5397
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_0cfbb39a:

    # hi "Hey, that's okay."
    hi "嘿，沒關係的。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5399
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_f09927ca:

    # "It really seems to have been bothering her."
    "這件事似乎真的困擾了她很久。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5401
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_f5e3fbdc:

    # "Besides, it's only a couple of weeks. And we'll still see each other in the mornings, and at lunch."
    "而且，也才幾個星期而已。我們早上和午餐時間還是會見面。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5403
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_80c83375:

    # hi "We can just hang out at school, no problem."
    hi "我們可以在學校見面，沒問題的。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5405
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_cc43877f:

    # hi "And after exams, we'll go on a date to celebrate their being over, okay?"
    hi "考完試後，我們去約會慶祝考試結束，好嗎？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5410
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_b549c8bc:

    # "Emi grins, pleased by this proposal."
    "笑美笑了，對這個提議很滿意。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5415
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_aa4a78da:

    # emi "Yeah, sure! That sounds great!"
    emi "好啊好啊！聽起來好極了！"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5420
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_1bd82e76:

    # "As if to signal the end of the conversation, she leans in and kisses me."
    "彷彿表示談話已經結束一般，她側過身來吻住了我。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5422
translate zh_hant a3_emi_afterschool_plans_a82e9d35:

    # "The rest of the night is not spent worrying about exams."
    "晚上剩餘的時間被我們用在了完全無關考試的事上。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5441
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_76b2fe88:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5444
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_f2a49980:

    # n "{vspace=60}It's weird how easily Emi and I can keep from seeing one another after class now."
    n "{vspace=60}笑美和我放學後完全不見面了；過程容易的令人驚訝。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5446
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_636fc52d:

    # n "Actually, I'd venture to say that it's vaguely disturbing."
    n "其實，我敢說這有點令人不安。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5448
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_43ccfa9d:

    # n "As easily as we'd come together, we seem to have split apart without much trouble."
    n "我們在一起得有多容易，分開似乎也沒什麼困難。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5450
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_ca6eb49f:

    # n "Well, I guess that's not exactly true."
    n "嗯，我想這也不完全正確。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5452
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_beb36f14:

    # n "We'd both been pretty bummed after that last night together."
    n "在那最後一晚之後，我們倆都挺沮喪的。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5454
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_f3dd8d65:

    # n "And we get to see each other every morning for our runs (and just our runs, I might add)."
    n "而且我們每天早上跑步時都能見到對方（我得補充一下，就只是跑步）。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5456
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_44631619:

    # n "Lunch, too. I especially enjoy lunchtime with her."
    n "午餐也是。我特別享受和她一起的午餐時光。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5458
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_04175a13:

    # n "We have plenty of time to talk about everything outside of school, whereas the morning runs have become increasingly businesslike."
    n "我們有很多時間可以聊學校以外的一切。而早上的跑步則變得越來越公事公辦。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5460
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_8ff1eb06:

    # n "I think it's because Emi wants to make up for our foolery in the storage shed."
    n "我想這是因為笑美想彌補我們在儲藏室裡的胡鬧。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5462
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_e43927dd:

    # n "But no matter how much we joke at lunch, I can't help feeling a little worried about her."
    n "但不管午餐時我們怎麼開玩笑，我還是忍不住有點擔心她。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5464
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_7028754c:

    # nvl clear
    # n "{vspace=60}She seems distracted more often, and I've caught her fidgeting nervously more than once."
    nvl clear
    n "{vspace=60}她似乎更常分心，而且我不止一次看到她緊張地坐立不安。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5468
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_21e57098:

    # n "Never figured her to be someone who cared that deeply about exams, but they certainly seem to be taking their toll."
    n "從沒想過她是那種那麼在乎考試的人，但考試顯然對她造成了很大的影響。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5470
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_1ec8a8c5:

    # n "Even though they haven't even started."
    n "考試甚至還沒開始呢。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5472
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_88dd447d:

    # n "This is just the run up, the deep breath before the plunge."
    n "這只是前奏，是縱身一躍前的深呼吸。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5474
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_2b8f23d5:

    # n "Tomorrow, the real trials begin."
    n "明天，真正的考驗才要開始。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5476
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_1e06ee1b:

    # n "Or the real exams, anyway."
    n "或者說，真正的考試。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5478
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_2bc1484a:

    # n "As for me, I actually don't feel that worried about exams at all."
    n "至於我，我其實一點也不擔心考試。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5480
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_d470d14a:

    # n "I'm not sure why. I mean, they're pretty important; my scores here will determine my odds of getting into a good university."
    n "我不確定為什麼。我的意思是，考試很重要；這裡的成績會決定我進入好大學的機率。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5482
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_da414c8e:

    # n "Hell, if I'm too cavalier now, it could spell doom for my academic career."
    n "該死，如果我現在太掉以輕心，可能會毀了我的學業生涯。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5484
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_426d9b82:

    # n "But going into them, I feel confident that I'll come out the other side okay."
    n "但面對考試，我很有信心能安然度過。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5486
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_52ac224e:

    # nvl clear
    # n "{vspace=180}Mutou thinks I've got the science examination locked up, at any rate."
    nvl clear
    n "{vspace=180}無論如何，武藤老師認為我的理科考試穩操勝券。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5490
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_28dba056:

    # n "Or as he says, 'The last thing that should give you trouble is my exam, Hisao. It's way beneath your talents.'"
    n "或者像他說的：「最不該讓你頭痛的就是我的考試了，久夫。這對你的才華來說太小兒科了。」"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5492
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_6e4f3a96:

    # n "Then again, it is Mutou who's telling me this."
    n "告訴我這話的人是武藤老師本人。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5494
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_d241477e:

    # n "His praise of me carries the veiled implication that anything less than perfect from me would be a disappointment, which has actually caused me to fret more than I should about the exam."
    n "他對我的讚美帶有隱含的意味，即任何不完美的表現都會令人失望，這反而讓我對考試感到比應有的更焦慮。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5498
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_76b2fe88_1:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5504
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_a35437b4:

    # "It's for that reason that I find myself in the library after class, poring over the textbook."
    "就是因為這個原因，我放學後發現自己待在圖書館，埋首於教科書中。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5506
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_3a204e22:

    # "Pretty simple things to look over; some formulas of velocity, a few bits about friction…"
    "要複習的東西很簡單；一些速度公式，一些關於摩擦力的知識……"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5508
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_3805f385:

    # "A walk in the park compared to my dreaded English exam. Never was good with languages…"
    "跟我那可怕的英文考試相比，簡直是小菜一碟。我從來就不擅長語言……"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5510
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_c0fd781b:

    # "As I flip through my notes one more time, my mind begins to wander."
    "當我再翻一遍筆記時，我的思緒開始飄走了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5514
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_76b2fe88_2:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5517
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_df418b1a:

    # n "{vspace=90}After these exams are over, things should get easier."
    n "{vspace=90}這些考試結束後，事情應該會變得輕鬆些。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5519
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_1be20381:

    # n "Soon we'll be graduated."
    n "很快我們就要畢業了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5521
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_e8a77bfb:

    # n "Then off to college, hopefully."
    n "然後，希望是上大學。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5523
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_d90a3788:

    # n "I remember my abortive attempt to find out what Emi plans to do after high school."
    n "我記得我曾試圖問笑美高中畢業後打算做什麼，但那次嘗試無疾而終。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5525
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_626806c8:

    # n "Hmm, she avoided the subject pretty deftly, as I recall."
    n "嗯，我記得她很巧妙地避開了這個話題。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5527
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_b4f0ef20:

    # n "Heck, it seems that just about every time I push too hard, she dances around the subject."
    n "可惡，似乎每次我逼得太緊，她就會繞開話題。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5529
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_96e3b897:

    # n "Or distracts me through… other means."
    n "或者用……其他方式分散我的注意力。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5531
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_969369b7:

    # n "Like a few days ago at lunch, when Rin wasn't around…"
    n "就像幾天前午餐，琳不在的時候……"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5533
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_ceccb846:

    # n "Heh."
    n "哼。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5537
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_76b2fe88_3:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5545
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_7aee21ca:

    # yu "I've done it!"
    yu "我成功了！"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5547
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_0bb148b9:

    # "I'm startled from my reverie by Yuuko's triumphant shout."
    "優子勝利的吶喊把我從白日夢中驚醒。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5549
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_7f83092f:

    # hi "Gah!"
    hi "啊！"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5554
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_7c7fb8cf:

    # "Yuuko seems mortified at my sudden starting."
    "優子似乎對我突然的驚嚇感到非常羞愧。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5558
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_95b82f20:

    # yu "Oh my god!"
    yu "天啊！"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5563
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_8512ab5f:

    # yu "I'm so sorry! I just got - and I really wasn't - and it's just that—"
    yu "我真的很抱歉！我只是——而且我真的不是——只是因為——"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5565
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_1d403a84:

    # "As she stutters, I move to quickly calm her down before she gets too agitated."
    "在她結結巴巴的時候，我趕緊安撫她，免得她太激動。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5567
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_fde50182:

    # hi "Woah, hey."
    hi "喂喂，好了好了~~"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5569
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_ef6489dd:

    # "My words seem ineffective."
    "我的話似乎沒什麼效果。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5571
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_4fa4aa29:

    # "Yuuko continues to work herself into a complete frenzy."
    "優子繼續把自己搞得越來越抓狂。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5576
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_000d9e95:

    # yu "And it's a library and I shouldn't be—"
    yu "而且這裡是圖書館，我不應該——"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5578
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_54e8b8db:

    # hi "Easy there, just calm down."
    hi "放輕鬆，冷靜點。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5583
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_7b5fe30f:

    # yu "And really I'm setting a bad example, and now I'll get fired because I can't do anything right—"
    yu "而且我真的做了壞榜樣，現在我要被開除了，因為我什麼都做不好——"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5585
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_5fa12704:

    # hi "YUUKO!" with vpunch
    hi "優子！" with vpunch

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5590
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_71063af3:

    # "Shouting seems to work, though I draw the ire of several other students studying in the library."
    "大喊似乎奏效了，雖然我引來了圖書館裡其他幾位學生的怒視。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5592
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_b1268190:

    # "Yuuko snaps to attention, like a soldier who's just heard the captain bark an order."
    "優子立刻回過神來，像個剛聽到長官下令的士兵。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5597
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_e72bf16c:

    # yu "Sorry! Sorry!"
    yu "對不起！對不起！"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5599
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_114ecea2:

    # hi "Calm down, it's okay."
    hi "冷靜下來，沒關係的。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5601
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_3583b8af:

    # hi "You just startled me a little, and that's only because I was daydreaming instead of studying."
    hi "妳只是嚇到我一下下，而且那也只是因為我沒在唸書，在做白日夢。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5603
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_e3066a05:

    # hi "So really, you got me back on task."
    hi "所以說，妳其實是把我拉回正軌。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5605
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_dc7e7500:

    # "This is a complete lie. But it seems to work."
    "這完全是謊話。但似乎奏效了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5610
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_aa68b654:

    # "Yuuko takes a deep breath and seems to calm down a little."
    "優子深深吸了一口氣，似乎冷靜了一點。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5612
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_2a58dd25:

    # "Though she keeps shifting around with a nervous energy that seems awfully familiar."
    "雖然她還是一直動來動去，那股緊張的能量感覺非常熟悉。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5614
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_e278e49b:

    # hi "So, what's got you so excited anyway?"
    hi "所以，到底是什麼事讓妳這麼興奮？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5619
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_1139c67d:

    # yu "The Yamaku Cat Burglar!"
    yu "山久小偷！"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5621
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_f7fb134a:

    # "To her credit, Yuuko manages to convey her intense excitement in a whisper."
    "值得稱讚的是，優子成功地用耳語傳達了她強烈的興奮感。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5626
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_64195ecb:

    # yu "I think I know who it is!"
    yu "我想我知道是誰了！"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5631
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_719a51ad:

    # yu "I got an anonymous tip as to their identity!"
    yu "我收到關於他們身分的匿名線報！"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5633
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_0068f50b:

    # yu "So I did some spying, and I think the tipster was right!"
    yu "所以我做了一些偵查，我想線人是對的！"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5635
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_83f0759c:

    # hi "Oh really? And who was this er, burglar?"
    hi "哦，真的嗎？那這個，呃，小偷是誰？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5640
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_f04e2f41:

    # "Yuuko shuts her mouth, shaking her head decisively."
    "優子閉上嘴，果斷地搖了搖頭。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5642
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_b6edcf9f:

    # yu "Nope, I can't tell you that."
    yu "不行，我不能告訴你。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5644
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_f5743db9:

    # hi "Why not?"
    hi "為什麼不行？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5649
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_193bfe8a:

    # yu "It's between me and the burglar."
    yu "這是我和小偷之間的事。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5651
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_6833e965:

    # yu "I can't risk you warning him that I'm on to his game."
    yu "我不能冒險讓你警告他我已經盯上他了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5653
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_8b548f1c:

    # yu "He could tip his hand early and blow town."
    yu "他可能會提早亮出底牌然後逃之夭夭。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5655
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_09bcf6ed:

    # yu "Then I'm left with no perp."
    yu "那我就抓不到犯人了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5657
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_494554ab:

    # "When did Yuuko start talking like a hard-boiled detective?"
    "優子什麼時候開始說話像個冷硬派偵探了？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5659
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_1606b007:

    # hi "I wouldn't warn them! Why would I care?"
    hi "我不會告訴他們的！我幹嘛要幫他們？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5664
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_9f0c3187:

    # yu "If you've got to ask that question, then you don't need to know."
    yu "如果你需要問這個問題，那你就不需要知道。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5666
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_66b73137:

    # hi "That doesn't make any sense, but okay."
    hi "這邏輯一點也講不通。不過好吧，聽妳的。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5668
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_8fcd60ec:

    # hi "Congratulations, I guess?"
    hi "那麼……恭喜妳了？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5673
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_28f039b7:

    # yu "Thanks!"
    yu "謝謝！"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5678
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_fd01a005:

    # yu "Uh, what for?"
    yu "呃，為了什麼？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5680
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_b439eb57:

    # hi "The uh, cat burglar thing?"
    hi "那個，呃，小偷的事？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5685
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_25fcd8d5:

    # "Yuuko nods and smiles appreciatively."
    "優子點了點頭，露出了感激的微笑。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5687
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_579f1941:

    # yu "So! Studying for exams?"
    yu "所以！在準備考試嗎？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5689
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_e34a6e33:

    # hi "Well, that was the plan. I'm not having much luck, though."
    hi "嗯，本來是這麼打算的。不過不太順利就是了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5694
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_b37e3231:

    # yu "Really? Is it because you can't find a book?"
    yu "真的嗎？是因為找不到書嗎？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5699
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_efb6ad7c:

    # yu "I'm really sorry!"
    yu "真的很抱歉！"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5701
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_cbd5d088:

    # yu "I've been meaning to clean the shelves up for weeks now, but I keep getting distracted!"
    yu "我一直想清理清理書架，想了好幾個禮拜了，但是總是有別的事分心！"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5703
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_29a28e99:

    # yu "I'm so sorry!"
    yu "真的很抱歉！"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5705
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_3a888913:

    # hi "Woah, wait."
    hi "咳咳，等下等下。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5707
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_753cbe5b:

    # hi "It's not that. I've got my book right here."
    hi "不是因為這個，我的書就在這裡。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5709
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_ea3a6b6b:

    # "To illustrate the point and hopefully calm Yuuko down, I show her the textbook in front of me."
    "為了證明我的話，也希望讓優子冷靜下來，我指給她看我面前的教科書。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5711
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_1a7f2ddc:

    # hi "My mind just keeps wandering, is all."
    hi "我只是思緒一直飄走，就這樣。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5716
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_54cf7126:

    # yu "Is it because of the noise in here?"
    yu "是因為這裡太吵嗎？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5718
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_0059ba82:

    # yu "I'm trying to be more strict about the noise levels, but I can't bring myself to yell at people…"
    yu "我試著對音量更嚴格一點，但我總是沒辦法斥責別人……"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5723
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_a67aa252:

    # yu "I mean aren't their lives hard enough without me throwing my authority around?"
    yu "我的意思是，大家的生活已經夠辛苦了，我還要擺架子嗎？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5725
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_ac1ee313:

    # hi "No, it's not the noise level either, I promise."
    hi "不，也不是音量的問題，我保證。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5727
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_4207cbca:

    # hi "I'm just…"
    hi "我只是……"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5729
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_9bc8906a:

    # "Hell, I don't know."
    "天啊，我也不知道。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5731
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_2ce4f7cf:

    # "Worried about Emi."
    "擔心笑美。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5733
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_2573b2f3:

    # "Worried about us."
    "擔心我們。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5735
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_40d81964:

    # "Worried about what happens after we graduate."
    "擔心我們畢業後會發生什麼事。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5737
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_bf32ea38:

    # hi "Emi's been kind of weird, lately."
    hi "笑美最近有點怪。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5742
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_f5c41094:

    # yu "What do you mean?"
    yu "什麼意思？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5744
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_7cab714b:

    # hi "Well, you know how we're dating now?"
    hi "嗯，妳知道我們現在在交往吧？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5746
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_601cbb40:

    # hi "I just don't know that we're actually, you know…"
    hi "我只是不知道我們是不是真的是……"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5748
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_e4639368:

    # hi "A couple. Or at least I don't know that we're beyond friends."
    hi "一對情侶。或者至少我不知道我們是否超越了普通朋友的關係。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5750
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_bfb9a6e0:

    # "Though friends normally don't do the sort of things we do."
    "雖然朋友通常不會做我們做的那種事。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5752
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_92404989:

    # "Physically we're a couple."
    "身體上我們是一對。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5754
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_4295f12a:

    # "Coupling, at least."
    "最少也算是在交配。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5756
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_9ef9c98a:

    # hi "It's like every time I try to find out more about her, or about what she wants to do with her life, she dodges the question."
    hi "就好像每次我試圖更了解她，或了解她想用她的人生做什麼，她都會迴避問題。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5758
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_8ca42a8b:

    # hi "Like the other day, I was talking to her at lunch about some schools I've been looking into."
    hi "就像前幾天，我在午餐時跟她聊一些我一直在考慮的大學。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5760
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_e6e5ea0f:

    # hi "And I asked her, 'Have you looked into any schools lately?'"
    hi "然後我問她，「妳最近有看什麼學校嗎？」"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5762
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_70ac39bc:

    # hi "She shrugs in response, says no, and when I ask why not, she says that she doesn't think that far ahead."
    hi "她聳聳肩回答說沒有，當我問為什麼不，她說她不會想那麼遠。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5764
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_d39a6706:

    # hi "I asked why she had that policy, and she…"
    hi "我問她為什麼，她就……"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5766
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_0101a1b4:

    # "I suddenly realize what I'm about to start describing, and wisely decide to clam up."
    "我突然意識到我將要描述什麼，明智地決定閉嘴。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5771
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_0ba172a7:

    # yu "She what?"
    yu "她就怎麼？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5773
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_e0aa7d41:

    # hi "Er, she changed the subject."
    hi "她就……呃……轉，轉移話題了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5775
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_71698b49:

    # hi "Wouldn't talk about it."
    hi "不肯談。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5780
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_bf79791b:

    # yu "Maybe it's an uncomfortable subject for her?"
    yu "也許這對她來說是個不舒服的話題？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5782
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_fc5662f3:

    # yu "Or she just doesn't think it needs explaining."
    yu "或者她只是覺得不需要解釋。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5784
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_bdce1d25:

    # hi "Yeah, but it's not just that."
    hi "也許吧。但是不僅是這件事。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5786
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_31387a47:

    # hi "Every time I try to find out what's been bothering her, she changes the subject too."
    hi "每次我問她，為什麼總是悶悶不樂，她也立刻撇開話題。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5788
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_976bf7c4:

    # hi "It's like she likes being with me, but not getting close to me."
    hi "感覺就好像她喜歡和我在一起，但是卻不想和我走得太近。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5790
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_87f799df:

    # "Now that I've said it out loud, I feel worse."
    "大聲把我的煩惱說出來後，我感覺更糟了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5792
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_38413fb9:

    # "Yuuko digests this bit of information."
    "優子消化著這些資訊。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5797
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_6d919ae0:

    # yu "You know, it seems to me that you're more serious about this than she is."
    yu "你知道嗎，在我看來，你比她更認真看待這段關係。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5799
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_b20819ef:

    # "I can almost feel my stomach twist into a knot."
    "我幾乎可以感覺到我的胃揪成一團。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5801
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_7fe46979:

    # "She's right."
    "她說得沒錯。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5803
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_99710323:

    # "That's exactly what it seems like."
    "看起來的確就是這麼回事。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5805
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_b6ae381e:

    # hi "But is that really what's going on? I mean…"
    hi "但真的是這樣嗎？我的意思是……"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5810
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_d1f76d3a:

    # yu "Sorry! I'm just talking nonsense!"
    yu "對不起！我只是在胡說八道！"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5812
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_ece7ebc6:

    # yu "You shouldn't take my advice, you barely know me!"
    yu "你不必聽我的建議的！話說我們幾乎都不認識！"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5817
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_48cc8d6d:

    # yu "I'm just the librarian, and I'm single so you can imagine I can't know what I'm talking about!"
    yu "我只是個圖書館員，而且還是單身，所以可想而知我根本不知道自己在說什麼！"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5819
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_7cac9890:

    # hi "No, I think…"
    hi "不，我覺得……"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5821
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_6e5f3d72:

    # hi "I think you have a point."
    hi "我覺得妳說得有道理。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5823
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_29c34b9a:

    # "As much as it hurts to even consider it."
    "儘管光是想到這點就讓我很心痛。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5825
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_874d25c0:

    # "Yuuko seems to try desperately to find a way to soften the blow somewhat."
    "優子似乎拼命想找個方法來緩和一下衝擊。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5830
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_de545e4c:

    # yu "Er, look."
    yu "呃，你看。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5835
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_1da49682:

    # yu "I'm probably wrong, but if you want to be sure of how obviously wrong I am, maybe you should just talk to her?"
    yu "我很可能說錯了，但如果你想確定我錯得有多離譜，或許你應該直接跟她談談？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5837
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_5fae837c:

    # yu "Get some time alone and just ask about it."
    yu "找個獨處的時間，直接問清楚。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5842
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_01876a59:

    # yu "And don't let her change the subject, either!"
    yu "還有，不要讓她再轉移話題了！"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5844
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_1b58ae30:

    # hi "Yeah, maybe I should do that."
    hi "是啊，也許我們的確該談談了……"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5848
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_76b2fe88_4:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5851
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_61469bf9:

    # n "{vspace=60}Or maybe I should just enjoy what I have."
    n "{vspace=60}或者，我也許該享受我現在所擁有的。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5853
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_c92f6b15:

    # n "We have fun hanging out, after all."
    n "畢竟，我們在一起的時候很開心。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5855
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_b7147e22:

    # n "And the runs are nice, and the other activities are nice, and talking to her is nice…"
    n "晨跑很棒，其他的活動也很棒，跟她聊天也很棒……"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5857
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_9a6c2349:

    # n "Do I really need to get closer to her? What I've got right now is pretty good."
    n "我真的需要跟她更親近嗎？我現在擁有的已經很好了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5859
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_670c1d33:

    # n "But that's silly."
    n "但這太傻了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5861
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_3f0b68c5:

    # n "I want to get closer to her."
    n "我想要跟她更親近。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5863
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_2e5c0678:

    # n "I want to be able to help her out with whatever is bothering her."
    n "我希望能幫她解決任何困擾她的事。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5865
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_b1a9147f:

    # n "But… maybe I should wait until after exams are over."
    n "但是……或許我該等到考試結束後再說。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5867
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_b1809124:

    # n "Maybe she'll brighten up once the stress has passed."
    n "也許等壓力過去後，她就會開心起來了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5869
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_8df9807f:

    # n "If she does, then I don't need to worry about it any more."
    n "如果真是這樣，那我就不用再擔心了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5871
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_bfacfc7f:

    # n "But if she doesn't, well."
    n "但如果不是，那……"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5873
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_cff700c2:

    # n "I'll cross that bridge when I come to it."
    n "船到橋頭自然直吧。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5878
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_76b2fe88_5:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5882
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_41c71065:

    # "I thank Yuuko for her advice and head back to my room."
    "我向優子道謝，謝謝她的建議，然後走回我的房間。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5887
translate zh_hant a3_emi_detached_f8db0e02:

    # "Maybe I'll be able to concentrate more on my studies in there."
    "也許在那裡我能更專心念書。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5902
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_91d73f2a:

    # "I leave the room after finishing my final exam and breathe a sigh of relief."
    "我考完最後一科後走出教室，鬆了一口氣。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5904
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_a877c3f5:

    # "As I'd hoped, the exams weren't so bad. I managed to breeze through just about everything but the English final."
    "如我所願，考試沒那麼糟。除了英文期末考之外，其他科目我都輕鬆過關。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5906
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_0e34496b:

    # "And even that was acceptable."
    "就連英文也還算過得去。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5908
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_aeed5931:

    # "I wonder how Emi did."
    "不知道笑美考得怎麼樣。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5910
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_c58840b4:

    # "Even more so, how she's doing; she looked terrible at lunch today."
    "更重要的是，她人怎麼樣了；今天午餐時她看起來糟透了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5912
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_ceb44181:

    # "I mean, she was pretty happy to be out of her wheelchair, but she was so exhausted."
    "我是說，她雖然很高興能擺脫輪椅，但她看起來非常疲憊。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5914
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_3843f87d:

    # "Something's been wearing her down, and I'm starting to really doubt that it was just the exams."
    "有什麼事一直在消耗她的精力，我開始真的懷疑不只是考試的關係。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5916
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_5d59690a:

    # "Should I confront her about this, though?"
    "但我應該和她直接攤牌嗎？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5918
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_0d1f7f0b:

    # "My musing is interrupted by a tap on the shoulder."
    "我的思緒被肩膀上輕輕一拍給打斷了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5923
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_d5244a83:

    # mu "Hey, Hisao."
    mu "嗨，久夫。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5927
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_825276c1:

    # mu "Got a minute?" nointeract
    mu "有空嗎？" nointeract

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5942
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_efbe6d0b:

    # "The question keeps spinning in my head even after I made my way back to my room."
    "即便我回到了房間以後，笑美的問題也還在我的腦海裡轉來轉去。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5946
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_76b2fe88:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5949
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_b21cdf59:

    # n "{vspace=60}What if she gets angry about it?"
    n "{vspace=60}如果她生氣了該怎麼辦？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5951
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_08e3627d:

    # n "Besides, what if it's nothing?"
    n "再說，如果原本就真的沒什麼大不了的呢？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5953
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_c90f8151:

    # n "If I go in and refuse to leave until she tells me what's wrong or something, won't that come off as clingy?"
    n "如果我進去，然後非要她告訴我出了什麼問題才肯走，這樣會不會顯得很黏人？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5955
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_ca5d3732:

    # n "I don't want to start a fight or anything over something like this."
    n "我不想為了這種事和她吵起來……"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5957
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_5e0de14f:

    # n "Maybe I should just drop the matter and see how she is tomorrow before I do anything."
    n "也許我應該先放下這件事，明天看看她的情況再說。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5959
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_63e7a279:

    # n "Would it be so bad to just let it go?"
    n "就這樣放著不管，會很糟嗎？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5961
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_0fc4bb43:

    # n "It's not like we don't enjoy each other's company."
    n "我們又不是不喜歡和對方在一起。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5963
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_4237b9fa:

    # n "But odd as it sounds, I really want to… help her."
    n "但聽起來可能很奇怪，我真的很想……幫她。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5965
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_0b384bef:

    # n "I don't even know what with or if there's anything at all she needs help for."
    n "雖然我連究竟該幫她些什麼，甚至連她到底需不需要幫助都不知道。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5967
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_7eb56115:

    # n "But I want to."
    n "但是我還是想幫她。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5975
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_76b2fe88_1:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5978
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_a0726d67:

    # "Suddenly, a knock at my door rouses me."
    "一陣突如其來的敲門聲打斷了我的沉思。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5986
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_1bfc4d53:

    # "I open it to see Kenji."
    "打開房門，赫然是健二站在門外。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5988
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_50684ad3:

    # hi "Oh, it's you."
    hi "喔，是你啊。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5995
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_9e51229e:

    # ke "It's me? That's it?"
    ke "是我啊？就這樣？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5997
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_90026d11:

    # ke "If you had any idea what I'd been through, what I'd done, you'd be happier to see me, dude."
    ke "哥們，如果你對我最近的經歷有一點點了解的話，你見到我可就會雀躍不已了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:5999
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_7c6f5b18:

    # ke "I mean that was some epic, you-may-never-see-me-again shit."
    ke "我是說，這可他媽的是一段生死離別的超傳奇故事啊。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6001
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_db853ef5:

    # ke "And here you're just acting like I went down to the store for some milk."
    ke "你的反應卻好像我只是去便利商店買了瓶牛奶一樣。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6006
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_48397c65:

    # ke "You're a cold man, Hisao. I really respect that."
    ke "你是一個多麼無情的人啊，久夫。不過，我尊敬你這一點。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6008
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_583054b1:

    # hi "Uh, thanks, I guess."
    hi "呃，謝了，我想。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6013
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_c132f93e:

    # ke "It's smart to play it safe, you know. Don't show any emotion."
    ke "要知道，穩中求勝才是明智的選擇。別流露出任何感情。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6015
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_f33ccb69:

    # ke "Keep your cards close to your chest."
    ke "把你要打的牌藏在胸前，不要暴露。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6017
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_3f91078b:

    # ke "Unless it's time to show your cards, or you have bad cards."
    ke "除非時機成熟……或者你的牌真的很爛。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6019
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_a2e9f1f4:

    # ke "Then you should fold or collect your winnings."
    ke "如果這樣，你就該放棄賭局，或者領取彩金了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6024
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_8f27f6fb:

    # ke "Do you understand?"
    ke "明白了嗎？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6026
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_244eb6f2:

    # hi "Yeah, that makes perfect sense."
    hi "是的，明白了。簡直透徹，令人毫無疑問。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6028
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_27ff780c:

    # hi "I take it the uh, mission went well?"
    hi "看來你的……這個……「任務」，一定很順利嘍？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6033
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_4e52ba6f:

    # ke "Woah, awfully nosy of you, isn't it?"
    ke "哇，你還真愛管閒事，不是嗎？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6035
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_3e0718d7:

    # ke "You can't just go saying things like that! Things are at a delicate stage!"
    ke "你不能就這樣四處招搖、胡亂說話！事件現在處於一種極為敏感的狀態！"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6037
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_2d30bc05:

    # ke "One wrong move, and BAM! The invasion succeeds!"
    ke "只要走錯一步，砰！侵略就成功了！"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6039
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_362f278d:

    # hi "I thought you were going to blow the conspiracy wide open?"
    hi "我以為你要把整個陰謀揭穿？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6041
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_2eef5f15:

    # ke "It's bigger than I thought; I need to update my charts."
    ke "這比我想的還大；我需要更新我的圖表。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6043
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_fc51f627:

    # ke "And probably change some of the puppets around."
    ke "可能還得換掉一些棋子。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6048
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_2835dbd7:

    # ke "You wanna help? I've got some whiskey from… somewhere."
    ke "想幫忙嗎？我弄到了一些威士忌……從某個地方。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6050
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_a164d139:

    # ke "You can fill me in on everything your investigation has turned up."
    ke "你可以告訴我你的調查有什麼新發現。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6052
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_8c7a5d43:

    # hi "Er, better not. I'm uh… supposed to meet her today."
    hi "呃，還是不要了。我……呃……今天應該要跟她見面。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6054
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_e406a14c:

    # hi "Gotta go do that. Can't raise suspicion."
    hi "得去赴約了。不能引起懷疑。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6059
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_35b2da72:

    # "Kenji nods in approval."
    "健二贊同地點了點頭。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6061
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_2fd398fc:

    # ke "Still keeping it close to the chest, eh? Okay man, I respect that."
    ke "還是把底牌藏得緊緊的，嗯？好吧，老兄，我尊重你。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6063
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_3cf1fe27:

    # ke "Good luck."
    ke "祝你好運。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6065
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_e7cbd408:

    # hi "Er, thanks."
    hi "呃，謝了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6072
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_94ae6363:

    # "I'm just going to pretend, for the sake of my own sanity, that he's wishing me luck in talking to Emi."
    "為了我自己的理智著想，我就當作他是在祝我跟笑美談話順利吧。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6074
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_1bea8b3b:

    # "And if I squint, that whole card analogy he was talking about works here."
    "如果我瞇起眼睛看，他剛才說的那些撲克牌比喻在這裡也說得通。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6076
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_1d5ba85a:

    # "Time to lay it all on the table."
    "是時候攤牌了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6078
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_e443c147:

    # "Or see if I can't get Emi to do so, rather."
    "或者更確切地說，是看看我能不能讓笑美攤牌。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6080
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_3a7b8281:

    # "With a sense of something approaching purpose, I head for Emi's room."
    "帶著一股近乎決心的感覺，我朝笑美的房間走去。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6087
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_21cdcb82:

    # "I hop up the stairs leading to her room and knock on her door."
    "我跳上通往她房間的樓梯，敲了敲她的門。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6089
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_1b2ea5c9:

    # emi "W-who's there?"
    emi "是……是誰？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6093
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_6674838b:

    # "Huh. That's odd. Her voice sounds a little choked."
    "嗯。真奇怪。她的聲音聽起來有點哽咽。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6095
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_7c5e53aa:

    # hi "Hey, it's me. Thought I'd stop by."
    hi "嘿，是我。想說過來看看。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6097
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_a18df911:

    # emi "Hisao?"
    emi "久夫？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6099
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_30885fe1:

    # emi "Come on in!"
    emi "進來吧！"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6101
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_eb2b44a1:

    # "I reach down to open the door, only to find that it's locked."
    "我伸手去開門，卻發現門是鎖著的。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6103
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_db01ceec:

    # "More and more curious."
    "越來越奇怪了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6105
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_87a016c7:

    # hi "Er, your door's locked."
    hi "呃，妳的門鎖著。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6107
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_cf923ff4:

    # emi "Oh yeah, sorry. Gimme a minute."
    emi "喔對，抱歉。等我一下。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6117
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_6e6512f9:

    # "In a few minutes, Emi opens the door, grinning."
    "幾分鐘後，笑美開了門，臉上掛著笑容。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6119
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_fa6ee035:

    # emi "Sorry, I had to put my legs on. I was napping."
    emi "抱歉，我得把義肢穿上。我剛才在睡午覺。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6121
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_d4cb5a92:

    # "Despite her grin, there's something definitely off."
    "儘管她臉上掛著大大的微笑，但是能感覺到，這裡絕對有什麼不對勁。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6123
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_f3b99e1c:

    # "Emi's eyes are slightly red, and it looks like she's been crying."
    "笑美的眼睛有點紅，看起來像是哭過。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6125
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_b94eb406:

    # hi "Hey, no problem."
    hi "嘿，沒關係。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6127
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_4ec637ea:

    # hi "Er, are you okay?"
    hi "呃，妳還好嗎？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6132
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_6fcca0dd:

    # emi "Huh? Yeah, I'm fine!"
    emi "蛤？對啊，我很好！"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6134
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_37b54c1d:

    # hi "It's just that you look like you've been crying…"
    hi "只是……妳看起來好像哭過……"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6136
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_5001e1e8:

    # "Oh yeah, Hisao. You're off to a great start on this one."
    "喔耶，久夫。你這次的開場白還真是漂亮啊。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6141
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_6d60086f:

    # emi "What? Nah, I'm fine. I'm just happy to see you."
    emi "什麼？沒有啦，我很好。我只是很高興見到你。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6146
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_c07acf33:

    # "She punctuates this with a long kiss that continues as the door slams shut behind us."
    "她用一個長吻來強調這句話，吻一直持續到門在我們身後砰地一聲關上。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6148
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_babf11c2:

    # "I know what she wants to do now, and I'm also painfully aware of how badly I want to do it too, but…"
    "我知道她現在想做什麼，我也痛苦地意識到自己有多想這麼做，但是……"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6154
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_fa5d8b9c:

    # "I break the kiss with a wrench of self control that nearly kills me."
    "我用幾乎要了我命的自制力中斷了這個吻。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6156
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_7d88a5e6:

    # hi "Hey, wait."
    hi "嘿，等等。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6161
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_83f77a6c:

    # "Emi's eyes crinkle in confusion."
    "笑美困惑地瞇起了眼睛。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6163
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_0460472f:

    # emi "Huh? Wait for what?"
    emi "蛤？等什麼？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6165
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_3215796f:

    # hi "We need to talk."
    hi "我們需要談談。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6170
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_1b987d43:

    # emi "Isn't that supposed to be my line?"
    emi "這不是應該是我的台詞嗎？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6175
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_07e9c53f:

    # emi "And never a good thing to say?"
    emi "而且通常都不是什麼好事吧？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6177
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_e3d0fbe3:

    # "She's got a point."
    "她說得有道理。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6179
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_50a2844b:

    # "It's usually the lead-in to a breakup."
    "這通常是分手的開場白。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6181
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_852a4040:

    # "Or the prelude to a fight."
    "或是吵架的前奏。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6183
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_41b11874:

    # hi "Maybe it can be a good thing this time."
    hi "也許這次會是件好事。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6185
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_2a023032:

    # hi "Er, that's the hope, anyway."
    hi "呃，無論如何，希望是這樣。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6190
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_276006e5:

    # emi "Uh… huh."
    emi "呃……嗯。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6195
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_42f584dc:

    # emi "Can we at least get onto the bed? It's my first day back on these things, and I'm still readjusting."
    emi "我們至少可以到床上去嗎？這是我第一天重新穿上它們，我還在重新適應。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6200
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_b5bf4e88:

    # emi "Plus the nurse said I should try to be on them less often, since running puts such a strain on them."
    emi "而且校醫說我應該盡量少穿，因為跑步對它們的耗損很大。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6202
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_eb14c7e5:

    # hi "Can't argue with that."
    hi "這點沒話說。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6204
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_3680e7d4:

    # "It's a trap, we both know it, and we both don't care."
    "這是個陷阱，我們都知道，但我們也都不在乎。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6206
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_45d61ce0:

    # "Then again, it's awfully hard to get angry while in bed with the object of your affections, so maybe there's that motivation too."
    "話說回來，和你心儀的對象躺在床上時，很難生氣，所以或許這也是個動機。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6223
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_efa1a123:

    # "I set Emi's legs by the bedside and sit down next to her, throwing an arm around her shoulders."
    "我把笑美的義肢放在床邊，然後坐在她身旁，用一隻手臂環住她的肩膀。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6225
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_1e659f38:

    # "In silence, we just enjoy being able to be in this position again for a few minutes."
    "我們沉默地享受著能再次這樣相處的幾分鐘。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6227
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_a3a07c07:

    # "Then, of course, I need to ruin it by opening my mouth."
    "然後，當然，我一開口就得毀了這氣氛。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6229
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_e444771a:

    # hi "Look, I know that… that you've been having kind of a rough time of it lately."
    hi "聽著，我知道……妳最近過得不太順遂。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6231
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_338352e6:

    # hi "And I want to help you out."
    hi "而我想要幫妳。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6233
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_3b2c2fac:

    # hi "I thought it was just exams getting to you, but now I come to your room and you've been crying, and that kills me."
    hi "我本來以為只是考試讓妳心煩，但現在我來到妳房間，發現妳一直在哭，這讓我心都碎了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6235
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_bc057710:

    # hi "But I can't do anything if you won't talk to me about it."
    hi "但如果妳不跟我說，我就什麼也做不了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6240
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_a30dda66:

    # emi "I told you, I'm fine."
    emi "我跟你說過了，我很好。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6242
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_5a89b29d:

    # hi "No, you aren't. It's obvious something's eating at you."
    hi "不，妳不好。很明顯有什麼事在困擾妳。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6244
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_0ca9089e:

    # hi "You can tell me, you know."
    hi "妳可以告訴我的，妳知道的。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6246
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_ac8ff505:

    # "There's the slightest increase in tension in Emi's voice."
    "笑美的聲音裡緊張感微微增加了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6251
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_c3f3ca2c:

    # emi "Why is my saying I'm fine not good enough?"
    emi "為什麼我說我很好還不夠？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6256
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_bfc364a6:

    # emi "You're concerned, I get that. That's cool."
    emi "你關心我，我明白。我很高興。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6258
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_1738645f:

    # emi "But I'm fine, and it's nothing that you need to worry about."
    emi "但是我沒事。沒什麼需要你擔心的事。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6260
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_62cdef89:

    # hi "Not sleeping and spacing out more than Rin doesn't strike me as 'being fine.'"
    hi "睡不著，還比琳更容易放空，在我看來可不叫「很好」。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6262
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_daf90821:

    # hi "I just… I want to help."
    hi "我只是……我想幫助妳。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6264
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_ca7d08c9:

    # emi "Uh-huh."
    emi "哼。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6266
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_587e0aaf:

    # hi "Yeah, I don't like seeing you like this."
    hi "是啊，我不喜歡看到妳這樣。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6268
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_b258ffa4:

    # hi "I want you to be happy, you know?"
    hi "我希望妳能開心，妳知道嗎？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6273
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_d1e6bc6d:

    # "I get the feeling that came out wrong, because Emi fixes me with an icy stare."
    "我感覺好像說錯話了，因為笑美用冰冷的眼神瞪著我。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6275
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_bfc2937a:

    # emi "So you want to fix me, Hisao?"
    emi "所以你想「拯救」我，久夫？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6277
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_b2fd68f2:

    # "She's definitely getting angry now."
    "她現在肯定生氣了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6282
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_35f2bc49:

    # emi "Wanna swoop in on your white charger and save the day?"
    emi "想騎著你的白馬衝進來拯救世界嗎？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6284
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_a3f6fe3c:

    # emi "Stop the nightmares, the phantom limb pains?"
    emi "驅逐我的惡夢，讓我忘記失去的雙腿？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6289
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_2fd0ee5c:

    # emi "Restore what's lost?"
    emi "還原我所失去的一切？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6294
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_da1e47c9:

    # "Her voice catches in her throat, and the tears start to flow."
    "她的聲音變得哽咽，眼淚從眼裡滿溢而出。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6296
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_0be76db0:

    # emi "Well you {b}can't{/b}."
    emi "告訴你，你{b}辦不到{/b}。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6301
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_f2ceaf19:

    # emi "Nobody can."
    emi "沒有人辦得到。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6303
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_35ffa19c:

    # emi "Nobody will."
    emi "永遠不會有人辦到。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6305
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_5fe78a0f:

    # "I'm so stunned by her sudden verbal assault that I remain quiet."
    "我被她突如其來的言語攻擊嚇得說不出話來。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6307
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_ab29cb41:

    # "Neither of us says anything for a while."
    "時間緩緩地流逝，我們兩個人都一言不發。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6309
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_8550c3b7:

    # "I'm surprised that Emi tightens her grip on me rather than pushing me away."
    "出乎我的意料，笑美不但沒有鬆開我的手，反而把它握得更緊了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6311
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_911c4cef:

    # "After a deep breath, she starts talking again."
    "笑美深深地吸了口氣，才再次開口說話。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6316
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_14b95518:

    # emi "Look, I'm sorry."
    emi "聽著，我很抱歉。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6321
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_ef915004:

    # emi "I just… there's these nightmares."
    emi "我只是……會做那些惡夢。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6323
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_db193b68:

    # emi "About the accident."
    emi "關於那場車禍。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6325
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_9679ab82:

    # "Ah. The accident. I should've known."
    "啊。那場車禍。我早該想到的。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6327
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_6e9231ab:

    # "It took her legs, after all, but it never comes up, of course."
    "畢竟，那場意外奪走了她的雙腿，但這件事從來沒被提起過。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6332
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_47fbb747:

    # emi "And I usually deal with them fine, because I can run."
    emi "一般來說，我還可以面對。因為我能跑步。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6334
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_5d5bee32:

    # emi "Running clears my head like nothing else."
    emi "跑步能清空我的腦袋，沒有什麼比得上。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6336
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_d155a896:

    # emi "I don't have to worry about anything while I'm running."
    emi "跑步的時候，我什麼都不用擔心。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6338
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_5ede7011:

    # emi "I just concentrate on breathing, on the rhythm of things."
    emi "我只專注在呼吸上，專注在節奏上。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6340
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_5a508f33:

    # emi "It's easier that way. Life's easier that way."
    emi "那樣真的更簡單。那樣真的一切都更簡單。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6345
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_2136b01f:

    # emi "Just keep moving forwards, you know? Nothing else matters, just getting around the next curve."
    emi "就是一直往前跑，你懂嗎？其他都不重要，只要跑過下一個彎道就好。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6347
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_7d99e273:

    # emi "And then it's the next curve, and the next, and the next, until I can't go any more, or think any more, or do anything but slow down and walk until I catch my breath again."
    emi "然後是下一個彎道，再下一個，再下一個，直到我再也跑不動、再也無法思考，除了慢下來走路，直到我再次喘過氣來，什麼也做不了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6349
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_5ddeddc8:

    # emi "After something like that, nothing else matters."
    emi "在那樣的經歷之後，其他一切都不重要了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6354
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_16cafc96:

    # emi "But I've been stuck in that goddamned wheelchair for too long. So, no outlet."
    emi "但我被困在那該死的輪椅上太久了。所以，沒有出口。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6359
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_5fa5cf56:

    # emi "Today it just kinda boiled over a little."
    emi "有些受夠了，所以才發脾氣了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6361
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_a433bca5:

    # hi "You could have talked to me about it, you know."
    hi "妳可以跟我說的，妳知道嗎。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6363
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_bb2db1af:

    # hi "You didn't have to go it alone."
    hi "你沒有必要一個人承受的啊。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6368
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_489e3dd7:

    # "Emi smiles sadly, like she's trying to explain to a child that all fire burns."
    "笑美悲傷地笑了，像是在跟一個孩子解釋火是會燙傷人的一樣。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6370
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_d964f6e0:

    # emi "Yeah, I did. And I do."
    emi "有必要的。以前如此，現在依然如此。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6372
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_6cd78fe5:

    # hi "But why?"
    hi "但是為什麼？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6374
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_56eee97c:

    # hi "Why do you have to keep going through this alone?"
    hi "為什麼妳非得一個人經歷這些？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6376
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_b9be715d:

    # hi "Why can't you just trust me enough to let me help you?"
    hi "為什麼妳就不能信任我，讓我幫妳？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6378
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_2eae27be:

    # "That smile again."
    "又是那個笑容。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6386
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_91d2efa2:

    # "Emi leans in and kisses me on my cheek, an almost motherly gesture."
    "笑美湊了過來，以一種接近慈母般的姿態 輕輕地吻過我的臉龐。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6388
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_b3c2080b:

    # "She leaves her mouth close to my ear, as she confesses this one thing to me."
    "她把嘴唇靠近我的耳朵，向我坦白了這件事。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6393
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_f9b5557a:

    # emi "Because, Hisao."
    emi "因為，久夫。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6395
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_019f2170:

    # emi "I've already had everything I knew ripped away from me once."
    emi "我曾經被奪走過我所知的一切。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6400
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_48aa3e70:

    # emi "I don't know what I'd do if it happened again."
    emi "我不知道如果再發生一次，我會怎麼辦。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6402
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_b26ab468:

    # "She pauses, as if uncertain as to whether or not she should continue."
    "她停頓了一下，好像不確定該不該繼續說下去。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6404
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_d23ce8fc:

    # "I can feel a violent churning in my gut."
    "我能感覺到我的胃在劇烈地翻攪。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6406
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_f9359455:

    # "She continues."
    "她繼續說。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6411
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_8e9ff78d:

    # emi "So I can't rely on you."
    emi "所以我不能依賴你。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6413
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_ae72a59b:

    # emi "Or the nurse."
    emi "或校醫。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6415
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_86804948:

    # emi "Or anyone else."
    emi "或任何人。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6420
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_0f4b7d0c:

    # emi "Just me."
    emi "只能靠我自己。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6422
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_483a95f1:

    # emi "That's how it's got to be."
    emi "只能是這樣。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6424
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_66eecf9f:

    # "Having delivered this short speech, she looks down and covers her mouth with the back of her hand."
    "說完這段簡短的話，她低下頭，用手背摀住嘴。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6426
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_acd0adf6:

    # "The conversation is clearly over. I search for something to say, but can't think of anything."
    "對話顯然結束了。我試圖找些話說，但什麼也想不出來。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6428
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_d77f5a13:

    # hi "I…"
    hi "我……"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6430
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_c57b6772:

    # hi "Maybe I should go, for now."
    hi "或許我現在該走了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6432
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_7442de69:

    # hi "I've got… stuff."
    hi "我還有……事。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6434
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_55bd749a:

    # "Emi doesn't even look up."
    "笑美連頭都沒抬。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6436
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_eedea99d:

    # "She sounds tired, or relieved."
    "她的聲音聽起來很疲憊，或者說是鬆了口氣。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6438
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_69d3937b:

    # "I can't tell which."
    "我分不出來是哪一種。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6440
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_741b568e:

    # emi "Okay, Hisao."
    emi "好的，久夫。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6442
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_526db814:

    # emi "Go take care of that stuff."
    emi "去忙你的事吧。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6444
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_405c2c99:

    # emi "I'll see you tomorrow."
    emi "明天見。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6454
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_890765e3:

    # "I get off the bed and head for the door, pausing at the doorway."
    "我從床上起身，走向門口，在門口停了下來。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6456
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_b95097d5:

    # hi "Hey, Emi…"
    hi "那個，笑美……"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6461
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_95e3e68e:

    # emi "Yeah?"
    emi "嗯？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6465
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_76b2fe88_2:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6468
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_43a34339:

    # n "{vspace=60}A thousand things I want to say."
    n "{vspace=60}我有千言萬語想說。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6470
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_9c4e8e4f:

    # n "I'm too mixed up to say any of them, though."
    n "但我思緒太亂，一句也說不出口。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6472
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_d25195e7:

    # n "After her admitting that she'll never let me close, I feel like {b}my{/b} world's just been ripped out from me."
    n "聽到笑美承認她永遠不會對我敞開心扉，{b}我{/b}的整個世界似乎也一同崩潰了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6474
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_893fde02:

    # n "What happened in that accident?"
    n "那次車禍，究竟發生了什麼？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6476
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_8640a555:

    # n "I know she lost her legs, but that's never seemed to bother her."
    n "我知道她失去了雙腿，但是笑美從來沒有對她的殘疾表示出任何困擾，"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6478
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_04297634:

    # n "What happened there?"
    n "那裡到底發生了什麼？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6480
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_e90b49b6:

    # n "What scares a girl so badly that she won't accept help, even from someone she loves?"
    n "是什麼事能把一個女孩變成這樣，以至於她不願接受幫助，即使是來自她所愛的人？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6482
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_f5fd36c3:

    # n "I don't know."
    n "我不知道。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6484
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_64684785:

    # n "{vspace=30}But I want to know."
    n "{vspace=30}但是我想要知道。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6486
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_f9d74b66:

    # n "I want to know so badly that being denied that answer feels like a knife in my guts."
    n "是如此迫切地想要知道，笑美的拒絕就像是一把尖刀，插在了我的胸口。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6490
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_76b2fe88_3:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6493
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_a18df911_1:

    # emi "Hisao?"
    emi "久夫？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6495
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_4b768ac9:

    # emi "You were saying?"
    emi "你剛才想說什麼？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6497
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_dfd96335:

    # "I'm still standing in the doorway."
    "我還站在門口。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6499
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_2eec6a14:

    # hi "…Nothing."
    hi "……沒什麼。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6501
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_edc7b9f4:

    # hi "Never mind."
    hi "別在意。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6509
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_5b9f5136:

    # "And I'm closing the door."
    "然後我關上了門。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6511
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_26e24540:

    # "And walking down the hallway."
    "沿著走廊"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6513
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_3392e5f5:

    # "Down the stairs."
    "走下樓梯。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6518
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_3879f84f:

    # "Out the door."
    "走出宿舍"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6520
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_b9740685:

    # "Into the dark."
    "走進黑暗中。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6527
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_52ae208b:

    # "Somehow I wander back to my own room. My brains are doing a mile a minute, going nowhere fast."
    "連自己都不知道究竟是怎麼走回房間的。無數想法在腦海裡奔騰，卻完全無法思考。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6529
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_76b2fe88_4:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6532
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_3e789cab:

    # n "{vspace=60}I can't figure out how to deal with this."
    n "{vspace=60}我不知道該如何處理這件事。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6534
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_01609bd7:

    # n "I thought that moving forward was a good thing."
    n "以為勇往直前就會有個好的結果。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6536
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_4b5f51b1:

    # n "Dwelling less on a past that I can't change. Living in the present and looking at the future."
    n "少去想無法改變的過去。活在當下，展望未來。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6538
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_ca2f4ba8:

    # n "{vspace=60}After this… thing with Emi, I'm not sure any more."
    n "{vspace=60}在跟笑美發生這件事之後……我再也不確定了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6540
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_f9856eb4:

    # n "She was saying the truth. It's simpler to look at the next curve, ignoring the path gone by."
    n "她說的是實話。只看著下一個彎道，忽略走過的路，是比較簡單的。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6542
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_9b4c9c44:

    # n "No worry about the opponent left behind. No care for the spectators on the sidelines."
    n "不用考慮被甩在身後的對手，不用擔心在邊線吶喊的觀眾。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6544
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_942f56f4:

    # n "And unfortunately, no time to watch out for lagging teammates either."
    n "不幸的是，也沒時間留意落後的隊友。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6546
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_76b2fe88_5:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6549
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_8684421a:

    # "I throw myself down on the bed, looking at one corner of my ceiling as if the answers I want were written there."
    "我把自己摔在床上，盯著天花板的一角，彷彿我想要的答案就寫在那裡。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6551
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_ffeb3ec8:

    # "No such luck, of course."
    "當然，沒那種好事。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6553
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_76b2fe88_6:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6556
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_0685fba6:

    # n "{vspace=150}She's literally running away from something - but have I not been doing the same thing, trying my best to forget about my hospitalization?"
    n "{vspace=150}她是在逃避什麼東西。但是我不是也一樣嗎？我不也是在盡力的逃避，盡力的想要忘記在醫院那段惡夢般的時光嗎？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6558
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_5ca82997:

    # n "I am getting better, but my health isn't going to magically fix itself."
    n "我正在好轉，但我的健康狀況不會奇蹟般地自己修復好。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6560
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_bcae3277:

    # n "{vspace=30}Emi has two legs instead of a heart to deal with, but those aren't going to magically fix themselves either."
    n "{vspace=30}笑美要處理的是兩條腿而不是一顆心，但那些也不會奇蹟般地自己長回來。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6562
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_250e5b09:

    # n "{vspace=30}Maybe this is just as fixed as the both of us can get."
    n "{vspace=30}也許這就是我們倆能被「修復」的最大程度了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6564
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_76b2fe88_7:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6567
translate zh_hant a3_emi_phantom_pain_f67d47cf:

    # "The room becomes darker and darker, until I can't really tell I'm looking at a corner any more."
    "房間越來越暗，直到我再也分不清自己是否還在看著那個角落。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6576
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_0bbf31df:

    # "The morning comes too soon, on the heels of a sleepless night."
    "在一個輾轉難眠的夜晚之後，清晨來得太快。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6578
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_9b48d6ee:

    # "Is this how Emi's been spending her nights?"
    "這就是笑美度過她夜晚的方式嗎？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6580
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_f7dcb03a:

    # "Staring at the wall, or ceiling. Trying to stop thinking about whatever it is."
    "凝視著牆壁，或天花板。試圖停止思考那些縈繞心頭的事。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6582
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_97e7b369:

    # "Her, in my case."
    "以我的情況來說，是關於她的事。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6584
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_a1583b46:

    # "That clenched feeling in my gut is still there."
    "昨天被她所傷害的心靈，依然在隱隱作痛。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6586
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_76b2fe88:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6589
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_524d2c66:

    # n "{vspace=60}'I can't rely on you.'"
    n "{vspace=60}「我不能依賴你。」"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6591
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_84c7dd39:

    # n "{vspace=30}Words spoken so casually."
    n "{vspace=30}說得如此隨便的幾個字。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6593
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_84559103:

    # n "Almost like she were teasing me, or chastising me for suggesting that the Earth is flat."
    n "幾乎就像她在逗我，或像在責備我說地球是平的一樣。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6595
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_e52283df:

    # n "{vspace=30}'That's how it's got to be.'"
    n "{vspace=30}「只能是這樣。」"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6597
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_b9225692:

    # n "{vspace=30}The way it's got to be sucks."
    n "{vspace=30}「只能是這樣」的方式爛透了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6599
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_42cd0061:

    # n "I'm feeling so miserable that I very nearly decide to skip the run."
    n "我心情糟透了，幾乎決定要翹掉晨跑。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6601
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_8912feb6:

    # n "That would be stupid, though. It's not something I should do just to see her."
    n "不過那樣太蠢了。這不該是只為了見她才做的事。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6603
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_e3dd44fd:

    # n "Sure, that was the original reason, but it's something more now."
    n "當然，那一開始是最初的理由，但現在已經不只是那樣了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6605
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_73ab70cf:

    # nvl clear
    # n "{vspace=120}I've started to enjoy the running itself."
    nvl clear
    n "{vspace=120}我已經開始享受跑步本身了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6609
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_db48a36b:

    # n "There are worse ways to get the blood flowing, anyway."
    n "總之，還有比這更糟的促進血液循環的方式。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6611
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_99f5e8a6:

    # n "Never thought I'd say it after that first week or so, but—"
    n "從沒想過在第一週左右之後我會這麼說，但是——"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6613
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_c35066c0:

    # n "{vspace=30}I feel a lot better after a run, like no matter what else I do today, I've at least done that one thing."
    n "{vspace=30}跑完步後我感覺好多了，好像不論今天還做了什麼，至少我完成了這一件事。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6615
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_b630c321:

    # n "It wakes me up, too, and Emi herself said that running always clears her mind. Maybe it'll help clear mine."
    n "跑步也讓我清醒，而且笑美自己也說過跑步總能讓她頭腦清晰。或許這也能幫助我理清思緒。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6617
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_4cca4b06:

    # n "{vspace=30}I hope so."
    n "{vspace=30}希望如此。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6619
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_76b2fe88_1:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6625
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_0cadd00a:

    # "The morning is cool and clear, if a bit humid. Summer's making itself known, it seems."
    "早晨涼爽晴朗，只是有點潮濕。看來夏天正宣告著它的到來。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6627
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_7a177fca:

    # "Emi's already stretching out when I arrive, and greets me with a smile and a wave."
    "我到的時候，笑美已經在伸展了，她笑著揮手跟我打招呼。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6632
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_41268bd2:

    # emi "Hey, Hisao!"
    emi "嘿，久夫！"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6634
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_dfc4aac0:

    # "The sight of her so chipper is like a kick in the nuts."
    "看到她這麼有精神的樣子，簡直像被人狠狠踹了一腳。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6636
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_df08732d:

    # "How can she be so happy after yesterday?"
    "經過昨天的事，她怎麼能還如此……若無其事？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6641
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_632eefb0:

    # "I give a half wave and am surprised to receive a hug."
    "我心不在焉地朝她招了招手；笑美出乎意料地給了我一個擁抱。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6646
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_6fd25320:

    # emi "Hey, about last night."
    emi "嘿，關於昨天晚上。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6648
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_4f30983b:

    # "Here it comes."
    "來了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6655
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_b4a1d3cb:

    # emi "I wanted to say thanks."
    emi "我想說，謝謝你。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6660
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_af4d1d4f:

    # emi "I actually managed to get some sleep for the first time in a while, and I think it's because of our talk."
    emi "這是我好一陣子以來第一次睡得著，我想是因為我們聊過的關係。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6665
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_e8de6908:

    # emi "So, thanks."
    emi "所以，謝謝啦。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6669
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_cb45918e:

    # "How could she sleep better after our chat?"
    "我們的談話之後，她怎麼可能睡得更好？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6671
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_7f6900a0:

    # "She basically told me that she wouldn't get any closer to me."
    "她基本上就是告訴我，她不會再讓我更靠近她了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6673
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_0c5851e5:

    # "And that let her sleep well?"
    "而那樣讓她睡得很好？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6675
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_634fc438:

    # "Excuse me, but what the hell?"
    "不好意思，這是在開什麼玩笑？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6677
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_18ee496e:

    # "Emi either doesn't notice my bafflement or chooses not to notice."
    "笑美要嘛沒注意到我的困惑，要嘛選擇不去注意。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6679
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_9da93fc2:

    # "No telling with her any more."
    "反正關於她的事，我再也搞不懂了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6681
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_54f64392:

    # hi "Oh, no problem. Glad it helped."
    hi "哦，沒問題。很高興有幫上忙。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6683
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_15acf596:

    # "The venom that threatens to drip into my voice is controlled for now, but I think I'd better start running now, before I do anything stupid."
    "我暫時控制住了那股差點滲入話語中的惡意，但我想我最好現在就開始跑步，免得做出什麼蠢事。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6688
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_a66bae7c:

    # "Emi seems equally willing to get started, and before long we're darting around the track."
    "笑美似乎也同樣想開始，沒多久我們就在操場上飛奔了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6690
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_08fe18e8:

    # "I can tell she feels more relaxed."
    "我看得出來她感覺放鬆多了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6697
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_7c05d675:

    # "Her running has gone back to the more graceful movements I remember from when I first watched her."
    "她跑步的動作又恢復了最初的優雅。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6699
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_19995892:

    # "It's a stark contrast to the almost brutal way she's been hurling herself around the track these past few days."
    "這和最近她那種近乎粗暴地在操場上猛衝的方式形成鮮明對比。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6701
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_66dc28c9:

    # "Our talk really does seem to have helped her."
    "我們的談話似乎真的幫了她。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6703
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_34232a4e:

    # "A pity it couldn't help me."
    "可惜沒能幫到我。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6705
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_19658c4f:

    # "I get into the rhythm of the running, thinking back to when I couldn't afford thinking about anything else but keeping my breathing steady and legs moving."
    "我進入了跑步的節奏，回想起當初我除了保持呼吸平穩和雙腿移動之外，根本無暇他顧的時候。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6707
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_499cb3b9:

    # "Guess those days are gone."
    "看來那些日子已經過去了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6709
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_075babd0:

    # "At least for the first couple of laps."
    "至少在頭幾圈是這樣。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6714
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_4d30bf68:

    # "Annoyed at the lack of success I'm having with clearing my head, I increase the pace."
    "對於清空腦袋這件事沒什麼成效，我感到惱火，於是加快了速度。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6716
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_47013e7d:

    # "Ah, there's the burning sensation in my legs."
    "啊，腿上那種灼熱感又來了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6718
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_0a9afe8c:

    # "The breaths coming ragged in my chest, the pounding of my heart. Which I still need to be careful about."
    "胸口傳來急促的呼吸，心臟怦怦直跳。我還是得小心點。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6720
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_400816f7:

    # "But it does seem to have gotten stronger; I can feel it pumping blood through my veins."
    "但它似乎真的變強了；我能感覺到它將血液泵送到我的血管裡。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6722
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_0ab09e4b:

    # "The sound thrums in my ears, but instead of being panicked as I was that day in the snow, I'm instead filled with elation."
    "低沉地跳動聲在我耳邊不斷響起，我並沒有像那個雪天一樣驚慌失措。相反，一種昇華的感覺湧過我的身體。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6724
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_86adaa66:

    # "Yes, it's working! My heart, that fatal flaw that landed me here, has improved."
    "太好了，它有在運作！我的心臟，那個讓我來到這裡的致命缺陷，已經改善了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6726
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_c25a8b8e:

    # "I'm able to keep going now, and maybe one day I'll be able to stop worrying as much."
    "又恢復了繼續前進地決心與動力。也許有一天，我能再也不必為它煩惱。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6728
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_9b049038:

    # "Right now, it doesn't matter that I have no idea what to do about Emi and me."
    "在這一刻，我和笑美之間的裂痕，我對於我們彼此感情之間的不知所措，似乎都無所謂了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6730
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_e63ea287:

    # "All that matters is that my arms and legs continue to pump in concert with one another."
    "現在，唯一重要的，就是我的手臂，我的雙腿，能夠像現在這樣，協調、均勻的不斷活動。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6732
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_d0c77d7b:

    # "Nothing else."
    "沒有別的了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6737
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_d8104f35:

    # "As I hit the final stretch, I remind myself that running really does help, though not as much as I'd hoped."
    "當我跑過最後一圈，我提醒我自己：跑步真的對我有幫助；只不過效果沒有我期望的那麼快就是了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6739
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_b7bb611a:

    # "I do feel better, and as I walk a few laps to cool down, I begin to remember last night in a slightly less emotional manner."
    "我確實感覺好多了，當我走幾圈緩和下來時，我開始用稍微不那麼情緒化的方式回想昨晚的事。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6741
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_43d69fd2:

    # "Emi wants me to stay distant from her."
    "笑美想要我與她保持距離。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6743
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_5ca0de6c:

    # "I can't bring myself to do so."
    "我沒辦法這麼做。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6745
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_69d21548:

    # "There's got to be a way around this, some kind of middle ground I can reach."
    "一定有辦法解決這個問題，某種我可以達成的中間地帶。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6747
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_2d4f4583:

    # "Not sure what that middle ground is, though."
    "不過，不確定那中間地帶是什麼。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6749
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_3a350c70:

    # "Damn, I was almost feeling optimistic."
    "可惡，我差點就覺得樂觀了起來。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6754
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_161d8dff:

    # emi "Nice run, Hisao! You've really improved!"
    emi "跑得不錯喔，久夫！你真的進步很多！"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6756
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_af555db9:

    # "Nice run. That's all I can hope for now, isn't it?"
    "跑得不錯。這是我現在唯一能指望的了，不是嗎？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6758
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_efa38e87:

    # "Congratulations, Hisao. You're pathetic."
    "恭喜你了，久夫。你這廢物。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6760
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_ee201a60:

    # "I gotta change my attitude."
    "不，我必須改變自己的態度。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6762
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_019a99b9:

    # hi "Well, you know. I am pretty awesome."
    hi "嗯，妳知道的。我可是很厲害的。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6764
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_9b52b830:

    # "And yet I just keep saying things that I don't mean."
    "然而我卻還是一直說著違心之論。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6766
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_48a7e73c:

    # "Any second now I'll be as good at hiding my problems as Emi is."
    "再過不久，我就會跟笑美一樣擅長隱藏自己的問題了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6771
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_d424a7c5:

    # emi "I like to think so."
    emi "我也這麼覺得喔。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6773
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_2c45da8d:

    # "Why does she do this to me? Say something like that with such real affection in her voice that it makes my heart leap?"
    "她為什麼要這樣對我？用那樣充滿真摯情感的聲音說出那樣的話，讓我的心都為之雀躍？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6775
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_a7cd818f:

    # "She doesn't mean it. She can't."
    "她不是真心的。絕對不可能。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6777
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_d4d1ed76:

    # "I must be doing a worse job than I thought, because Emi peers closely at me."
    "我顯然沒有我想像的那樣善於隱藏感情。笑美眯著眼湊了過來。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6782
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_f189db56:

    # emi "Hey, you feeling okay?"
    emi "喂喂，你沒事吧？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6787
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_0a3644b0:

    # emi "Maybe we should get to the nurse, huh?"
    emi "也許我們該去看校醫了，嗯？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6789
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_76eac390:

    # hi "Yeah, I'd hate to keel over on you."
    hi "是啊，我可不想昏倒在妳面前。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6791
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_7e5c4722:

    # "Emi looks a little shocked at my bitter tone."
    "笑美似乎對我尖酸的語氣有點驚訝。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6796
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_6d68562d:

    # emi "Don't say things like that!"
    emi "別說這種不吉利的話！"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6801
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_529b30e0:

    # emi "You've already done it once before, you know."
    emi "要知道，在我面前暈倒這種事情，你已經做過一次了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6803
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_978e8125:

    # "Why does she act so affectionate?"
    "她為什麼表現得這麼親暱？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6805
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_6deadfd8:

    # "She doesn't really care, I thought she made that clear."
    "她根本不在乎，我以為她已經說得很清楚了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6807
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_81779e12:

    # "But despite all of that I find myself apologizing, even though I shouldn't have to. Even though she's probably just putting on an act."
    "但儘管如此，我發現自己還是在道歉，即使我不該這麼做。即使她可能只是在演戲。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6809
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_8b65049b:

    # hi "Sorry, heh."
    hi "抱歉，呵。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6811
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_21c623e9:

    # hi "Come on, let's see the nurse."
    hi "走吧，我們去看校醫。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6813
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_4c593746:

    # "I can't get myself to calm down the whole time."
    "我始終無法讓自己冷靜下來。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6817
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_76b2fe88_2:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6820
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_05ccc61b:

    # n "{vspace=120}Every time it feels like I've gotten over what happened last night, Emi does something or says something that shows affection, and I'm back to the beginning."
    n "{vspace=120}每當我覺得自己已經挺過昨晚的事時，笑美就會做些或說些表示親暱的話，然後我又被打回原形。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6822
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_56f102a0:

    # n "The image of her ending that conversation haunts me."
    n "那次談話結束時，她無情的話語，依然環繞在我的心頭。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6824
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_96dcec54:

    # n "It was like the final twist of the knife that left me feeling bereft of any hope that Emi and I could be more than what we are."
    n "它彷彿刺向我心臟的最後一刀，剝奪了任何笑美與我關係能夠更近一步的希望。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6826
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_244fb547:

    # n "And what are we at this point? Little more than friends who happen to fuck."
    n "我們現在的關係是什麼？偶爾會一起做愛的普通朋友罷了？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6828
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_e02f24b3:

    # n "And really, it's not like I don't enjoy the time I spend with her. Said so the other day myself."
    n "可是我真心地享受著和她在一起的每一分鐘。以前如此，現在也是如此。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6830
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_a8302645:

    # n "I very nearly didn't even bring anything up with her, was just gonna hop on in there and let it ride, wasn't I?"
    n "幾乎都沒能鼓起勇氣面對她；只想著隨波逐流，順其自然，是嗎？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6834
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_76b2fe88_3:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6840
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_25d5da16:

    # "With this running through my head, I find myself in front of the nurse's office, still brooding as he checks out Emi."
    "腦中想著這些，我發現自己已經在保健室前，沉思著等笑美檢查結束。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6842
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_8eef6f34:

    # "Emi comes bounding out of the door, gives me a kiss, and darts off to shower, I assume."
    "笑美蹦蹦跳跳地出來，給了我一個輕吻，然後沿著走廊疾馳而去。大概是去沖澡了吧。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6844
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_6f5c3372:

    # "Meanwhile, the nurse beckons me into his office to give me the ritual once-over."
    "同時，校醫招手要我進他的辦公室，給我做例行的檢查。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6853
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_cdd0b28f:

    # nk "Any problems today?"
    nk "今天感覺如何？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6855
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_971b5fb6:

    # hi "Nah. I even pushed it a little harder today than I have in the past, and I seemed able to handle it."
    hi "沒什麼問題。今天跑步比平常要激烈一些，但是身體似乎還能夠適應。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6860
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_265627ca:

    # nk "That's uncharacteristically risky coming from you, Hisao."
    nk "你這樣說還真不像你平常的作風，久夫。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6862
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_b4236130:

    # nk "You've been hanging out with Emi too much. She's rubbed off on you, and not necessarily in a good way."
    nk "你和笑美相處時間太多了。看來她對你產生影響了，這可不是什麼好的影響哦……"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6864
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_23db58fd:

    # "At the mention of Emi's name, I can't help but frown unhappily in spite of my efforts at control."
    "一提到笑美的名字，儘管我努力控制，還是忍不住不悅地皺起了眉頭。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6869
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_d34ee6d4:

    # nk "Well, now. This is new, don't you think?"
    nk "哦，這下有意思了。這很新鮮，你不覺得嗎？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6874
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_0dc74a74:

    # nk "Last I checked, your usual response to Emi's name was a grin, not a frown."
    nk "上次我檢查的時候，你對笑美名字的通常反應是傻笑，而不是皺眉。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6879
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_4a074454:

    # nk "What exactly happened between you two? Because Emi doesn't seem to be in on it, whatever it is."
    nk "你們兩個到底發生了什麼事？因為不管是什麼事，笑美似乎都沒察覺。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6884
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_f89d7762:

    # nk "She looked more relaxed than I've seen her in weeks, which is unusual for this time of the year."
    nk "我有好幾周沒看到她這麼放鬆了。每年這個時候，這可並不常見。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6886
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_a09f8d61:

    # hi "What do you mean by that?"
    hi "你那樣說是什麼意思？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6891
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_5c0032a1:

    # nk "By what?"
    nk "什麼什麼意思？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6893
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_d9bcd658:

    # hi "'For this time of year.' I keep trying to find out what's been bothering her, but she clams up as soon as I broach the subject."
    hi "「每年這個時候。」我一直想找出是什麼在困擾她，但只要我一提起這個話題，她就閉口不談。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6895
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_79d07ddc:

    # hi "Then last night, she said—"
    hi "然後昨天晚上，她說——"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6900
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_11dd6e74:

    # nk "Let me guess. She won't tell you, because she says she can't trust you?"
    nk "讓我猜猜。她不告訴你，因為她說她不能信任你？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6902
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_5ece713e:

    # nk "And now you're crushed, because you thought that the two of you were so much more than she seems to think, right?"
    nk "所以你現在心碎了，因為你以為你們兩個的關係遠比她所想的更深，對吧？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6904
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_4b0fcd94:

    # hi "Er, more or less."
    hi "呃，差不多吧。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6906
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_b75a3000:

    # hi "How the heck did you know?"
    hi "你他媽是怎麼知道的？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6911
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_d19658dc:

    # nk "Hisao, I'm the nurse. It's my job to know these things."
    nk "久夫，我可是校醫。了解這些東西，不過是我的工作罷了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6916
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_62ec7fa4:

    # nk "Plus, I've known Emi for long enough to know that she'd try to do something like this; it's just like her."
    nk "再說，我認識笑美很久了；我知道她會做出這種事。她就是這樣的人。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6918
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_0a679eb9:

    # "He says this in the sort of half-affectionate, half-frustrated tone that would seem more appropriate if he had a cigarette dangling from his lips."
    "校醫先生說話的語氣半是親切，半是懊惱。這種大叔語氣，真應該給他嘴裡再叼上根菸。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6920
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_b5a02908:

    # "As it is, he seems willing to make do with a pen."
    "不過他嘴裡叼著的鋼筆也差不多啦。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6928
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_4c4bc11c:

    # nk "Look, you mind if I give you some advice?" nointeract
    nk "喂，我可能有些建議，你想聽聽嗎?" nointeract

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6942
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_4425a0b8:

    # "I open my mouth to respond but a knocking sound at the door interrupts me."
    "在我能開口回覆之前，一陣敲門聲打斷了我。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6944
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_8f502fa0:

    # emi "Hey, you guys still in there?"
    emi "喂，你們還在裡面嗎？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6949
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_407949d2:

    # nk "Just a moment, Emi."
    nk "等一下，笑美。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6951
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_aadb7537:

    # nk "Give us a second to get our pants back on."
    nk "給我們一點時間把褲子穿上。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6967
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_b22c8aee:

    # "The door bursts open and Emi glares knives at the nurse."
    "門碰的一聲打開，笑美瞪著眼，對著校醫怒目而視。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6969
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_b50cdfbd:

    # emi "Asshole."
    emi "混蛋。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6974
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_2dae0031:

    # nk "Didn't mean to get your hopes up."
    nk "我可不是故意讓妳想歪的。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6976
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_391b5314:

    # hi "Hey, can we… leave me out of this?"
    hi "喂，我們……可以不要把我扯進來嗎？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6978
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_d166ef66:

    # hi "Anyway, what's up, Emi? Forget something?"
    hi "總之，怎麼了，笑美？忘了什麼東西嗎？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6980
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_899181f1:

    # "I try to take a more cheerful tone with her."
    "我試著用更愉快的語氣跟她說話。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6982
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_e3e4cf73:

    # "No need to upset her. Two can play the 'everything's fine' game."
    "沒必要讓她不高興。我也可以玩「一切都很好」這種把戲。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6987
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_d810e149:

    # emi "Actually, I forgot to ask you something."
    emi "其實，我忘了問你一件事。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6989
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_b241ddd2:

    # hi "Oh? What's that?"
    hi "哦？什麼事？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6994
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_a603ab2a:

    # emi "Do you wanna come with me on a trip to my house?"
    emi "你想到我家一趟嗎？今天。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:6999
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_a020c4a4:

    # emi "My mom's making dinner, and I thought you might want to join us."
    emi "我媽媽做晚飯，我就想你要不要一起來吃……"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7004
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_99362257:

    # nk "Well, of course I accept."
    nk "嗯，當然了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7015
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_2dd46cb5:

    # "Emi punches the nurse in the arm playfully."
    "笑美開玩笑地捶了校醫的手臂一拳。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7017
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_d0d1d321:

    # emi "Not you, idiot. You were over last week."
    emi "不是你啦，笨蛋。你上週才來過。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7022
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_a1cd714f:

    # emi "I was talking to Hisao."
    emi "我是在問久夫。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7027
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_94013fc7:

    # nk "Oh? How interesting! Meeting the parent!"
    nk "哦哦？這真是有趣，已經要見家長了嗎！"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7029
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_129b3992:

    # hi "I'd love to go, Emi. Thanks."
    hi "我很樂意去，笑美。謝謝妳。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7034
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_962de355:

    # "The nurse raises an eyebrow, but says nothing."
    "校醫挑了一下眉毛，但什麼也沒說。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7036
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_82dbc18a:

    # emi "Great! I'll be in my room, swing by after you shower and change into something clean and we'll grab the bus!"
    emi "太好了！我會在我房間，你沖完澡換上乾淨的衣服後過來，我們就去搭公車！"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7038
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_ee372cef:

    # hi "Sounds good. I'll see you in a bit!"
    hi "沒問題，待會見！"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7045
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_93b15ea6:

    # "This time it's me who leans in for a quick kiss before darting off to my room."
    "這次，我採取了主動，在離開前傾身給了笑美一個輕吻。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7050
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_becbe0a0:

    # "What an interesting development."
    "真是個有趣的發展。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7052
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_993b4732:

    # "Maybe we're getting closer after all."
    "也許我們的距離終於還是逐漸拉近了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7054
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_89805690:

    # "Maybe Emi's finally ready to open up a little."
    "也許笑美終於準備好稍微敞開心扉了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7056
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_e4921fc8:

    # "Or maybe she's just being polite, and a free meal seems like a good way to apologize for last night."
    "再不然，也許她只是出於禮貌，用請我吃飯這種方法來為昨晚的事情道歉？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7058
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_e4be70b8:

    # "Great. Now I can't decide whether to be excited, nervous, or depressed."
    "太好了。現在我無法決定該興奮、緊張，還是沮喪。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7060
translate zh_hant a3_emi_debate_expresses_doubt_dcfe7be7:

    # "I settle for a combination of all three and hop in the shower."
    "我決定三種情緒都來一點，然後跳進淋浴間。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7077
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_76b2fe88:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7080
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_8a7ed09f:

    # n "{vspace=90}I don't think I like riding on buses."
    n "{vspace=90}我想我不喜歡搭公車。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7082
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_ba9a9572:

    # n "Actually, I think I'm pretty comfortable saying that as a fact."
    n "實際上，我相當確定，我根本不喜歡坐公車。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7084
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_5be26d8f:

    # n "They sway a lot, and they smell funny, and you can feel every bump in the road."
    n "搖搖晃晃，有股奇怪的味道。車子的每次顛簸，都被僵硬的座椅確切地傳達到我的身體。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7086
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_da63d109:

    # n "I'm really not looking forward to this."
    n "我真的一點也不期待。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7088
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_a6155558:

    # n "{vspace=30}Plus Emi's legs keep making a clanking noise that draws the attention of everyone else on the bus."
    n "{vspace=30}另外，笑美的腿時不時發出哐啷哐啷的聲音，把車上所有人的注意力都吸引了過來。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7090
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_2d4e9ba3:

    # n "She's in shorts again, and she's got long socks drawn up on her prosthetics so they don't look so obviously false again."
    n "她穿著短褲，外加拉得很高的長腿襪，以便把腿遮住，不至於一眼看出她戴著義肢。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7092
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_d0864dda:

    # n "But that doesn't stop the odd look or two every time her legs bump together with an audible clunk."
    n "但那並不能阻止每當她的腿碰在一起發出清晰的哐啷聲時，投來的一兩道奇怪的目光。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7094
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_0bf8ef19:

    # nvl clear
    # n "{vspace=90}I shift nervously in my seat, and Emi raises an eyebrow questioningly."
    nvl clear
    n "{vspace=90}我不自然地在座位裡扭來扭去；笑美疑惑地揚起了一邊眉毛。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7098
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_8fde870e:

    # n "She doesn't seem to mind the stares; either that or she doesn't even notice that people are staring."
    n "她似乎並不在意周圍人的視線；或者就是根本就沒有注意到。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7100
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_fa4575d2:

    # n "I'm sure she's gotten her fill of odd looks before. After a certain amount of time, I doubt she'd notice any more."
    n "我相信她以前已經受夠了奇怪的目光。過了一段時間後，我懷疑她根本不會再注意到了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7102
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_3be2bf38:

    # n "{vspace=60}Not that she'd ever tell me if I asked."
    n "{vspace=60}不過就算我問了，她也絕不會告訴我。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7104
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_43c945cf:

    # n "Another fact is, I'm not just uncomfortable about the bus."
    n "另一個事實是，我不只是對公車感到不自在。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7106
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_c63a736f:

    # n "I can't seem to come to terms with the fact that Emi appears to be trying to bring me closer while at the same time pushing me away."
    n "我似乎無法接受這個事實：笑美似乎在試圖拉近我的同時，又把我推開。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7108
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_76b2fe88_1:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7111
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_d0e4abc5:

    # n "{vspace=90}The nurse said she trusts me, even if it doesn't look like it."
    n "{vspace=90}校醫說過，即便表面看來並非如此，笑美也其實相信著我。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7113
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_108ee925:

    # n "But I'm not sure I can trust the nurse."
    n "但我不確定我能不能相信校醫。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7115
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_7ac49045:

    # n "He's protective of Emi, just like I'm protective of Emi, and I'd be likely to say something to make her look good if someone asked me about her."
    n "他努力保護著笑美不受傷害的心情，同我完全一樣。如果是我的話，我一定不願意在其他人面前說笑美的壞話。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7117
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_d4350c68:

    # n "{vspace=30}So he might just be doing that."
    n "{vspace=30}所以他可能只是在保護笑美。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7119
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_cb93adce:

    # n "{vspace=30}Still, there was something about the way he seemed genuinely surprised that Emi invited me along…"
    n "{vspace=30}無論如何，至少笑美對我的邀請，似乎真的令他吃了一驚。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7121
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_58f11d2b:

    # n "Maybe last night's talk helped more than I think, but I'm still worried."
    n "也許昨晚的談話比我想像的更有幫助，但我還是很擔心。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7125
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_c8284ac4:

    # nvl clear
    # n "{vspace=90}Meeting the parents is a big deal, right?"
    nvl clear
    n "{vspace=90}見家長。應該是件大事吧？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7129
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_151ac978:

    # n "Not that I haven't already met Emi's mother, but that was just as an acquaintance."
    n "雖然我早就見過笑美的母親了；不過，那隻能算是偶然相遇罷了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7131
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_eb595e05:

    # n "Now it's going to be as Emi's boyfriend, with everything that implies."
    n "這次，我的身份是笑美的男朋友。帶著這個身份所蘊含的一切意義。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7133
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_68d66c3f:

    # n "I can feel my heart pounding in my chest, an echo of that snow-covered afternoon that feels like it was so long ago that it might as well be another life entirely."
    n "我能感覺到我的心在胸口怦怦直跳，是那個白雪覆蓋的下午的回聲。感覺像是很久以前的事，久到彷彿是前輩子。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7135
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_8951f940:

    # n "Except then, I didn't know what was going on; I also didn't have medication to help prevent things spiraling out of control."
    n "只是那時，我不知道發生了什麼事；我也沒有藥物來幫助防止事情失控。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7137
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_9d11fb7d:

    # n "I've come a long way in terms of my physical health, and for the second time today I feel like I'll be able to live normally now, or at least as normally as possible."
    n "在我的身體健康方面，我已經進步很多了。今天，第二次我覺得我可以過正常人的生活了，或者至少盡可能地正常。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7139
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_b16aa4e1:

    # n "{vspace=30}Now if only I could manage my relationship as well as I've managed my heart, I'd be in great shape."
    n "{vspace=30}現在，要是我能像管理我的心臟一樣管理好我的感情關係，那就太好了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7143
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_76b2fe88_2:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7153
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_3215f00b:

    # emi "Well, we're here."
    emi "好了，我們到了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7157
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_19c6d106:

    # "Emi grabs my hand as soon as we've stepped off the bus. She starts heading down the street almost immediately."
    "剛一下車，笑美就抓起了我的手，刻不容緩地拉著我走了起來。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7162
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_99a092e0:

    # emi "Come on, we've got a couple blocks until my place."
    emi "快點快點，我們還要走好一段路呢"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7164
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_99973ebe:

    # hi "What? Oh, okay."
    hi "什麼？哦，好。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7171
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_36c9aab3:

    # "I follow Emi down the street, watching her confident stride."
    "我跟著笑美走在街上，看著她自信的步伐。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7173
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_5cf8b0b8:

    # "She's setting kind of a quick pace for just a walk."
    "對於正常的步行趕路來說，速度似乎有點快。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7175
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_4932c634:

    # "I guess she's anxious to get there."
    "看來她很急著回家嘛。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7177
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_e8a2dbe4:

    # hi "So does your mom do this sort of thing often?"
    hi "妳媽會經常安排這種事嗎？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7182
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_b00167cb:

    # emi "Nah, not too frequently. Mom's never been much for playing hostess."
    emi "不，不常。媽媽從來不怎麼喜歡當女主人。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7184
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_63754ef5:

    # hi "Oh yeah?"
    hi "哦，是嗎？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7189
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_c281946f:

    # emi "Yeah, my dad was always the one pushing her to have people over."
    emi "對啊，我爸才是喜歡熱鬧，總是慫恿她請人來家裡玩的。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7191
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_3c2ba0b9:

    # "This sudden and unprompted reference to her father catches me off guard."
    "突如其來地提到她父親，讓我措手不及。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7193
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_271e212c:

    # "And from the look on Emi's face, I'm not sure she meant to mention him. I think I've only ever heard her talk about him once."
    "從笑美的表情來看，我不確定她是不是有意提到他。我想我只聽她談過他一次。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7195
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_ded34242:

    # "All I remember is that Emi's mom told me that he wasn't around any more."
    "我只記得笑美的媽媽告訴我，他已經不在了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7197
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_8f35b675:

    # hi "Oh? Your mom prefers solitude?"
    hi "哦？妳媽媽喜歡獨處？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7202
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_1aa54e29:

    # "Emi laughs, either from relief that I didn't ask about her father or from finding my statement actually funny."
    "笑美笑了，要嘛是因為我沒問她父親的事而鬆了口氣，要嘛是覺得我的話真的很好笑。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7204
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_b0f69dca:

    # emi "Not at all! She's why I'm such an outgoing person, you know."
    emi "才不是這樣子！我這麼外向，可都是遺傳她的。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7209
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_a274fb6b:

    # emi "She just prefers to be a guest rather than a hostess; it's less stressful that way, or so she says."
    emi "她只是比較喜歡當客人而不是主人；那樣壓力比較小，至少她是這麼說的。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7211
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_49e21529:

    # hi "Clearly she's never had to meet her girlfriend's mother for dinner."
    hi "顯然她從來沒去女朋友家見她媽媽吃晚餐。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7213
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_773bc333:

    # "Emi giggles again and speaks in a teasing tone."
    "笑美又咯咯地笑了，用戲弄的語氣說話。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7218
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_92c8676c:

    # emi "Nervous, Hisao?"
    emi "緊張嗎，久夫？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7223
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_ad037194:

    # emi "You shouldn't be, you know! It's not that big a deal! Just dinner at my house, that's all!"
    emi "你不該緊張的，你知道嗎！沒什麼大不了的！只是在我家吃頓飯，就這樣！"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7225
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_f3285db1:

    # hi "Yeah, but have you ever brought home a boyfriend before?"
    hi "是啊，但妳以前帶過男朋友回家嗎？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7227
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_bbda0e07:

    # "I confess that part of me dreads hearing the answer to this."
    "我承認，我心底有些害怕聽到她的回答。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7229
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_b959ef4f:

    # "I know very little of Emi's past relationships - I don't even know if there were past relationships."
    "我對笑美過去的感情關係所知甚少——我甚至不知道她有沒有過往的感情關係。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7234
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_00f58c71:

    # emi "No, I guess I haven't."
    emi "沒有，我想我沒有。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7239
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_d9c0cb35:

    # emi "Hey, maybe this really is kind of a big deal after all…"
    emi "喂喂，也許這其實還真是件挺重要的事啊……"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7241
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_55c0a7cb:

    # hi "Oh good, now I feel twice as nervous."
    hi "哦，太好了，現在我感覺加倍緊張了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7243
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_f1d5e40f:

    # "Though to tell the truth, I'm pretty happy to hear that I'm the first one."
    "不過說實話，聽到我是第一個，我還挺高興的。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7245
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_6b029773:

    # "Maybe we've got something special after all."
    "也許我們之間終究有些特別的東西。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7255
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_7f1af478:

    # "Bolstered by this new thought, I've managed to calm down considerably by the time Emi knocks on her front door."
    "被這個新想法鼓舞，當笑美敲她家前門時，我已經鎮定了不少。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7260
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_20f845c9:

    # emi "Hey, mom, open up! We're here!"
    emi "喂，媽媽，開門！我們到啦！"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7269
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_843b5843:

    # "The door swings open, and Mrs. Ibarazaki stands grinning at her daughter. The grin is still surprisingly similar to Emi's."
    "門吱呀一聲地打開了。茨崎夫人站在門口，笑嘻嘻地看著她的女兒。二人的笑顏相似得出奇。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7271
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_634c6e39:

    # "I'm never going to get used to that."
    "我永遠都不會習慣這點。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7276
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_03fe68ad:

    # emm "You know, people normally wait for a few minutes before they start shouting at the door."
    emm "妳知道嗎？一般來說，人們在敲門後，會等上一段時間，才開始大吼大叫。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7281
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_08839c54:

    # emi "And most mothers say hello to their daughters instead of scolding them right away."
    emi "一般來說，女兒回家後，母親也會先打聲招呼，再開始批評她們。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7286
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_69cb3e1e:

    # emm "Ah, of course. Welcome home, dear. I've missed you."
    emm "啊，當然。歡迎回家，親愛的。我想妳了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7293
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_6fed2131:

    # "An affectionate hug later we're inside, and it is only then that Emi's mom seems to remember that I'm actually here."
    "一次深情的擁抱過後，我們一起走進了前門。直到這個時候，笑美的母親才似乎發覺我的存在。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7298
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_2429653d:

    # emm "And hello to you too, Hisao. How are you?"
    emm "你也好啊，久夫。最近怎麼樣？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7300
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_a9322a68:

    # hi "I'm quite well, thank you. Nice to not have school to worry about for a little bit."
    hi "我很好，謝謝。暫時不用擔心學校的事，感覺不錯。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7305
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_ec4b8631:

    # emm "Ah yes, you've finished up your exams, haven't you? That must be quite a relief for you both."
    emm "啊，對了，你們考完試了，對吧？對你們兩個來說一定鬆了一口氣。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7307
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_af3f277a:

    # hi "It's certainly a weight off of my mind, that's for sure."
    hi "那肯定是放下了我心頭的一塊大石。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7316
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_a2bfbb6e:

    # emi "Mine too! I think I slept well for the first time in weeks last night from relief alone."
    emi "我也是！鬆了一口氣，我昨晚是幾週來第一次睡得很好。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7318
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_369701e0:

    # "If this news is a surprise to Emi's mother, she doesn't show it. Still, her response betrays a note of interest."
    "如果這個消息讓笑美的媽媽感到驚訝，她並沒有表現出來。不過，她的回答還是透露出一絲興趣。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7323
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_7a768848:

    # emm "Is that so? I'm very glad to hear that, Emi. You know I get worried when you get all wound up about… well, exams."
    emm "是嗎？很高興聽到這個，笑美。妳知道的，當妳為了……嗯，考試……而緊張兮兮的時候，我都很擔心妳。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7325
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_c131bcd6:

    # "Certainly Emi's mother knows something I don't - or rather, she doesn't know that Emi's told me about the nightmares."
    "笑美的媽媽肯定知道一些我不知道的事——或者說，她不知道笑美已經告訴我關於惡夢的事了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7327
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_a91750ad:

    # "It's interesting, being able to observe how Mrs. Ibarazaki covers for Emi. That protective instinct to make sure that I don't know any more than Emi's willing to tell me."
    "能夠觀察茨崎太太如何為笑美掩飾，很有趣。那種保護本能，確保我不會知道任何笑美不願意告訴我的事。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7330
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_7db11b24:

    # "I suppose Emi's got more in common with quarks than I ever realized."
    "我想笑美和夸克的共同點比我意識到的還多。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7332
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_b857a616:

    # "Moves around fast, impossible to understand through direct observation, yet she has an effect on everyone she encounters."
    "跑得超快，無法透過直接觀察來理解，卻影響著她周圍的所有人。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7334
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_ebe4e0c6:

    # "I wonder if Mrs. Ibarazaki will figure out that I know about the nightmares, or is she just keeping everything secret from everybody?"
    "不知道茨崎太太會不會發現我知道惡夢的事，還是她只是對所有人都保密？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7339
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_03a6cfda:

    # emi "Yeah, it's not been as bad this year as in the past; Hisao helped me to stay focused."
    emi "嗯，今年沒有過去那麼糟；久夫幫我保持專注。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7341
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_729f6cb0:

    # "Okay, I know that's not true. She even cut off contact outside of school hours during exam week!"
    "好吧，我知道那不是真的。考試週期間，她甚至切斷了上課時間外時間的聯繫！"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7343
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_4fecd3ad:

    # "But… she did see me during the day. And she told me more than once that the morning run was the only thing she looked forward to during exams, so maybe it's not that much of a lie."
    "但是……白天她確實有見到我。而且她不止一次告訴我，晨跑是她在考試期間唯一期待的事，所以也許那也不是那麼大的謊言。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7345
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_11bf9e96:

    # "Either way, to hear that being around has helped even a little makes me feel a bit better."
    "無論如何，聽到我的存在即使只有一點點幫助，也讓我感覺好一些。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7347
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_aac3dd04:

    # "Emi's mother raises an eyebrow at this statement. Either she doesn't believe Emi, or she's as surprised as I am."
    "笑美的媽媽對這句話挑了挑眉。要嘛她不相信笑美，要嘛她和我一樣驚訝。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7352
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_93c96af6:

    # emm "Well, then it appears that it's a good thing you two have become so close."
    emm "嗯，那麼看來你們兩個變得這麼親近會是件好事。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7357
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_4f40d6af:

    # emm "I'd tell you to take good care of my daughter, Hisao, but it looks like you're already doing that."
    emm "我本來想跟你說好好照顧我女兒，久夫，但看來你已經在這麼做了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7362
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_bc0ce105:

    # "Emi grins at this and seems to take pride in my having managed to ingratiate myself with her mother so easily."
    "笑美對此咧嘴一笑，似乎為我這麼輕易地討好她媽媽而感到自豪。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7364
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_ecac9269:

    # hi "Actually, I'd say your daughter's been the one taking care of me. She's gotten me out and running."
    hi "其實，我倒覺得是您的女兒一直在照顧我。她讓我出門跑步。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7366
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_8f2542a7:

    # hi "I've probably been more active since meeting her than I ever was, even before…"
    hi "自從遇見她以來，我可能比以前任何時候都更充滿活力，甚至在……之前也是。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7368
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_ed798aa5:

    # "I'd actually never thought of it that much, nor had I ever appreciated the humor in it."
    "我其實從來沒有想想那麼多，也從來沒有發覺其中的黑色幽默。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7370
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_572d399f:

    # "I wasn't too active before the heart attack. Pickup games of soccer don't really count since they weren't that common."
    "在我心臟病發作前，我其實根本就是個死宅。除了和朋友及偶爾踢踢足球以外，幾乎從來不運動。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7372
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_b68c660e:

    # "So now that I know for sure that I have a weak heart, {b}now{/b} I run every day, pushing my luck with the help of my medication."
    "所以我知道了自己心臟不好，{b}現在{/b}反而每天跑步，靠著藥物的幫助挑戰身體的極限。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7374
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_2bc2ad07:

    # "I chuckle quietly, then realize that I never finished my sentence."
    "我輕輕地笑了笑，然後才意識到我還沒說完我的句子。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7376
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_95169090:

    # hi "Well, before I had my heart attack and wound up at school here."
    hi "嗯，在我心臟病發作並來到這裡上學之前。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7378
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_eab47adf:

    # "It comes out so casually. There was a time that I would have thought twice about talking about what was wrong with me at all."
    "曾經，我對任何有關我身體的話題都退避三尺。現在，我卻能夠如此隨意地談起它。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7380
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_ad4f9c4a:

    # "But now? Now it just seems silly to care, especially in the company of Emi and her mother."
    "此時此刻，在笑美和她母親面前，在意這種問題顯得很傻。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7382
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_fb0cf212:

    # "If Emi can be cavalier about her disability, then so can I."
    "如果笑美能對她的殘疾毫不在意，那麼我也可以。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7384
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_e04bb472:

    # "I think back to the track meet, where Emi declared herself the fastest thing on no legs."
    "我回想起那次運動會，笑美宣稱自己是沒有腿跑得最快的。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7386
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_0a2dfed6:

    # "The fact of her obvious loss has never seemed to bother her, at least not in public."
    "她明顯的缺陷似乎從未困擾過她，至少在公開場合沒有。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7388
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_1c095f7d:

    # "Being stuck in the wheelchair frustrated her, I know. But even that was something she dealt with on her own, despite my efforts to the contrary."
    "我知道，被困在輪椅上讓她很沮喪。但即使是那樣，她還是堅持依靠自己的力量，儘管我努力想幫忙。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7393
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_f5d0922e:

    # emm "Emi has a way of bringing out the more active side in people. I've never quite figured out how she does it."
    emm "笑美總是能激發身邊的人更有活力的一面。我一直沒搞懂她怎麼做到的。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7395
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_228a06d9:

    # "Those puppy dog eyes she gets, for starters."
    "喂喂，您看到過她那雙萌到犯規的大眼睛嗎……"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7400
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_0dce7133:

    # emm "I'm not surprised that she managed to rope you into an exercise routine."
    emm "她能把你拉進運動計畫裡，我一點也不驚訝。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7402
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_d91ab5cf:

    # emm "If Rin weren't just as stubborn as she is, I'm sure that Emi would have gotten her out and running with you too."
    emm "如果琳不是跟她一樣固執，我敢肯定笑美也會讓她跟你一起出去跑步的。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7407
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_8844467e:

    # emi "Oh, that reminds me! Rin says hello."
    emi "哦，這提醒我了！琳說跟你問好。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7412
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_54c5e239:

    # "I drift to the outer edges of the conversation again as we move into the dining room to eat."
    "走進餐廳入座，話題又轉向了與我無關的方面。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7414
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_46dd1e9b:

    # "It smells delicious in here, and the spread that Emi's mom has produced is impressive."
    "這裡聞起來好香，笑美媽媽準備的菜色也很豐盛。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7420
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_166a5b7f:

    # emi "Woah, you've made enough to feed an army in here!"
    emi "哇，妳做的菜夠餵飽一支軍隊了！"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7425
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_7bdb99ee:

    # emm "Is it too much? Well, you can always take some leftovers with you when you go."
    emm "太多了嗎？嗯，妳們走的時候可以打包外帶。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7427
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_c7bc167c:

    # hi "That sounds great! I can only handle cafeteria food for so long. Something home-cooked would be a welcome change of pace."
    hi "好啊！餐廳早就吃膩了。能有些家常菜，我贊成。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7432
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_e9653c2d:

    # emi "What he said. Thanks, mom."
    emi "他說的對。謝謝，媽。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7434
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_953178c3:

    # "The food tastes as good as it smells, and there's a lull in the conversation while we all dig in."
    "食物嚐起來和聞起來一樣美味，在我們都埋頭苦吃的時候，對話暫停了下來。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7436
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_5ee05f86:

    # "Emi assaults her plate with the usual amount of gusto, and I will admit that I set a pretty fast pace myself."
    "像平常一樣，笑美活力充沛地向盤子裡的食物發起全面進攻；我承認，我吃的速度也一點不慢。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7441
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_c85ff4ae:

    # emm "So Hisao, I hear that you and my daughter here have gotten rather close, hmm?"
    emm "所以，久夫，我聽說你和我女兒最近走得很近，嗯？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7443
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_e015eaec:

    # "The urge to say something like 'Not really' is so strong that I open my mouth to say it, but then reassert control."
    "那股想說「其實沒有」的衝動如此強烈，以至於我張開了嘴，但又重新控制住自己。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7445
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_01ca0ddd:

    # "We are close, there's no getting around it. I mean Emi's brought me here, hasn't she?"
    "我們很親近，這是無法迴避的。我的意思是，笑美把我帶到這裡來了，不是嗎？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7447
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_dcbeeac8:

    # "Fortunately, both Emi and her mother seem to take my reaction as a sign that I'm caught off guard rather than considering saying something cruel."
    "幸運的是，笑美和她媽媽似乎都把我的反應當作是我措手不及的表現，而不是在考慮說些殘酷的話。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7449
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_d484047f:

    # hi "Heh, I suppose we have. I blame the morning runs, myself."
    hi "哈哈，也許是吧。都是晨跑搞的鬼。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7454
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_28dc01e5:

    # emi "You make it sound like a bad thing, Hisao."
    emi "聽起來你對此很不滿啊，久夫。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7459
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_06bdd557:

    # emm "Well, I for one found it a relief."
    emm "嗯，我倒是鬆了一口氣。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7461
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_e2ba6edd:

    # hi "Why's that?"
    hi "為什麼？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7466
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_463818ea:

    # emm "Emi's always been a popular girl, but never made many close friends."
    emm "笑美從小就很受歡迎，但是真正的好朋友從來不多。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7468
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_33dd3af8:

    # "This is a bit of news to me. I've always seen Emi chatting with her classmates in the hallways."
    "這對我來說倒是件新鮮事。我一直都能看到笑美在走廊裡和她的同學嘰嘰喳喳的。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7470
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_c1df0fa8:

    # "And certainly the whole track team seems to love her, but it is true that she chooses to isolate herself during lunch with Rin and me."
    "而且學校的整個田徑隊也似乎對她青睞有加。不過，每到午休時間，她的確總是和我與琳單獨相處。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7472
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_4ae31f68:

    # "Not exactly the sort of behavior one expects from a popular girl, after all. Then again, I've experienced her unwillingness to get close firsthand, so I can't say I'm that surprised."
    "似乎的確不是一個人氣少女該有的作風……不過話說回來，我可是親自感受到了她自我封閉的傾向，所以我也沒法對此感到驚訝。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7477
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_90d1a678:

    # emm "I was beginning to have my doubts."
    emm "我都開始懷疑了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7482
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_8043a524:

    # "Emi rolls her eyes to the ceiling and grumbles something I can't quite make out."
    "笑美對著天花板翻了個白眼，咕噥了一些我聽不太清楚的話。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7486
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_0f638bea:

    # hi "Huh?"
    hi "哈？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7491
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_cf45f9a1:

    # emi "What?"
    emi "幹嘛？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7493
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_a13564ab:

    # hi "What's that you just said?"
    hi "妳剛才說了什麼？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7498
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_9beded29:

    # emi "Nothing."
    emi "什麼也沒說。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7503
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_fee27260:

    # "Mrs. Ibarazaki chokes on her drink with laughter."
    "茨崎夫人笑得幾乎把飲料都噴了出來。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7507
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_dbb9427c:

    # emm "You've been hanging out with the nurse too long, Emi."
    emm "妳跟那個校醫混太久了，笑美。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7509
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_7f9ca110:

    # emm "I'm going to have to talk to him about corrupting my daughter."
    emm "我得找他談談帶壞我女兒的事。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7511
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_ae5fa616:

    # hi "Somehow I don't think that would be very effective."
    hi "不知怎麼的，我覺得那樣不會很有效。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7516
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_8de4e42e:

    # emi "I learned most of it from you anyway. Not the nurse."
    emi "切，反正我都是從妳這裡學到的，又不關校醫的事。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7521
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_374f8d01:

    # emm "Don't listen to her, Hisao. She's a born liar."
    emm "別聽她的，久夫。她天生就是個小騙子。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7526
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_6a329f53:

    # emi "Hmph. Yeah right."
    emi "哼。最好是。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7528
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_32ec23fc:

    # hi "Oh, I don't know, Emi. I think your mother has a point."
    hi "哦，我不知道耶，笑美。我覺得妳媽媽說的有點道理。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7533
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_e1a3b072:

    # emi "What? You traitor! You're supposed to take my side in this!"
    emi "什麼？你這個叛徒！你應該站在我這邊的！"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7535
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_5e736e57:

    # hi "Yeah, but you did lie about your leg after the meet—{w=0.3}{nw}"
    hi "是啊，但是妳那次運動會後說自己的腿……{w=0.3}{nw}"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7539
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_f8858abd:

    # extend " ow!"
    extend " 噢！"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7541
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_ca3a150a:

    # "A kick in the shins from an unmistakably plastic foot cuts me off, but not before Mrs. Ibarazaki's eyebrows shoot upwards."
    "小腿處突如其來的痛苦打斷了我的的話，但還是引起了茨崎夫人的注意。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7546
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_1f7021fb:

    # emm "What about your leg?"
    emm "妳的腿怎麼了？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7551
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_5d05c03a:

    # emi "It wasn't a big deal, that's all… I just was, er, inawheelchairforabit."
    emi "沒什麼大不了的，就這樣……我只是，呃，坐了一陣子輪椅。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7553
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_c5755eb4:

    # "The last few mumbled words are quickly deciphered by Emi's mother - I suspect she has experience with this sort of thing - and a worried frown appears on her face."
    "最後幾個含糊的字被笑美的媽媽迅速解讀出來——我懷疑她對這種事有經驗——她臉上露出了擔憂的愁容。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7558
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_10b003df:

    # emm "So that's why he kept dodging my calls…"
    emm "所以他才一直躲我的電話……"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7560
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_32a1ecf5:

    # emm "Oh Emi… I know how much you hate being in a wheelchair."
    emm "哦天啊，我可憐的笑美……我知道妳有多討厭輪椅……"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7562
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_725c7ac6:

    # emm "No wonder you've been in such a mood lately!"
    emm "怪不得最近脾氣這麼差！"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7567
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_37020521:

    # hi "Yeah, she's much happier on her feet, so to speak."
    hi "是啊，她能站著的時候開心多了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7573
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_8f036395:

    # emm "Well of course! She spent enough time in a chair just after the accident."
    emm "那當然！事故剛發生後，她在輪椅上待了夠久了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7578
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_e3585a21:

    # hi "She didn't get prosthetics immediately?"
    hi "她沒有馬上裝義肢嗎？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7584
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_0466cd92:

    # emm "No, she had to finish healing up before they'd let her start the sort of therapy you've got to go through to adjust to those things."
    emm "沒有。療了好久的傷，那些醫生才允許她開始匹配義肢所必要的特殊療程。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7586
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_b9ad829c:

    # emm "Especially since she wanted to run on them."
    emm "尤其是她還想跑步……"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7591
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_1d9bf979:

    # hi "I had no idea."
    hi "我從來都不知道……"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7596
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_16ef8a97:

    # emi "Yeah, it sucked. Oh, did you see Rin's mural at the festival?"
    emi "對啊，超糟的。喔，妳在學園祭上有看到琳的壁畫嗎？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7598
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_d99e95ec:

    # "Emi's sudden change of topic makes me realize belatedly that she's been fidgeting the whole time her mother and I have been talking."
    "笑美突然轉變話題，讓我後知後覺地意識到，在我跟她媽媽說話的這段時間，她一直都坐立不安。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7600
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_03cc72b7:

    # "I should have figured on her being a little skittish when it comes to talking about the accident. Even around her mother."
    "我早該想到，只要一談到那場意外，她就會有點緊張。即使是在她媽媽面前也一樣。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7605
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_07bcaae4:

    # emm "No, I didn't make it out to the festival, remember?"
    emm "沒有，我沒去學園祭，妳忘了嗎？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7610
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_290dece8:

    # emm "Although I caught a glimpse of it at your track meet. It seemed pretty weird to me."
    emm "不過在妳上次的運動會上，我倒是瞥見了一眼。對我來說還挺詭異的。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7615
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_536e05f3:

    # emi "I think that's more or less what she was going for. She talked a lot about it being dreamlike. Or trying to make it dreamlike."
    emi "我想她要的就是那種感覺吧。她說了很多關於要讓它有夢境般的感覺。或是試著讓它變得如夢似幻。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7620
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_a4f345bb:

    # emm "Rin's art is one of those things I don't think I'll ever understand."
    emm "琳的藝術，我想我這輩子大概都無法理解了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7625
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_4b87f18e:

    # emi "That's not surprising. I don't think Rin expects to be understood."
    emi "那不意外啊。我想琳也沒期望別人能理解她。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7630
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_0ed9e21c:

    # emi "She told me once that art allows people to understand stuff they wouldn't understand otherwise, but all the same she doesn't think it actually works that way."
    emi "她有一次跟我說，藝術能讓人們理解他們原本無法理解的東西，但她同時也覺得實際上並不是那樣運作的。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7632
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_40f1ec35:

    # "I'm surprised that Emi's talked about this with Rin extensively enough to actually have Rin's opinion, such as it is."
    "我很驚訝笑美竟然和琳就這個話題聊得這麼深入，甚至還知道了琳的想法，儘管那想法還是很難懂。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7634
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_7f6b9020:

    # "Although I expect that Rin could not, if she were so inclined, say the same thing about Emi's."
    "不過我猜，如果琳有那個興致的話，她大概沒辦法說出同樣的話。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7636
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_9921e9cb:

    # "Unless, of course, Emi is purposely keeping me in the dark about everything; which is likely, but unpleasant to think about."
    "當然，除非笑美是故意對所有事情都瞞著我；有可能，但想起來就讓人不舒服。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7638
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_bfc4fe33:

    # "I drift down this unpleasant train of thought for a while, losing track of the conversation."
    "腦海充滿了這串壓抑的想法，思緒又離開了眼前的談話。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7643
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_b71f5676:

    # emm "Hey Emi, I've been meaning to ask…"
    emm "欸，笑美，我一直想問妳……"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7648
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_d5e5048f:

    # emi "Huh?"
    emi "嗯？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7653
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_551b3be0:

    # emm "Are you going to visit your father this year?"
    emm "妳今年要去探望妳爸爸嗎？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7657
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_30b6cf65:

    # "From the way she says it, you'd think Emi's mother was talking about the weather. From the way Emi reacts, it's clearly not the weather they're talking about."
    "從她說話的語氣來聽，你可能會以為笑美的媽媽在談論天氣。但從笑美的反應來看，她們談論的顯然不是天氣。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7662
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_8ab5bf74:

    # "She flinches, a slight jerk of the head backwards as if she's just been slapped in the face."
    "笑美的頭向後猛地一抽，身體向後退縮，彷彿被人扇了耳光。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7667
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_f3776a60:

    # emi "Can we talk about this later?"
    emi "我們可以晚點再談這個嗎？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7669
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_c0450383:

    # "Her voice sounds brittle, strained. It looks as if she's been severely shaken by the question."
    "她的聲音聽起來很脆弱、很緊繃。看來這個問題讓她受到了很大的打擊。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7671
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_7c05bc2f:

    # "It seems that Mrs. Ibarazaki misjudged just how close Emi and I are."
    "看來茨崎夫人似乎誤判了我跟笑美的親近程度。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7673
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_a1059814:

    # "Some things, it seems, are best not conversed about with me around. Her father is one of these things."
    "有些事情，看來最好不要在我身邊談論。她的父親就是其中之一。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7675
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_e2e1899a:

    # "The accident that took her legs is probably another one of those things, if her reaction to the earlier conversation between her mother and myself is any indication."
    "如果她對先前她母親和我之間對話的反應能說明什麼的話，那場奪走她雙腿的意外，大概也是其中之一。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7677
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_e0c9019c:

    # "It doesn't take Emi's mother long to realize she's screwed up."
    "笑美的母親很快就發覺了自己的錯誤。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7682
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_fc616770:

    # emm "Of course we can, dear. I'm sorry to bring it up, I just wanted to ask so I could make plans—"
    emm "當然了，親愛的。真是十分抱歉，我只是想早些做好準備……"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7687
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_14d83275:

    # emi "It's fine. Don't worry about it."
    emi "沒關係。別擔心。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7689
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_98e1c6e8:

    # "Emi fidgets nervously, as if embarrassed by her own reaction. I confess that her reaction is confusing."
    "笑美緊張地坐立不安，好像對自己的反應感到尷尬。我承認，她的反應令人困惑。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7691
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_b4fcff75:

    # "She only just mentioned her father to me earlier today! Less than a few hours ago, even!"
    "她今天稍早才跟我提到她父親！甚至不到幾個小時前！"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7693
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_ad44ae1f:

    # "Why does a simple question about when she'll visit her father cause such a strong reaction?"
    "為什麼一個關於她何時去探望父親的簡單問題，會引起這麼強烈的反應？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7695
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_f75b261e:

    # "Unless whatever serenity she claimed to have reached by means of our talk the previous evening has suddenly evaporated."
    "除非她聲稱透過我們前一晚的談話所獲得的任何平靜，都突然煙消雲散了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7697
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_8156789b:

    # "Or it didn't help as much as she thought. Or claimed."
    "或者是它根本就沒有她想像中那樣有效。再或者她根本就是在騙人。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7702
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_4d5d59ee:

    # emi "I'll uh, be right back. Gotta visit the little girl's room."
    emi "我、呃，馬上回來。要去一下洗手間啦。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7711
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_cb1cf1ef:

    # "Emi gets up suddenly and leaves the table, leaving me and Mrs. Ibarazaki alone."
    "笑美突然站起來離開餐桌，留下我和茨崎夫人獨處。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7713
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_5a946000:

    # "I'm a little conflicted. Should I go after her, or should I stay here?"
    "我內心有些掙扎。究竟是該追她出去，還是留在這裡？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7715
translate zh_hant a3_emi_guess_whos_coming_never_mind_9f687960:

    # "It's obvious that Emi's departure was not based on the call of nature. Something's bothering her, and I have to know what it is."
    "很明顯，笑美的離開並不是因為生理需求。有什麼事在困擾她，而我必須知道那是什麼。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7753
translate zh_hant a3_emi_instant_replay_b680217d:

    # "The morning alarm sounds and I roll over, switching it off. My eyes open blearily to stare at the ceiling."
    "早晨的鬧鐘響起，我翻了個身，把它關掉。睡眼惺忪地睜開眼睛，盯著天花板。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7757
translate zh_hant a3_emi_instant_replay_76b2fe88:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7760
translate zh_hant a3_emi_instant_replay_6a3194b6:

    # n "{vspace=60}What am I going to do? Do I get out of bed, go down to the track, and pretend that nothing happened?"
    n "{vspace=60}我該怎麼辦？起床，下樓去操場，假裝什麼事都沒發生過？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7762
translate zh_hant a3_emi_instant_replay_5ab072f7:

    # n "Will Emi even show up? After last evening's events, I doubt it."
    n "笑美會出現嗎？經過昨晚的事，我想大概是不會了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7764
translate zh_hant a3_emi_instant_replay_f722a445:

    # n "Even supposing that she did, what would I do then? Get over this fight just to dance the same routine the next time something's bothering her?"
    n "就算她真的出現了，那我又該怎麼辦？忘記這次爭吵，然後下次她又有什麼煩心事時，再跳一次同樣的舞？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7766
translate zh_hant a3_emi_instant_replay_849db78f:

    # n "I know that I spoke hastily last evening, especially trying to use her father as leverage."
    n "我知道我昨晚說話太衝動了，特別是想用她父親的事當作籌碼。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7768
translate zh_hant a3_emi_instant_replay_7466e7f4:

    # n "But was anything I said really off the mark? She won't let me in, ever, and she'll be forced to suffer alone."
    n "但我說的話真的有哪裡不對嗎？她永遠不會讓我走進她的內心，她只會被迫獨自受苦。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7770
translate zh_hant a3_emi_instant_replay_6c093fa7:

    # n "Nothing I do, nothing I say is going to change that. She won't change, and she's already decided to keep me at arm's length."
    n "我做什麼、說什麼都改變不了這點。她不會改變，而且她已經決定要和我保持距離了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7772
translate zh_hant a3_emi_instant_replay_59b1b5a2:

    # n "{vspace=30}Can I really bring myself to go down there and see her, knowing that I'm never going to get past where I am now?"
    n "{vspace=30}清楚地知道我們的關係永遠不會再進一步，我真的能現在就這樣去面對她嗎？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7774
translate zh_hant a3_emi_instant_replay_76b2fe88_1:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7780
translate zh_hant a3_emi_instant_replay_b558f347:

    # "No, I decide. I really can't. Not today. I roll over and go back to sleep."
    "不，我決定了。我真的辦不到。今天不行。我翻過身，繼續睡回籠覺。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7782
translate zh_hant a3_emi_instant_replay_368a2055:

    # "She probably won't be there anyway."
    "反正她也根本不會在那裡的。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7787
translate zh_hant a3_emi_instant_replay_f2af4db5:

    # "A similar mental conversation repeats itself when it comes time to go to lunch, and I eat in the cafeteria, alone."
    "到了午餐時間，類似的內心對話又重複了一遍，我一個人在餐廳吃飯。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7789
translate zh_hant a3_emi_instant_replay_aef0cd7d:

    # "I don't want to see her; the very thought makes me feel ill."
    "我不想見到她；光是這個念頭就讓我覺得不舒服。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7794
translate zh_hant a3_emi_instant_replay_a513cf4d:

    # "That night, I go for a run; I'm solo for the first time since Emi got sick after the track meet."
    "那天晚上，我去跑步了；這是自從運動會後笑美生病以來，我第一次自己一個人跑。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7796
translate zh_hant a3_emi_instant_replay_53fd5c7a:

    # "Skipped seeing the nurse, just in case he asked about Emi."
    "我沒去找校醫，免得他問起笑美的事。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7798
translate zh_hant a3_emi_instant_replay_3c4c8b74:

    # "I don't want to talk about her, either."
    "我也不想提到她。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7803
translate zh_hant a3_emi_instant_replay_0462fc35:

    # "The next day, I do the same thing. Alarm, off. Stay in bed. Eat alone, run alone."
    "第二天，我做了同樣的事。關鬧鐘。賴床。一個人吃飯，一個人跑步。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7805
translate zh_hant a3_emi_instant_replay_40f83df9:

    # "To fill the time that I would usually be spending with Emi, I start reading more."
    "為了填補平常會和笑美在一起的時間，我開始讀更多的書。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7807
translate zh_hant a3_emi_instant_replay_68ae325d:

    # "It works surprisingly well, until I find myself ducking into a restroom because I see her walking down the hall in between classes."
    "這方法出奇地有效，直到我在課間看到她走在走廊上，而我下意識地躲進了廁所。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7809
translate zh_hant a3_emi_instant_replay_067980ec:

    # "If she noticed me, she didn't show it, even though I don't suppose she ever shows anything."
    "如果她有注意到我，她也沒有表現出來，雖然我猜她從來不會表現出任何反應。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7811
translate zh_hant a3_emi_instant_replay_763198c0:

    # "Certainly not to the girls from her class I see talking cheerfully to her."
    "至少對她那些一起嘻嘻鬧鬧的同班同學沒有。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7813
translate zh_hant a3_emi_instant_replay_cadf6a00:

    # "Or to her fellow track members."
    "對她田徑隊的其他隊員也沒有。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7815
translate zh_hant a3_emi_instant_replay_a4e3112d:

    # "Especially not to me."
    "尤其對我沒有。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7817
translate zh_hant a3_emi_instant_replay_a08995ae:

    # "Alarm off. Stay in bed."
    "關掉鬧鐘。繼續睡覺。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7823
translate zh_hant a3_emi_instant_replay_d7d7db9f:

    # "Mutou and I have a lengthy talk about the possibility that string theory is plausible. I don't buy it, myself."
    "我和武藤老師就弦論是否可信進行了長時間的討論。我自己是不太信的。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7825
translate zh_hant a3_emi_instant_replay_fc8c183a:

    # "More than four dimensions, I can buy. But a bunch of vibrating strings at the subatomic level? That's asking a bit much."
    "超過四個維度，我可以接受。但在次原子層級有一堆振動的弦？這就有點太扯了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7827
translate zh_hant a3_emi_instant_replay_263ec96c:

    # "Looks like I'm not the only one to think this way, too. Apparently it's not really as strong a theory as it once was."
    "看來不只我一個人這麼想。顯然，這個理論已經不像以前那麼有力了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7829
translate zh_hant a3_emi_instant_replay_b12d92d3:

    # "Mutou says that's just because nobody has found the right way of looking at the data yet."
    "武藤老師說，那只是因為還沒有人找到看待數據的正確方式。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7837
translate zh_hant a3_emi_instant_replay_8aeeb3af:

    # "Eat alone."
    "一個人吃飯。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7839
translate zh_hant a3_emi_instant_replay_3ca0d5ad:

    # "The rooftop is deserted today. I briefly wonder where Emi and Rin are, but shrug off the question. The important thing is that they aren't here, so I won't have to talk to them."
    "今天的屋頂空無一人。我短暫地想了一下笑美和琳在哪裡，但隨即把這個問題拋到腦後。重要的是她們不在這裡，所以我不用跟她們說話。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7841
translate zh_hant a3_emi_instant_replay_8683142c:

    # "Since I have nobody to talk to, I bring a book with me to read."
    "既然沒人可以說話，我就帶了本書來讀。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7843
translate zh_hant a3_emi_instant_replay_0822dd6b:

    # "The weather's nicer, if getting a little hot."
    "天氣變好了，雖然有點熱。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7845
translate zh_hant a3_emi_instant_replay_605fab63:

    # "Hopefully it will be cooler in the evening; a cool breeze seems to back up my theory."
    "希望晚上會涼快一點；一陣涼風似乎印證了我的想法。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7852
translate zh_hant a3_emi_instant_replay_ffe6c4e7:

    # "Run alone."
    "一個人跑步。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7854
translate zh_hant a3_emi_instant_replay_a70e82c7:

    # "It is, in fact, cooler at the track. No sign of Emi, which is exactly the sort of thing I'm going for."
    "事實上，操場這裡比較涼快。沒有笑美的蹤影，正合我意。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7856
translate zh_hant a3_emi_instant_replay_8624089c:

    # "I stretch out and start on my usual run, trying hard to ignore the lack of a running partner in front of me."
    "我伸展身體，開始我平常的跑步，努力忽視眼前少了個跑步夥伴。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7858
translate zh_hant a3_emi_instant_replay_14ba994a:

    # "Finding my thoughts drifting damnably to that girlish laugh, incorrigible grin, those wide and friendly eyes, her incredibly toned body—"
    "發現自己的思緒可恨地飄向那少女般的笑聲、那無可救藥的笑容、那雙寬大友善的眼睛、她那迷人的線條——"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7863
translate zh_hant a3_emi_instant_replay_749ec5cb:

    # "I increase the pace to clear my head. Chew up the distance between me and the turns, find the speed that makes me think only of my legs and how much they burn."
    "我加快速度來清空腦袋。吞噬我與彎道之間的距離，找到那種能讓我只專注於雙腿以及它們有多灼熱的速度。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7865
translate zh_hant a3_emi_instant_replay_62d6141e:

    # "I glance at my watch as I round the final turn, noting that my time's gotten faster."
    "繞過最後一個彎道時，我瞥了一眼手錶，似乎又刷新紀錄了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7870
translate zh_hant a3_emi_instant_replay_c34435a9:

    # "My heart seems a little squirrelly tonight, so I give myself a few extra cool-down laps just to be safe."
    "今晚心臟似乎有點不對勁，所以為了安全起見，我多跑了幾圈緩和運動。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7872
translate zh_hant a3_emi_instant_replay_30baaa09:

    # "No reason to bring this to the nurse's attention. I'll be fine. A rather Emi-ish thought to have, I'll admit."
    "沒理由讓校醫注意到這件事。我會沒事的。我承認，這真是個非常笑美式的想法。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7874
translate zh_hant a3_emi_instant_replay_aba6608c:

    # "I have to hope that eventually I'll stop thinking about her so much."
    "我只能希望，總有一天我會停止這麼頻繁地想起她。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7879
translate zh_hant a3_emi_instant_replay_6b61b823:

    # "I finish another book before going to bed that night. I'll have to stop by the library tomorrow."
    "那天晚上睡前我又讀完了一本書。明天得去一趟圖書館了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7900
translate zh_hant a3_emi_instant_replay_4b326df0:

    # "I don't know why I keep the early alarm on any more, but it wakes me up the next morning just the same. I still turn it off and go back to sleep."
    "我不知道為什麼還開著早上的鬧鐘，但隔天早上它還是一樣把我叫醒。我依然關掉它，然後繼續睡。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7908
translate zh_hant a3_emi_instant_replay_d600b3ca:

    # "That afternoon, as I get ready to head to the cafeteria for another solo lunch (I've got a new book about a couple of con men in ancient Persia that I'm pretty excited about reading) I am suddenly cornered by Misha and…"
    "那天下午，當我準備去餐廳吃另一頓一個人的午餐時（我借了一本關於古波斯兩個騙子的新書，正興致勃勃地想讀），我突然被米莎和……"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7910
translate zh_hant a3_emi_instant_replay_4567b99b:

    # "Huh. I guess just Misha."
    "咦。只有米莎？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7915
translate zh_hant a3_emi_instant_replay_eff7d165:

    # mi "Off to eat alone again, Hicchan~?"
    mi "又要自己一個人去吃飯啦，小久～？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7920
translate zh_hant a3_emi_instant_replay_125a6879:

    # mi "We've noticed, you know~!"
    mi "我們注意到了喔～！"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7922
translate zh_hant a3_emi_instant_replay_be2d8009:

    # hi "We?"
    hi "我們？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7927
translate zh_hant a3_emi_instant_replay_ca9b28c0:

    # mi "Uh huh! Shicchan and I noticed that you've been spending more time alone!"
    mi "是哦！小靜和我，注意到了你獨自一人的時間可是多了許多哦！"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7932
translate zh_hant a3_emi_instant_replay_7f250962:

    # mi "She wanted me to find out why, so I told her I'd ask you!"
    mi "她想知道為什麼，所以我就跟她說我會來問你！"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7934
translate zh_hant a3_emi_instant_replay_dbcf5995:

    # hi "I'm surprised she didn't ask me herself."
    hi "我很驚訝她沒有親自來問我。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7939
translate zh_hant a3_emi_instant_replay_7c0f0e12:

    # mi "She would have, but she wanted to get a head start on some paperwork. There's a lot of it since we're coming up on the end of the term, you know~!"
    mi "她本來想來的，但她想先處理一些文件。快到學期末了，有很多東西要處理，你知道的嘛～！"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7941
translate zh_hant a3_emi_instant_replay_a9798800:

    # hi "Why the sudden interest in my well-being, anyway?"
    hi "話說回來，怎麼突然關心起我的狀況了？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7946
translate zh_hant a3_emi_instant_replay_29a7f10e:

    # mi "Ah, Shicchan said 'It is the duty of the Student Council to keep track of the emotional health of its students! To allow a cons—constituent to spiral into depression unchecked would be an unforgivable failure in the council's duties!'"
    mi "啊，小靜說：『學生會的職責就是要關心學生的心理健康！放任一個學生陷入憂鬱而不顧，是學生會不可原諒的失職！』"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7948
translate zh_hant a3_emi_instant_replay_3d6f7497:

    # hi "Well, that's easy, then. I'm not depressed."
    hi "哦，那簡單了。我沒有憂鬱。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7953
translate zh_hant a3_emi_instant_replay_3a768537:

    # mi "But you're eating alone, and nobody's seen you and Emi together at all! Something happened, didn't it, Hicchan~?"
    mi "但是你都自己一個人吃飯，而且完全沒人看到你和笑美在一起！發生了什麼事，對不對，小久～？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7955
translate zh_hant a3_emi_instant_replay_3525cbdd:

    # "Misha's voice takes on a slightly sterner tone, though somehow she keeps the familiar lilt at the end of her sentences."
    "米莎的語氣變得稍微嚴厲了些，但不知為何，她的句尾還是帶著那熟悉的輕快語調。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7976
translate zh_hant a3ec1o1_1e6ef2de:

    # hi "Are you absolutely sure?"
    hi "妳確定嗎？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7978
translate zh_hant a3ec1o1_2c5b5ed3:

    # hi "You don't want to go ahead and adjust it before heading up the stairs?"
    hi "妳不想在上樓前先調整一下嗎？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7980
translate zh_hant a3ec1o1_631f6b45:

    # hi "You could get hurt if you don't, right?"
    hi "如果不調整的話，妳可能會受傷的，不是嗎？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7985
translate zh_hant a3ec1o1_2835b752:

    # emi "I said it was fine, Hisao."
    emi "我說過了，沒事的，久夫。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7990
translate zh_hant a3ec1o1_d8ef0a60:

    # emi "Seriously, don't worry about it."
    emi "真的，別擔心。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7995
translate zh_hant a3ec1o1_7abc511b:

    # emi "I've got some experience in these matters, after all."
    emi "畢竟，我在這方面還算有經驗。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7997
translate zh_hant a3ec1o1_f47650ad:

    # hi "Yeah, I suppose so."
    hi "嗯，我想也是。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:7999
translate zh_hant a3ec1o1_ffa75436:

    # "Emi grins reassuringly."
    "笑美放鬆地露出了微笑。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8004
translate zh_hant a3ec1o1_8556a6d0:

    # emi "Honestly, Hisao, I appreciate the concern but I really am okay."
    emi "說真的，久夫，很感謝你的關心，但我沒事的。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8009
translate zh_hant a3ec1o2_1304d62e:

    # "Well, she's probably fine."
    "嗯，她大概沒事吧。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8011
translate zh_hant a3ec1o2_6ae99f52:

    # "I imagine she'd say something if it was really a problem."
    "我想如果真的有問題，她應該會說的。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8013
translate zh_hant a3ec1o2_07d3e409:

    # "Heck, she'd probably get annoyed if I kept bringing it up."
    "還是算了，如果我再繼續追問下去，她可能會嫌我煩的。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8018
translate zh_hant a3ec2o1_49acf163:

    # hi "Yeah, I've got some time. Nowhere important to be or anything like that."
    hi "有啊，我有的是時間。沒什麼重要的事。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8023
translate zh_hant a3ec2o1_f6ff709d:

    # "Mutou raises an eyebrow as if questioning my statement, then beckons me back into the classroom."
    "武藤老師挑起一邊眉毛，像是在質疑我的話，然後示意我回到教室裡。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8034
translate zh_hant a3ec2o1_c0fcded6:

    # mu "I wanted to get some feedback from you, if I could."
    mu "如果可以的話，我想聽聽你的一些回饋。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8036
translate zh_hant a3ec2o1_2ae600e4:

    # mu "I know that this course wasn't quite up to your level…"
    mu "我知道這門課對你來說，程度有點太淺了……"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8038
translate zh_hant a3ec2o1_b7d75319:

    # hi "Don't worry about it. The science club activities more than made up for it."
    hi "別這麼說。科學社的活動足以彌補這點了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8043
translate zh_hant a3ec2o1_ec1ed78c:

    # mu "Hmm, did they?"
    mu "哦，是嗎？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8048
translate zh_hant a3ec2o1_6f109888:

    # mu "Well in fact, that's what I wanted to talk to you about."
    mu "嗯，事實上，那正是我想要跟你談的。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8050
translate zh_hant a3ec2o1_1eb5d0ab:

    # mu "Do you think that was a worthwhile activity? Just for my own reference."
    mu "你覺得那個活動有價值嗎？只是供我個人參考。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8052
translate zh_hant a3ec2o1_a058eb79:

    # hi "Well yeah, it was a great way to go further than we did in class. It was definitely worthwhile."
    hi "嗯，有啊，那是個比課堂上更深入的好方法。絕對很有價值。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8057
translate zh_hant a3ec2o1_ab053ee6:

    # "Mutou seems delighted by my response."
    "武藤老師似乎對我的回答感到很高興。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8059
translate zh_hant a3ec2o1_b651e417:

    # mu "That's great! Exactly the sort of thing I was hoping for."
    mu "太好了！正是我所期望的。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8061
translate zh_hant a3ec2o1_8b5f656b:

    # mu "You know, Hisao, I'm glad you came here. It's always good to have a student who really gets into the subject you teach."
    mu "你知道嗎，久夫，我很高興你來到這裡。能有一個真正投入你所教科目的學生，總是一件好事。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8063
translate zh_hant a3ec2o1_3a84ff1b:

    # mu "In a way, it makes dealing with the rest of the students more tolerable."
    mu "某種程度上，甚至會讓那些其他學生更加……能夠忍受。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8065
translate zh_hant a3ec2o1_f0d69a0c:

    # mu "You're a bright kid, too. You took to this stuff like a duck to water, or some other such simile."
    mu "你也是個聰明的孩子。你學這些東西就像如魚得水，或是，其他類似的比喻。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8067
translate zh_hant a3ec2o1_e7cbd408:

    # hi "Er, thanks."
    hi "呃，謝謝。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8069
translate zh_hant a3ec2o1_e1c8d28c:

    # hi "You were a great help. Especially with that college stuff."
    hi "您幫了我很大的忙。尤其是在升學那些事情上。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8074
translate zh_hant a3ec2o1_3d2fc31a:

    # mu "There's one more thing, Hisao."
    mu "還有一件事，久夫。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8076
translate zh_hant a3ec2o1_aadb7a11:

    # mu "A bit of advice, from one scientist to another."
    mu "一點建議，來自一個科學家給另一個科學家的建議。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8078
translate zh_hant a3ec2o1_111a58e1:

    # hi "What's that?"
    hi "是什麼？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8080
translate zh_hant a3ec2o1_104f1141:

    # mu "What does a scientist do?"
    mu "科學家是做什麼的？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8082
translate zh_hant a3ec2o1_0ccb7eba:

    # hi "Observe the world around him."
    hi "觀察他周遭的世界。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8087
translate zh_hant a3ec2o1_03d49752:

    # mu "Exactly. Good."
    mu "完全正確。很好。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8092
translate zh_hant a3ec2o1_551b9eff:

    # mu "A simple question, but one that most people can't seem to answer. That's the essence of a scientist, Hisao."
    mu "一個簡單的問題，但卻是大多數人似乎無法回答的。這就是科學家的本質，久夫。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8094
translate zh_hant a3ec2o1_977d7c08:

    # mu "We observe what's there, and try to figure it out."
    mu "我們觀察存在的事物，並試圖解開他們周圍的謎團。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8096
translate zh_hant a3ec2o1_c63ab9a8:

    # mu "But what if there's something you can't figure out?"
    mu "但是如果遇到了無法理解的東西呢？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8098
translate zh_hant a3ec2o1_54e4e3d1:

    # mu "What's a scientist to do if he can't observe something?"
    mu "作為一名科學家，如果觀察不到一件東西，應該怎麼辦？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8100
translate zh_hant a3ec2o1_18e46db2:

    # mu "How, for example, can we talk about quarks when nobody has ever actually seen one? Or black holes when observing them directly is impossible?"
    mu "比如說，沒有一個人見過夸克，我們怎麼能討論它呢？或者在根本不可能直接觀察的情況下討論黑洞？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8102
translate zh_hant a3ec2o1_a3264b91:

    # hi "Well, scientific equipment's pretty advanced…"
    hi "嗯，科學儀器很先進……"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8107
translate zh_hant a3ec2o1_aa7ff39c:

    # "Mutou irritably waves away my response."
    "武藤老師不耐煩地揮手打斷了我的回答。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8109
translate zh_hant a3ec2o1_885e0fe7:

    # mu "No, that's not it at all."
    mu "不，完全不是那樣。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8111
translate zh_hant a3ec2o1_4a210c68:

    # mu "Those are tools, I'm trying to give you a philosophy."
    mu "那些是工具，我試著給你的是一種哲理。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8116
translate zh_hant a3ec2o1_3ef87056:

    # mu "Think. If you can't observe something directly, then how can you observe it?"
    mu "好好想想；如果你不能直接觀察一件事物，那麼應該怎麼觀察？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8118
translate zh_hant a3ec2o1_b9b5c963:

    # hi "Uh, guess?"
    hi "呃，猜測？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8120
translate zh_hant a3ec2o1_40c33409:

    # mu "How? How would you guess the movement of a quark? What is your guess based on?"
    mu "怎麼猜？你怎麼猜一個夸克的活動軌跡？你的猜測有什麼根據？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8122
translate zh_hant a3ec2o1_e5f4a4e1:

    # "Of course."
    "原來如此。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8124
translate zh_hant a3ec2o1_d2fd2fa5:

    # "I should have thought of it earlier."
    "我早該想到的。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8126
translate zh_hant a3ec2o1_40fa6360:

    # hi "The things it affects."
    hi "根據它對其他東西產生的影響。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8131
translate zh_hant a3ec2o1_245db389:

    # "Mutou claps his hands together excitedly and whoops."
    "武藤興奮地叫了一聲，並鼓起了掌。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8133
translate zh_hant a3ec2o1_505d9c34:

    # mu "Yes, exactly. Good."
    mu "是的，完全正確。很好。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8135
translate zh_hant a3ec2o1_8a376fc3:

    # mu "Remember that, Hisao."
    mu "記住這點，久夫。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8140
translate zh_hant a3ec2o1_2a7ca04b:

    # mu "If you can't examine something directly, it's because you're looking at it wrong."
    mu "如果你不能直接檢視某樣東西，那是因為你看待它的方式錯了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8142
translate zh_hant a3ec2o1_2e2c8e2f:

    # mu "You have to look at it differently if you want to uncover the truth. And if it eludes you, then look at what it leaves behind."
    mu "如果你想揭開真相，就必須用不同的方式看待它。如果它讓你捉摸不定，那就看看它留下的痕跡。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8144
translate zh_hant a3ec2o1_db89a8d6:

    # mu "That is the essence of being a scientist. We never stop looking for the answer. Never take anything for granted."
    mu "這就是身為科學家的本質。我們從不停止尋找答案。從不把任何事視為理所當然。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8146
translate zh_hant a3ec2o1_5158fddd:

    # mu "Observe, experiment, and observe some more."
    mu "觀察、實驗，然後再多觀察。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8148
translate zh_hant a3ec2o1_c7b6fc13:

    # mu "There's a lot of stuff out there that makes no sense, Hisao. Your job is to get it to make sense."
    mu "外面有很多事情是沒有道理的，久夫。你的工作就是讓它們變得清晰。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8150
translate zh_hant a3ec2o1_df338b28:

    # mu "If nothing else, I hope you've learned that here."
    mu "即使沒有別的東西，我希望你在這裡至少學到了這一點。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8152
translate zh_hant a3ec2o1_ca060dfb:

    # hi "I think I can remember that."
    hi "我會記住的。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8157
translate zh_hant a3ec2o1_d448d0e1:

    # "Mutou smiles, satisfied."
    "武藤露出了滿意的微笑。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8159
translate zh_hant a3ec2o1_9170cc54:

    # mu "Good. Now go enjoy your time off. You've earned it."
    mu "很好。現在去享受你的假期吧。你應得的。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8166
translate zh_hant a3ec2o1_23c758ca:

    # "I leave the room feeling a little confused."
    "我離開房間時，感覺有點困惑。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8168
translate zh_hant a3ec2o1_2a7d631f:

    # "What brought that on?"
    "他怎麼突然說這些？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8170
translate zh_hant a3ec2o1_8d26952d:

    # "Although…"
    "不過……"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8172
translate zh_hant a3ec2o1_4772ef91:

    # "Am I going about this thing with Emi the wrong way?"
    "我處理笑美這件事的方式，是不是錯了？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8174
translate zh_hant a3ec2o1_d7ba5a40:

    # "If she won't tell me, then can I go about it some other way?"
    "如果她不肯告訴我，那我能用其他方法嗎？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8180
translate zh_hant a3ec2o2_d55dd87c:

    # hi "Actually, I've got something I need to do…"
    hi "那個，我其實有點別的事……"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8185
translate zh_hant a3ec2o2_34fbbd33:

    # mu "Yeah? Oh well."
    mu "是嗎？哦，好吧。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8187
translate zh_hant a3ec2o2_8d007dd6:

    # mu "I wanted to get some feedback on the science club from you. But we can do that later, I guess."
    mu "我本來想聽聽你對科學社的一些回饋。但我想我們可以晚點再說。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8189
translate zh_hant a3ec2o2_4ceaf043:

    # mu "Enjoy your break, you hear?"
    mu "好好享受你的假期，聽到了嗎？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8191
translate zh_hant a3ec2o2_c488fa82:

    # hi "Thanks, I will."
    hi "謝謝，我會的。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8193
translate zh_hant a3ec2o2_784c5475:

    # "I'd really love to chat with Mutou, but I've got other things on my mind."
    "我其實很想跟武藤老師聊聊，但我心裡有別的事。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8195
translate zh_hant a3ec2o2_0a4a50c3:

    # "Specifically, what to do about Emi."
    "確切來說，是該怎麼處理笑美的事。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8197
translate zh_hant a3ec2o2_ef154516:

    # "Can I really just confront her?"
    "我真的可以直接去質問她嗎？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8202
translate zh_hant a3ec3o1_e71151dd:

    # "What was it Mutou said yesterday?"
    "武藤老師昨天和我討論了什麼？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8204
translate zh_hant a3ec3o1_8789c9de:

    # "If you can't observe the thing, then observe what's around it?"
    "如果你觀察不到事物本身，那就觀察它周遭的事物？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8206
translate zh_hant a3ec3o1_6b021aa1:

    # "Worth a shot."
    "值得一試。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8208
translate zh_hant a3ec3o1_166a0e2d:

    # "The nurse knows Emi better than I do, I'll wager."
    "我敢打賭，校醫比我更了解笑美。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8210
translate zh_hant a3ec3o1_6a455da5:

    # hi "Sure, I'm open to suggestions."
    hi "好啊，我洗耳恭聽。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8212
translate zh_hant a3ec3o1_477bba36:

    # hi "Honestly, I'm kind of lost."
    hi "老實說，我有點不知所措。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8214
translate zh_hant a3ec3o1_78f76b0c:

    # hi "I've got no idea how to deal with this."
    hi "我完全不知道該怎麼處理這件事。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8219
translate zh_hant a3ec3o1_3811de36:

    # nk "I never would have guessed."
    nk "這還真是出乎我的意料啊！"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8221
translate zh_hant a3ec3o1_cdbe098c:

    # "He grins while he says this. I think he's kidding."
    "他說這話的時候咧嘴一笑。我想他是在開玩笑。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8226
translate zh_hant a3ec3o1_6b1de434:

    # nk "Look, here's the deal: Emi is… stubborn."
    nk "聽著，事情是這樣的：笑美……很固執。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8231
translate zh_hant a3ec3o1_a8943490:

    # nk "You should know that by now, and if you don't then you're pretty unobservant, but I'm giving you the benefit of the doubt here."
    nk "你現在應該知道了，如果你還不知道，那你觀察力也太差了，不過我就姑且相信你不是那樣的人吧。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8233
translate zh_hant a3ec3o1_a1eada82:

    # hi "I'm so grateful."
    hi "真是感激不盡。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8238
translate zh_hant a3ec3o1_16b77770:

    # nk "Anyway, if she's decided that she doesn't want to talk about what happened, then she's not going to talk about what's happened."
    nk "總之，如果她決定不想談論發生的事，那她就絕對不會談。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8240
translate zh_hant a3ec3o1_bfc48be2:

    # nk "Has she said anything about what's been bothering her? Even a hint?"
    nk "她有說過任何關於困擾她的事嗎？就算只是一點暗示也好？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8242
translate zh_hant a3ec3o1_0bc45ea7:

    # hi "Well, she did say she'd been having nightmares about the accident…"
    hi "嗯，她確實說過她一直做關於那場意外的惡夢……"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8247
translate zh_hant a3ec3o1_4a03fcd2:

    # nk "Really? You're making progress, then. That's good."
    nk "真的？那你有進展了嘛。不錯。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8252
translate zh_hant a3ec3o1_ffabed58:

    # nk "Well, I guess I can fill you in on this without violating my strict non-interference policy when it comes to Emi making stupid decisions."
    nk "我想，透漏一些資訊給你，應該不算違反我那條『笑美做蠢事時絕不插手』的嚴格原則。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8257
translate zh_hant a3ec3o1_018c58a8:

    # nk "The anniversary of her accident is coming up soon."
    nk "那場意外的週年紀念日快到了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8259
translate zh_hant a3ec3o1_3308ccdc:

    # nk "She gets depressed around this time, because it was a pretty traumatic event, considering what she lost."
    nk "每年這時候她都會有些抑鬱寡歡，因為畢竟失去了那麼多，留下了很嚴重的精神創傷吧。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8261
translate zh_hant a3ec3o1_be2d9336:

    # hi "That's the other thing. She acted like she lost more than just her legs. What happened?"
    hi "就是這個。從她的表現來看，似乎不止是失去了雙腿吧？究竟發生了什麼？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8266
translate zh_hant a3ec3o1_2829c4ee:

    # nk "Whoa! Nope, not going there. You'll have to ask someone else about that, because that's a whole can of worms I'm not about to open."
    nk "咳咳！停停停，無可奉告。這可是個我絕對不想打開的潘多拉魔盒。想知道的話，你得另尋高明瞭。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8271
translate zh_hant a3ec3o1_a9d99ce6:

    # nk "If Emi wants you to know, she'll tell you in her own time."
    nk "如果笑美想讓你知道，她會在她自己的時機告訴你。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8273
translate zh_hant a3ec3o1_129e0d70:

    # nk "You've just got to be patient, that's all."
    nk "你只需要有耐心，就這樣。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8275
translate zh_hant a3ec3o1_9f28c1e1:

    # hi "Why are you even helping me with all this?"
    hi "你為什麼要幫我這麼多？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8280
translate zh_hant a3ec3o1_7c13bfdd:

    # nk "Because you're good for her. She trusts you, even if you don't think she does."
    nk "因為你對她很重要。儘管你可能不這麼認為，她其實是信任你的。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8282
translate zh_hant a3ec3o1_457066f1:

    # nk "And you've got the best chance out of anyone at this school right now to help her through this time of year."
    nk "而且現在在這所學校裡，你是最有機會幫助她度過這段時間的人。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8287
translate zh_hant a3ec3o1_13ecab05:

    # nk "She won't accept my help, but she might accept yours if you don't screw it up."
    nk "我的幫助，她是不會接受的。但是你；如果你不把一切搞砸的話，你的幫助，也許她會接受的。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8292
translate zh_hant a3ec3o1_eae33d34:

    # nk "So don't screw it up, got it?"
    nk "所以說，不要搞砸了哦。聽見了嗎？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8298
translate zh_hant a3ec3o2_0ad0a7b4:

    # "Advice? About what? I don't think there's anything I can actually do about this."
    "建議？關於什麼？我不覺得我能做些什麼。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8300
translate zh_hant a3ec3o2_6983fb7e:

    # hi "Not really. I don't think there's anything you can say that'll help."
    hi "還是算了。我不覺得你能給什麼有幫助的建議。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8305
translate zh_hant a3ec3o2_8f596860:

    # nk "You never know, Hisao."
    nk "很難說喔，久夫。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8307
translate zh_hant a3ec3o2_e835aaf7:

    # hi "No, I think I've got a pretty good idea."
    hi "不，我想我心裡有數。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8309
translate zh_hant a3ec3o2_2267ef90:

    # hi "Emi's just being stubborn about some things, and it's bothering me, but I'll get over it."
    hi "笑美只是對某些事情很固執，這讓我很困擾，但我會處理好的。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8311
translate zh_hant a3ec3o2_6f38490c:

    # hi "Don't worry about us."
    hi "不用擔心我們。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8316
translate zh_hant a3ec3o2_f81ce9ca:

    # "The nurse doesn't seem to believe me, but shrugs."
    "校醫似乎不相信我，但還是聳了聳肩。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8318
translate zh_hant a3ec3o2_70b7ddfe:

    # nk "Have it your way, kiddo."
    nk "隨便你啦，小子。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8323
translate zh_hant a3ec4o1_9c8e11d3:

    # "The only way to find out is to go to the source. And the source is currently pretending that she has to use the toilet."
    "想找出答案只有一個辦法：直搗黃龍。而那個黃龍目前正假裝要去上廁所。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8328
translate zh_hant a3ec4o1_bd114144:

    # "I excuse myself politely from the table and head that way, only to catch sight of Emi not in the bathroom, but in the kitchen just next to the living room."
    "我禮貌地向餐桌告辭，朝那個方向走去，結果發現笑美並不在廁所，而是在客廳旁的廚房裡。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8333
translate zh_hant a3ec4o1_fd855342:

    # "Emi's left the door open, and as I approach I can see that she's holding on to the table in an attempt to compose herself, an effort that fails as soon as I open my mouth."
    "笑美沒關門，我走近時，可以看到她正抓著桌子，試圖讓自己冷靜下來，但就在我開口的那一刻，她的努力就失敗了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8335
translate zh_hant a3ec4o1_063abe3d:

    # hi "Doesn't look like nature's call was that urgent."
    hi "看來妳也不是那麼急著上廁所嘛。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8340
translate zh_hant a3ec4o1_c23081e8:

    # "Emi jumps and glares at me."
    "笑美嚇了一跳，轉過身來瞪著我。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8345
translate zh_hant a3ec4o1_40cdd248:

    # emi "What are you doing here? I didn't come here to be with other people."
    emi "你來這裡做什麼？我不是為了跟別人聊天才過來的。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8347
translate zh_hant a3ec4o1_841169a6:

    # hi "I just wanted to help you. You looked pretty rattled."
    hi "我只是想幫妳。妳看起來有點心神不寧。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8352
translate zh_hant a3ec4o1_a3712d14:

    # emi "I said it was nothing, didn't I? And besides, I thought we'd established that you can't help me."
    emi "我說了沒事，不是嗎？而且，我以為我們已經說好了，你幫不了我。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8354
translate zh_hant a3ec4o1_8059de66:

    # hi "No, we've established that you're stubborn."
    hi "不，我們說好的是妳很固執。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8359
translate zh_hant a3ec4o1_d8295499:

    # emi "Look who's talking. The guy who followed me."
    emi "還真是諷刺啊，被你這種不知好歹跟蹤我的人這麼說。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8361
translate zh_hant a3ec4o1_e2bda517:

    # hi "This is different! I want to help you with… whatever this is."
    hi "這不一樣！我想幫妳……不管妳是為了什麼事。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8366
translate zh_hant a3ec4o1_8b313be2:

    # emi "Funny, because {b}I{/b} just want you to leave me alone."
    emi "笑死人了。{b}我{/b}似乎只想讓你離我遠些。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8368
translate zh_hant a3ec4o1_cd150340:

    # hi "But why? Why can't you just trust me?"
    hi "可是為什麼？為什麼妳就是不能相信我？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8373
translate zh_hant a3ec4o1_7bf3a941:

    # emi "We've been over this already, Hisao. I've got to deal with this stuff on my own."
    emi "我們已經談過這件事了，久夫。這些事我必須自己處理。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8375
translate zh_hant a3ec4o1_a2825f8f:

    # hi "I won't accept that! You need my help, you just won't take it!"
    hi "我不能接受！妳需要我的幫助，妳只是不肯接受！"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8377
translate zh_hant a3ec4o1_141187e6:

    # "My wording seems to have been a little off."
    "我的用詞似乎有點不對勁。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8382
translate zh_hant a3ec4o1_f89785b9:

    # emi "Need? I {b}need{/b} your help?"
    emi "需要？我{b}需要{/b}你的幫助？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8389
translate zh_hant a3ec4o1_2a92923b:

    # emi "Well, it's a good thing we met, isn't it? Because otherwise I guess I'd just be a broken human being, wouldn't I?"
    emi "哎呀，還好我們遇見了，對吧？不然我想我大概就只會是個破碎不堪的人，不是嗎？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8391
translate zh_hant a3ec4o1_b821520c:

    # emi "No, it's a damn good thing that Hisao came along to save the day, isn't it? Because God knows I can't save myself, can I?"
    emi "不不不，有久夫來拯救世界，真是太幸運了，不是嗎？天知道，我自只是個懦弱的可憐蟲，嗯？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8393
translate zh_hant a3ec4o1_064143eb:

    # emi "I'm just the poor, emotionally damaged girl with no legs, right?"
    emi "我不過是個可憐、心靈受創、沒有腿的女孩，對吧？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8395
translate zh_hant a3ec4o1_643f4798:

    # hi "Emi, you know I don't think that—"
    hi "笑美，妳知道我不是那麼想的——"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8400
translate zh_hant a3ec4o1_5beb76b0:

    # emi "Really? Because if you thought differently then I don't think you'd be here, saying I need your help."
    emi "真的嗎？因為如果你不是這麼想，我想你就不會在這裡，說我需要你的幫助了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8402
translate zh_hant a3ec4o1_607b466f:

    # emi "I've gotten pretty far in life as a normal human being without you."
    emi "在沒有你的情況下，我作為一個正常人也過得很好。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8404
translate zh_hant a3ec4o1_35f86601:

    # hi "So what, nothing we've shared was important? I'm just the guy who hangs out with you?"
    hi "所以呢，我們共享的一切都不重要了？我只是個跟妳混在一起的傢伙？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8409
translate zh_hant a3ec4o1_596a9d5e:

    # emi "You're my boyfriend, Hisao, not my savior."
    emi "你是我的男朋友，久夫，不是我的救世主。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8411
translate zh_hant a3ec4o1_d33eb32b:

    # hi "Well no, that much is obvious. You won't even consider that I could be a help to you, will you?"
    hi "嗯，這點很明顯。妳根本不會考慮我能幫上妳，對吧？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8413
translate zh_hant a3ec4o1_f51c5f34:

    # hi "You'll just bottle it all up and hope that a run will solve your problems, or you'll come visit me and we'll fool around until you feel better."
    hi "妳只會把一切都悶在心裡，希望跑跑步就能解決問題，或者來找我廝混一下，直到妳心情好轉。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8415
translate zh_hant a3ec4o1_a3639338:

    # hi "That's not being a healthy human being, Emi. That's not what a relationship means."
    hi "那不是一個健康的人該有的樣子，笑美。那不是一段關係該有的樣子。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8420
translate zh_hant a3ec4o1_2d24456b:

    # emi "Well it's what it means to me right now, Hisao."
    emi "可是這就是它現在對我的意義，久夫。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8425
translate zh_hant a3ec4o1_703adbc5:

    # emi "I wish—"
    emi "我希望——"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8427
translate zh_hant a3ec4o1_7536b546:

    # "She seems to reconsider her words just then. A flicker of pain, of doubt on her face. For a moment I think she's about to cry."
    "她似乎在那一刻重新考慮了自己的話。一絲痛苦、一絲懷疑閃過她的臉。有那麼一瞬間，我以為她快哭了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8432
translate zh_hant a3ec4o1_35bbac76:

    # "But the moment passes, and now she's composed herself again. Whatever that wish was will have to go unspoken."
    "但那一刻過去了，她又重新鎮定了下來。無論那個願望是什麼，都只能深埋心底了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8434
translate zh_hant a3ec4o1_3c511ab7:

    # emi "Look, I just… I can't do this right now."
    emi "聽著，我只是……我現在沒辦法這樣。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8436
translate zh_hant a3ec4o1_885fb58f:

    # hi "What, have a serious conversation? Be open? Be honest? Give a damn about anyone besides yourself and your problems?"
    hi "怎樣？認真地談一談？敞開心扉？誠實一點？除了妳自己和妳的問題之外，也關心一下別人？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8441
translate zh_hant a3ec4o1_3682b830:

    # emi "What do you know about my problems? Nothing! You don't know what I've been through, so don't pretend that you do."
    emi "你懂我的問題嗎？什麼都不懂！你根本不知道我經歷了什麼，所以別假裝你知道。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8443
translate zh_hant a3ec4o1_20eb2ac1:

    # hi "I know you have nightmares, and I know your father's gone. What happened to him?"
    hi "我知道妳會做惡夢，也知道妳父親不在了。他發生了什麼事？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8448
translate zh_hant a3ec4o1_004c29b3:

    # "Emi's head jerks backwards as if I've just slapped her. That brittle quality has gotten back into her voice."
    "笑美猛地抬頭，就像是我打了她一個耳光。她的聲音再一次變得生硬冷漠。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8453
translate zh_hant a3ec4o1_5fe96675:

    # emi "That's enough."
    emi "夠了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8455
translate zh_hant a3ec4o1_a5c070fe:

    # "This is stupid. This whole conversation has just been variations on Emi stonewalling me."
    "的確夠了。這整個對話就是笑美用各種方法逃避我的問題。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8457
translate zh_hant a3ec4o1_45c759d0:

    # hi "What, you won't even answer that question? Fine, keep your secrets. They can lie in the grave as far as I'm concerned."
    hi "怎麼，妳連這個問題都不回答？好啊，守著妳的秘密吧。對我來說，那些秘密跟妳一起進墳墓都沒差。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8462
translate zh_hant a3ec4o1_0e1c2080:

    # "Emi's eyes widen in shock. When she speaks again, it's in a voice that is low, dangerous."
    "笑美震驚地睜大了眼睛。當她再次開口時，聲音低沉而危險。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8467
translate zh_hant a3ec4o1_ee2abcaf:

    # emi "Get out of my house, Hisao."
    emi "從我家滾出去，久夫。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8469
translate zh_hant a3ec4o1_3fceda3a:

    # "The sudden change in her tone snaps me out of my self-righteous anger and makes me realize with a dawning horror what I've just said."
    "她語氣的突然轉變，讓我從自以為是的憤怒中驚醒，並帶著一股逐漸升起的恐懼，意識到我剛才說了什麼。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8471
translate zh_hant a3ec4o1_e2c54dc9:

    # hi "Emi, I didn't mean—"
    hi "笑美，我不是那個意思——"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8478
translate zh_hant a3ec4o1_f1dab570:

    # emi "I said {b}go{/b}, Hisao."
    emi "我說了，久夫，{b}滾{/b}。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8480
translate zh_hant a3ec4o1_014eb49f:

    # emi "Tell my mother that she cooked a wonderful meal but you've forgotten a prior engagement, and get out of my house."
    emi "告訴我媽，她煮了一頓很棒的晚餐，但你忘了之前有約，然後滾出我家。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8482
translate zh_hant a3ec4o1_de7dd83b:

    # "She's trembling now, shaking with anger, or sadness, or determination. Her voice is still low, controlled. Almost a growl."
    "她現在顫抖著，因憤怒、悲傷或決心而發抖。她的聲音依舊低沉、克制。幾乎像一種低吼。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8484
translate zh_hant a3ec4o1_00b9d2d6:

    # "I reach out to put an arm on her shoulder, to apologize for going too far, but she jerks away from my touch."
    "我伸出手想搭上她的肩膀，為自己太過分而道歉，但她猛地甩開我的觸碰。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8489
translate zh_hant a3ec4o1_fddca906:

    # emi "Get out."
    emi "滾。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8495
translate zh_hant a3ec4o1_f4a4531a:

    # "What can I do? I walk out of the kitchen and go to the living room, make my apology to Mrs. Ibarazaki, and let myself out."
    "我還能做什麼？我走出廚房，回到客廳，向茨崎太太道歉，然後自己走了出去。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8503
translate zh_hant a3ec4o2_aee4b1dd:

    # "There's an awkward silence at the table for a while after Emi dashes off. I can't think of anything to say."
    "笑美衝出去後，餐桌上陷入了一陣尷尬的沉默。我想不出任何話可說。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8508
translate zh_hant a3ec4o2_3daf3f05:

    # "Emi's mother sighs, breaking the silence."
    "笑美的媽媽嘆了口氣，打破了沉默。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8512
translate zh_hant a3ec4o2_e99f1509:

    # emm "Sorry about that, Hisao. I sometimes forget that Emi's touchy about certain subjects."
    emm "真抱歉，久夫。我有時候會忘了笑美對某些話題很敏感。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8514
translate zh_hant a3ec4o2_ec5ad9cd:

    # emm "And I was talking about the wheelchair thing, too…"
    emm "而且我還提了輪椅的事……"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8516
translate zh_hant a3ec4o2_a7505259:

    # hi "Should I go after her?"
    hi "我該去追她嗎？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8521
translate zh_hant a3ec4o2_01c8973d:

    # emm "Heavens no! She didn't leave the table to continue the conversation, you know."
    emm "天啊，千萬不要！她離開餐桌可不是為了繼續這個話題。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8523
translate zh_hant a3ec4o2_ee16b503:

    # hi "But if she's troubled, shouldn't someone help her?"
    hi "可是如果她很困擾，不該有人去幫她嗎？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8528
translate zh_hant a3ec4o2_972cf9cc:

    # emm "If it were anyone else, I'd say yes. But my daughter is stubborn as a mule, and if she wants to be alone it's best to let her be alone."
    emm "如果是其他人，我會說對。但我女兒跟驢子一樣固執，如果她想一個人靜一靜，最好就讓她一個人。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8530
translate zh_hant a3ec4o2_d50e7c78:

    # emm "Otherwise she'll probably say something she'd regret, which would cause you to say something you'd regret, and I would prefer that dinner doesn't end with one or the both of you storming out of the house."
    emm "不然她可能會說出一些會後悔的話，然後你也會說出一些你會後悔的話，我可不希望這頓晚餐以你們其中一人或兩個人都氣沖沖地離開收場。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8535
translate zh_hant a3ec4o2_43dce610:

    # emm "If that were to happen I'd be a terrible hostess, wouldn't I? I've already acted as a fool once today."
    emm "如果果真如此的話，我這個主人豈不是太失職了？我今天已經出過一次醜了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8537
translate zh_hant a3ec4o2_62945f2b:

    # hi "That's okay, I shouldn't have brought up the wheelchair, apparently."
    hi "沒關係的。我顯然不應該提到輪椅的事。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8542
translate zh_hant a3ec4o2_3fd4b53f:

    # "Mrs. Ibarazaki frowns, clearly more bothered by Emi's omission than she'd let on."
    "茨崎夫人皺起了眉頭。看來，笑美對此的緘口不提，使她母親比所表現出的要更為擔心。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8544
translate zh_hant a3ec4o2_7269a38c:

    # emm "I wish she wouldn't do that. It just makes me worry more, you know."
    emm "真希望她不要這樣。這只會讓我更擔心。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8546
translate zh_hant a3ec4o2_c345fa10:

    # hi "She does this often?"
    hi "她常常這樣嗎？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8551
translate zh_hant a3ec4o2_cc665604:

    # emm "What, running off to the bathroom? No, I can't say she does. Keep injuries from her mother, though? Well, that's a little more common."
    emm "什麼，突然跑去廁所嗎？倒是不怎麼經常。向她的母親隱藏傷痛？這就更常見些了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8553
translate zh_hant a3ec4o2_92c2e2ff:

    # emm "Every time I catch her lying like that, she assures me that the only reason she didn't tell me is because it wasn't a big deal."
    emm "每次我發現她像這樣撒謊，她就向我保證，她不告訴我只不過是因為不值一提罷了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8555
translate zh_hant a3ec4o2_40ec6131:

    # hi "If it's any consolation, I'm sure the only reason I knew about it at all was because I saw her every day."
    hi "請寬心……如果不是我每天都和她在一起，我根本什麼都不可能知道。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8560
translate zh_hant a3ec4o2_52c85904:

    # "This elicits a dry chuckle from across the table. Mrs. Ibarazaki sighs, a little sadly."
    "我的話引起了桌子對面的一陣乾笑。茨崎夫人有些傷感地嘆了口氣。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8565
translate zh_hant a3ec4o2_2ed81d0a:

    # emm "Still hesitant about getting close to people, huh? I keep hoping that she'll get over that."
    emm "她還是不願意親近別人，嗯？我一直希望她能克服這一關的。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8567
translate zh_hant a3ec4o2_9133b5d6:

    # emm "It's funny, really. She's bounced back so well from the accident in so many ways…"
    emm "說起來真是滑稽。自從那次事故，她明明已經恢復了那麼多……"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8572
translate zh_hant a3ec4o2_f50f0e74:

    # emm "I guess some things never really go away."
    emm "也許有些傷痕真的是永遠不會痊癒的。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8574
translate zh_hant a3ec4o2_af914936:

    # "From the looks of it, the whole thing still bothers her, too."
    "看來，這整個事件也同樣在煩擾著她。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8576
translate zh_hant a3ec4o2_1581ba11:

    # "She seems to be a little more willing to talk about the accident without Emi around, though."
    "不過，笑美不在身邊時，她似乎對於那次事故更為坦率一些。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8578
translate zh_hant a3ec4o2_a4fc3a64:

    # hi "Hey, I've got a question, if it's all right."
    hi "呃，我有個問題，不知道該不該問。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8583
translate zh_hant a3ec4o2_dc0216ca:

    # emm "Oh?"
    emm "嗯？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8585
translate zh_hant a3ec4o2_2325f9bd:

    # hi "What else did Emi lose in that accident? The nurse said that she gets this way near the anniversary, and she won't talk about it to me…"
    hi "那次意外，笑美還失去了什麼嗎？校醫說，每年這個時候她都這個樣子，而她自己又不願意對我說……"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8590
translate zh_hant a3ec4o2_064e74d8:

    # emm "So you thought I'd fill you in, hmm?"
    emm "所以你覺得我會告訴你，嗯？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8592
translate zh_hant a3ec4o2_d3f362db:

    # hi "Er, yeah. Hopefully."
    hi "呃，對。希望是這樣。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8597
translate zh_hant a3ec4o2_94a84261:

    # emm "Well, there's a problem with that request, you know."
    emm "啊哈哈，要滿足這個請求，有一個小問題。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8599
translate zh_hant a3ec4o2_b776a7b1:

    # hi "Let me guess: you promised Emi that you wouldn't tell anyone she didn't want to know, and you don't know if she wants me to know?"
    hi "讓我猜猜：妳答應過笑美，不會告訴任何她不想讓別人知道的人，而妳不確定她想不想讓我知道？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8601
translate zh_hant a3ec4o2_c0546718:

    # emm "Something like that. I promised Emi that she'd be the one to tell people the full story."
    emm "差不多是這樣。我答應過笑美，要由她自己來告訴別人完整的故事。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8603
translate zh_hant a3ec4o2_74cd4844:

    # hi "But isn't that important? I mean, it's clearly had a huge effect on her if she's still like this so long after the accident happened."
    hi "但那不是很重要嗎？我的意思是，如果意外發生這麼久了她還是這樣，那顯然對她有很大的影響。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8608
translate zh_hant a3ec4o2_fbc04b16:

    # emm "That's true. It did have a long-lasting effect on her. There are a few things that she'll probably never really get over."
    emm "沒錯。那確實對她有長遠的影響。有些事她可能永遠都無法真正釋懷。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8610
translate zh_hant a3ec4o2_18a090c5:

    # "For a moment Mrs. Ibarazaki looks incredibly saddened, as if an old wound is bothering her."
    "在那一刻，茨崎夫人看起來無以倫比地悲傷，彷彿一道舊傷又在困擾著她。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8612
translate zh_hant a3ec4o2_ac46f44e:

    # emm "I suppose there are a few things I'll never really get over either…"
    emm "我想，有些事，我也永遠無法真正釋懷……"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8617
translate zh_hant a3ec4o2_ec9f3444:

    # "Another dry chuckle, and with a shake of her head Emi's mother banishes the memory."
    "又一陣壓抑的乾笑。笑美的母親用力搖了搖頭，驅走了腦海裡的記憶。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8622
translate zh_hant a3ec4o2_1b682c1a:

    # emm "Look, there's something you absolutely must understand about the way Emi thinks about the accident."
    emm "聽著，關於笑美如何看待那場意外，有一件事你絕對必須了解。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8624
translate zh_hant a3ec4o2_111a58e1:

    # hi "What's that?"
    hi "那是什麼？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8626
translate zh_hant a3ec4o2_e48c0f85:

    # emm "It wasn't a big deal."
    emm "那不是什麼大事。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8630
translate zh_hant a3ec4o2_a2c89b3d:

    # "Somehow I manage to keep my mouth from falling open in surprise, but it takes some effort."
    "我目瞪口呆，差點沒有吃驚地張大嘴巴。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8632
translate zh_hant a3ec4o2_52d1fd73:

    # "That has to be the most ridiculous thing I've ever heard."
    "這一定是我聽過最荒謬的事了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8634
translate zh_hant a3ec4o2_37f63bc4:

    # hi "I beg your pardon?"
    hi "夫人，請問……？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8641
translate zh_hant a3ec4o2_a97675aa:

    # emm "Okay, maybe it's not that simple, but it's a pretty accurate summation. Emi believes that the accident did not define her, and that everything she lost that day didn't define her either."
    emm "好吧好吧，也許並不這麼簡單，但這還算是個很精準的總結吧。笑美拒絕讓那次意外定義自己的人生，也拒絕讓她在那天所失去的一切定義她的人生。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8643
translate zh_hant a3ec4o2_1f6f00a2:

    # emm "She's not 'that girl who lost her legs,' she's 'The Fastest Thing on No Legs.' Her optimism and energy came out of that wreck without a scratch, as far as she's concerned."
    emm "她不是『那個失去雙腿的女孩』，她是『沒有腿但跑得最快的人』。對她來說，她的樂觀和活力在那場災難中毫髮無傷。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8645
translate zh_hant a3ec4o2_d19923cb:

    # hi "Yet it goes beyond that, doesn't it? I mean, last night she told me that she refused to rely on me because it would make losing me too painful."
    hi "但不僅如此，不是嗎？我的意思是，昨晚她告訴我，她不願意依賴我，因為那樣失去我的時候會太痛苦。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8650
translate zh_hant a3ec4o2_cf578c14:

    # emm "Not really. You said she won't tell you about the accident, even though you've asked her about it before."
    emm "不完全是。你說過，即使你以前問過她，她還是不肯告訴你關於意外的事。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8652
translate zh_hant a3ec4o2_7e01cfe0:

    # emm "The reason she won't talk about it when you ask is because to her it's not something you absolutely need to know. Even if she wasn't terrified of getting too close to anyone, she still wouldn't talk about it."
    emm "她不願意談論的原因是，對她來說，那不是你非知道不可的事。即使她不害怕與人太親近，她還是不會談論這件事。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8654
translate zh_hant a3ec4o2_022419ee:

    # hi "She's afraid of being close to me?"
    hi "她害怕跟我親近？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8659
translate zh_hant a3ec4o2_ec33e884:

    # emm "Oh goodness me, yes. For all that talk about being unscathed by the accident, she's gained the ugly knowledge of how quickly it can all be over."
    emm "哦，天啊，是的。儘管她說自己沒有被意外所傷，但她卻醜陋地體會到，一切可以多快就結束。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8664
translate zh_hant a3ec4o2_eae2b4c6:

    # emm "So she's not going to let people get especially close to her, and she certainly would resent any implication that she cannot work through this on her own."
    emm "所以她不會讓別人特別親近她，而且她肯定會討厭任何暗示她無法獨自解決這件事的說法。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8666
translate zh_hant a3ec4o2_10c41f3d:

    # hi "But I don't think she {b}can{/b}."
    hi "但我不認為她{b}可以{/b}。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8671
translate zh_hant a3ec4o2_60f7a665:

    # emm "Oh no? Are you sure you've been dating my daughter and not somebody else? Trust me Hisao, she could get through it on her own."
    emm "哦，是嗎？你確定你交往的是我女兒，而不是別人？相信我，久夫，她可以自己度過難關的。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8673
translate zh_hant a3ec4o2_74778278:

    # hi "But she has nightmares, and can't sleep well, and—"
    hi "但是她會做惡夢，睡不好，而且——"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8678
translate zh_hant a3ec4o2_bbd69266:

    # emm "And she does this every year. Tell me, if she wasn't able to get through it on her own, do you really think she'd still be alive? She would've killed herself, or something equally melodramatic."
    emm "她每年都會經歷這事。告訴我，如果她無法自己度過，你真的認為她還能好好地活著嗎？她早就自殺了，或做些同樣戲劇化的事了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8680
translate zh_hant a3ec4o2_e508959d:

    # hi "So what, I shouldn't try to help her?"
    hi "所以呢，我不該試著幫她？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8685
translate zh_hant a3ec4o2_33cc99a7:

    # emm "I didn't say that! I hate seeing my daughter like this, and knowing that she could rely on someone else would let me relax."
    emm "我可沒這麼說！我也不想看到自己的女兒這樣。要是能夠知道她可以依靠別人，我也能放下心來。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8687
translate zh_hant a3ec4o2_a1eff8b4:

    # emm "You just need to understand that accepting help goes against everything Emi thinks about herself and the way the world works."
    emm "你只需要明白，接受幫助違背了笑美對自己以及世界運作方式的所有看法。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8689
translate zh_hant a3ec4o2_81d0f696:

    # emm "If you still want to offer her help, then I guess that's your call. Honestly, I'd like you to, but it'd be silly not to warn you that it's not going to be easy."
    emm "如果你還想幫助她，那我想這就是你的決定了。老實說，我希望你這麼做，但不得不警告你：這並不容易。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8694
translate zh_hant a3ec4o2_910ed9da:

    # emm "You just need to be patient with her. She's already closer to you than anyone else she's ever met at Yamaku."
    emm "你需要耐心。比起她在山久認識的任何其他人，你已經是與她關係最密切的一個了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8696
translate zh_hant a3ec4o2_53de06fc:

    # hi "Well it sure doesn't feel like we're very close."
    hi "嗯，我可不覺得我們有那麼親近啊。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8707
translate zh_hant a3ec4o2_e09d0b46:

    # emi "Good, that makes this part easier."
    emi "很好，那接下來就簡單多了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8709
translate zh_hant a3ec4o2_87b7328c:

    # "Emi's voice nearly gives me a heart attack."
    "笑美的聲音差點讓我心臟病發。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8711
translate zh_hant a3ec4o2_86253193:

    # hi "Whoa! Didn't hear you come back, Emi."
    hi "哇！沒聽到妳回來啊，笑美。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8716
translate zh_hant a3ec4o2_d5e6a6d9:

    # emi "How convenient."
    emi "真方便，不是嗎？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8718
translate zh_hant a3ec4o2_a5d9aa0b:

    # hi "Wait, were you eavesdropping?"
    hi "等等，妳在偷聽？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8723
translate zh_hant a3ec4o2_4f26dba0:

    # emi "Nope. Just happened to come back at the right moment, I guess."
    emi "沒有啊。我想，只是剛好在對的時間回來罷了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8728
translate zh_hant a3ec4o2_3ea115ef:

    # emm "Emi, Hisao was just—"
    emm "笑美，久夫只是——"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8730
translate zh_hant a3ec4o2_d2ac4696:

    # "Emi holds up a finger, cutting her mother off."
    "笑美舉起一根手指，打斷了她媽媽的話。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8735
translate zh_hant a3ec4o2_b0b14af5:

    # emi "On his way out of the house? Yeah, I know."
    emi "……準備離開？我知道的。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8737
translate zh_hant a3ec4o2_f9987016:

    # "Emi's trembling with anger now, looking vaguely betrayed."
    "笑美現在氣得發抖，看起來隱約有種被背叛的感覺。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8739
translate zh_hant a3ec4o2_554adec7:

    # emm "Emi, don't be ridiculous, we were just—"
    emm "笑美，別胡鬧了，我們只是——"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8744
translate zh_hant a3ec4o2_28bf991a:

    # emi "You {b}promised{/b}!"
    emi "妳{b}答應過{/b}的！"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8748
translate zh_hant a3ec4o2_c92ee310:

    # "The pain carried in that last word is almost too much for me to bear. The idea that I could hurt her that much is like being kicked in the gut."
    "那話裡承載的痛苦，幾乎讓我無法承受。我竟然能如此傷害她，這個念頭就像被人狠狠踹了一腳肚子。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8750
translate zh_hant a3ec4o2_11af2e0e:

    # "Emi's mother looks similarly pained by the thought."
    "笑美的母親看起來為此同樣地痛苦。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8752
translate zh_hant a3ec4o2_4d083dbc:

    # emm "And I kept that promise! Just listen, there's no reason to go throwing people out of the house."
    emm "我遵守了那個承諾！給我聽好，妳沒有任何理由把任何人踢出這間房子。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8754
translate zh_hant a3ec4o2_5697cbac:

    # "Emi's mother seems to be both angry at her daughter's outburst and embarrassed that I'm a witness to it."
    "笑美的媽媽似乎既對女兒的爆發感到生氣，又為我目睹了這一切而感到尷尬。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8756
translate zh_hant a3ec4o2_439acdd9:

    # "There's only one real solution to this problem, I think."
    "我想，這個問題只有一個真正的解決辦法。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8758
translate zh_hant a3ec4o2_5b4d6d74:

    # hi "It's okay. I'll go."
    hi "沒關係的，我先走了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8760
translate zh_hant a3ec4o2_17fa4223:

    # emm "Now really, that seems a little unnecessary…"
    emm "別這樣，這真的有點太小題大作了……"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8762
translate zh_hant a3ec4o2_ccbebf78:

    # hi "Don't worry about it. Thank you for dinner, Mrs. Ibarazaki, and for the advice."
    hi "別擔心。謝謝妳的晚餐，茨崎太太，還有妳的建議。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8767
translate zh_hant a3ec4o2_8682b0fe:

    # emm "It was my pleasure, Hisao. I'm sorry we didn't get to the dessert."
    emm "這是我的榮幸，久夫。很抱歉我們沒能吃到甜點。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8769
translate zh_hant a3ec4o2_67cb332d:

    # hi "That's okay. I have to watch what I eat anyway."
    hi "沒關係。反正我也得注意飲食。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8771
translate zh_hant a3ec4o2_21bc2e04:

    # hi "Good evening, Emi, Mrs. Ibarazaki."
    hi "晚安，笑美，茨崎太太。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8773
translate zh_hant a3ec4o2_0fe5cb19:

    # "The formality of our conversation, coupled with the fact that I'm getting ready to leave, seems to snap Emi out of her anger."
    "我們對話的客套，加上我準備離開的事實，似乎讓笑美從憤怒中驚醒。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8778
translate zh_hant a3ec4o2_ec363ccd:

    # emi "No, wait. I'm sorry, I've been so… and after last night I just thought… You don't have to go, I take it back, it's okay—"
    emi "不，等等。對不起，我一直都……而且昨晚之後我只是以為……你不用走的，我收回，沒關係——"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8780
translate zh_hant a3ec4o2_d91e162f:

    # "I can't help but smile slightly. She can barely articulate her apology, and I really would like to stay…"
    "我忍不住微微一笑。她幾乎無法清楚地表達歉意，而我真的很想留下……"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8782
translate zh_hant a3ec4o2_f8aba906:

    # "But I don't think I can, right now. I need to think about what her mother said, and about what I'm going to do about us."
    "但我不能這麼做。我需要消化她母親剛才所說的話，也要考慮我該如何面對我們的未來。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8784
translate zh_hant a3ec4o2_889f8b03:

    # "I don't want to risk accidentally getting Emi angry again in her current state, either."
    "我也不想再不小心惹笑美生氣，尤其是在她情緒如此不穩定的情況下……"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8786
translate zh_hant a3ec4o2_be06c1c8:

    # hi "No, I think I'd better leave. You seem pretty shook up, and, well, I'd only wind up trying to help you again. I know you'd prefer I didn't, so I'm going to leave instead."
    hi "不，我想我最好還是先走吧。妳看起來很激動，而且，嗯，我只會又想幫妳。我知道妳不希望我這樣，所以我還是先離開了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8791
translate zh_hant a3ec4o2_1fba2c13:

    # emi "But—"
    emi "可是——"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8793
translate zh_hant a3ec4o2_a17d550f:

    # hi "Hey, it's not a problem. You don't want a knight on a white charger, right? Just promise me one thing, okay?"
    hi "嘿，沒關係的。妳也說過，妳不想要個白馬王子的，不是嗎？只是答應我一件事，可以嗎？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8798
translate zh_hant a3ec4o2_cf45f9a1:

    # emi "What?"
    emi "什麼？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8800
translate zh_hant a3ec4o2_448fc66c:

    # hi "Don't be angry at your mom, okay? She was just giving me some advice, that's all."
    hi "別生妳媽媽的氣，好嗎？她只是給我一些建議，就這樣。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8805
translate zh_hant a3ec4o2_639f61bf:

    # "Emi nods, hesitantly, like this simple idea is all that she can grab on to at this point. She's so terribly off-balance, but I can't do anything about that right now."
    "笑美猶豫地點了點頭，彷彿在這個時候，這個簡單的想法是她唯一能抓住的東西。她非常地心神不寧，但我現在對此無能為力。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8807
translate zh_hant a3ec4o2_c3d21b44:

    # emi "Okay."
    emi "好。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8809
translate zh_hant a3ec4o2_9c103bef:

    # hi "See you tomorrow, okay? Running in the morning. Don't forget!"
    hi "明天見，好嗎？早上跑步。別忘了！"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8811
translate zh_hant a3ec4o2_15ca8316:

    # "I can see that I've hurt Emi by deciding to leave. But there's nothing I can do for her as things stand, and I know that she's too stubborn to admit that she wants me to stick around."
    "我看得出我決定離開傷了笑美的心。但就目前的情況來看，我為她做不了什麼，而且我知道她太固執了，不會承認她希望我留下來。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8813
translate zh_hant a3ec4o2_07c94172:

    # "I watch various emotions cross Emi's face as she tries to process everything that's just happened."
    "我看著笑美消化著剛才所發生的一系列情況；無數的複雜情感閃過她的臉龐。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8818
translate zh_hant a3ec4o2_aa3c270b:

    # "Shortly comes that calm look again, like last night, and that voice that tries so hard to sound careless."
    "很快，那種平靜的表情又出現了，就像昨晚一樣，還有那種努力裝作不在乎的聲音。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8820
translate zh_hant a3ec4o2_9bcce717:

    # emi "Sure, Hisao. See you around."
    emi "當然，久夫。回頭見。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8822
translate zh_hant a3ec4o2_9ee7d4bd:

    # "Both of us are unwilling to concede emotion at this point, and I'm having a hard time keeping up my facade, so I turn on my heel and walk out the door."
    "我們二人都不願意流露出自己的感情，而我已經快維持不住自己的僞裝，所以我只得轉身大步走出了房門。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8829
translate zh_hant a3ec4o2_b1eef769:

    # "I shut it behind me slowly, pausing for a moment as the latch catches, my hand on the doorknob."
    "我慢慢地把身後的門關上，當門閂卡住時，我的手還放在門把上，停頓了一下。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8831
translate zh_hant a3ec4o2_a61b5ef6:

    # "Did I make the right decision just now? Should I have stayed and tried to work things out?"
    "我剛才的決定是對的嗎？我應該留下來試著解決問題嗎？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8833
translate zh_hant a3ec4o2_49f57b9a:

    # "No, I decide. Not in front of her mother like that. In spite of everything, I'd rather keep Emi's mother insulated from the sort of anger that surfaced last night."
    "不，我決定。不能那樣當著她媽媽的面。儘管如此，我還是寧願讓笑美的媽媽遠離昨晚那種憤怒。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8835
translate zh_hant a3ec4o2_68abcf7d:

    # "Even though she's probably used to it, some protective instinct wants me to keep Emi's image as a cheerful girl intact."
    "即使她可能已經習慣了，某種保護本能還是想讓我維持笑美開朗女孩的形象。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8837
translate zh_hant a3ec4o2_7472a3d5:

    # "With a start, I realize my hand is still resting on the knob. I take my hand away, put it in my pocket, and head down the slowly darkening street."
    "我猛然驚覺，我的手還放在門把上。我把手拿開，放進口袋，沿著逐漸昏暗的街道走去。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8844
translate zh_hant a3ec4o2_67e1da17:

    # "I let out a long breath."
    "我長長地呼了一口氣。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8846
translate zh_hant a3ec4o2_6716e4b7:

    # "The wait until tomorrow morning comes isn't going to be easy."
    "等待明天早上的來臨，看來會很難熬。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8848
translate zh_hant a3ec4o2_a8f6844f:

    # "In any case, I have to think on what to say to Emi. I must apologize, and I must get through to her somehow."
    "無論如何，我得想想該對笑美說些什麼。我必須先道歉，而且必須設法讓她明白。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8850
translate zh_hant a3ec4o2_f128fadb:

    # "On that account, something has been on my mind for most of the way back to my room."
    "說起這個，有件事在我回房間前一直在我腦海中盤旋，"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8852
translate zh_hant a3ec4o2_78cf2dc7:

    # "The letter of apology from Iwanako."
    "巖魚子的道歉信。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8854
translate zh_hant a3ec4o2_41a2ddb1:

    # "I was so concerned about my new life when I received it that I didn't even bother to really read it."
    "收到信的時候，我太專注於我的新生活，甚至懶得真正去讀它。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8856
translate zh_hant a3ec4o2_9e02c33e:

    # "Now that I find myself in a similar position, my curiosity got rekindled. What did she want to let me know so badly?"
    "現在我發現自己處於類似的境地，我的好奇心又被重新點燃了。她那麼急切地還想讓我知道什麼？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8858
translate zh_hant a3ec4o2_39f5ef17:

    # "If nothing else, reading her thoughts might help me frame mine."
    "就算沒別的，讀讀她的想法或許能幫助我整理自己的思緒。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8860
translate zh_hant a3ec4o2_5d5daed8:

    # "I remember tossing it away. Damn, where did I throw that thing?"
    "我記得把它扔掉了。可惡，我把那東西扔到哪裡去了？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8862
translate zh_hant a3ec4o2_4c3c4c68:

    # "I check under my desk. That turns up nothing, so I look for harder-to-reach, more unlikely locations."
    "我檢查了書桌底下。什麼也沒找到，於是我開始尋找更難觸及、更不可能的地方。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8864
translate zh_hant a3ec4o2_ce617998:

    # "…"
    "……"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8866
translate zh_hant a3ec4o2_80a1dc21:

    # "Well, now I know where that lost sock went, at least."
    "嗯，至少現在我知道那隻不見的襪子去哪了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8868
translate zh_hant a3ec4o2_91d1d7a1:

    # "Still no letter, though."
    "不過還是沒有找到那封信。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8870
translate zh_hant a3ec4o2_d78a5abd:

    # "It's when I try sweeping my arm under my nightstand that I feel something crinkly jammed between it and the wall."
    "當我試著用手臂掃過床頭櫃底下時，我感覺到有什麼皺巴巴的東西卡在它和牆壁之間。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8872
translate zh_hant a3ec4o2_1d2e07d2:

    # "Grunting a little with the effort, I reach for my prize and soon manage to bring it into the light."
    "我費力地哼了一聲，伸手去拿我的戰利品，成功地把它拿到光線下。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8874
translate zh_hant a3ec4o2_f978f6d6:

    # "Bingo."
    "賓果。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8881
translate zh_hant a3ec4o2_169d14d8:

    # "I sit at my desk and spread the crumpled paper open. A flick turns on the table light."
    "坐在桌子前，將滿是褶皺的紙張撫平；隨手一伸，把檯燈打開。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8883
translate zh_hant a3ec4o2_c49de01b:

    # "Skipping past the empty pleasantries, I look for the point where I stopped reading. Ah, here it is."
    "跳過那些空洞的客套話，我尋找我上次停下來的地方。啊，在這裡。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8889
translate zh_hant a3ec4o2_5eb5fbc8:

    # "Giving up on happiness…"
    "放棄幸福……"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8891
translate zh_hant a3ec4o2_cba0877c:

    # "This sounds unpleasantly familiar."
    "這聽起來有種令人不快的耳熟。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8899
translate zh_hant a3ec4o2_920f684a:

    # "After finishing reading the letter I smooth it out carefully and set it aside on my desk."
    "讀完了信，我小心翼翼地把它再次撫平，放在書桌的一旁。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8903
translate zh_hant a3ec4o2_76b2fe88:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8906
translate zh_hant a3ec4o2_00283d1a:

    # n "{vspace=90}Thank you, Iwanako. I wanted to answer 'yes' to your question on that snowy winter day, but I never got to."
    n "{vspace=90}謝謝妳，巖魚子。那個冬日，我好想回答妳「我願意」，可是我從來沒有過機會。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8908
translate zh_hant a3ec4o2_4e528fd9:

    # n "By the time we met again, it was too late."
    n "當我們再次見面的時候，已經太晚了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8910
translate zh_hant a3ec4o2_6e9d2108:

    # n "Or so I thought. What would have happened if I had behaved differently, back in that dismally sterile hospital room?"
    n "至少我是這麼想的。當初在那個令人憂鬱的病房裡，我的行為表現如果有所不同，會發生什麼事呢？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8912
translate zh_hant a3ec4o2_9fa0f1ed:

    # n "I'm sorry. There's no point in wondering now, but there's no point in trying to forget either."
    n "對不起，現在想這些已經毫無意義了。但是強行想要忘記它也同樣的毫無意義。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8914
translate zh_hant a3ec4o2_90e85921:

    # n "I am who I am because of all that happened to me and all I look forward to experience. Present, future, and past."
    n "我之所以是我，是因為我所經歷的一切，以及我所期待的一切。現在、未來和過去。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8918
translate zh_hant a3ec4o2_41c2efed:

    # n "{vspace=60}And the past may just have taught me an important lesson now."
    n "{vspace=60}而過去，或許剛剛教會了我重要的一課。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8922
translate zh_hant a3ec4o2_76b2fe88_1:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8928
translate zh_hant a3ec5o1_82832ea0:

    # "I'm not sure I like the idea of airing private matters to the Student Council."
    "我不太確定把私事告訴學生會是個好主意。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8930
translate zh_hant a3ec5o1_411b365a:

    # hi "Nothing major."
    hi "沒什麼大不了的。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8935
translate zh_hant a3ec5o1_3349a56b:

    # mi "Hicchan, lying is a terrible thing to do~!"
    mi "小久，說謊是不好的行為喔～！"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8937
translate zh_hant a3ec5o1_10006c17:

    # "She's not buying it."
    "她不買帳。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8939
translate zh_hant a3ec5o1_afcd1269:

    # "Okay, give her something, but not too much."
    "好吧，告訴她一點，但不要太多。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8941
translate zh_hant a3ec5o1_9dfb4357:

    # hi "We had a disagreement and haven't resolved it yet."
    hi "我們意見不合，還沒解決。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8946
translate zh_hant a3ec5o1_03cffce5:

    # mi "Oh? Why not?"
    mi "哦？為什麼還沒？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8948
translate zh_hant a3ec5o1_c548e197:

    # hi "Because - look, I don't need to talk about this, okay?"
    hi "因為——聽著，我不需要談論這件事，好嗎？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8950
translate zh_hant a3ec5o1_76f21957:

    # hi "It's not a big deal, okay? I'm fine."
    hi "不是什麼大事，好嗎？我沒事。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8955
translate zh_hant a3ec5o1_718309a7:

    # mi "And Emi? Is she fine too, Hicchan?"
    mi "那笑美呢？她也沒事嗎，小久？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8959
translate zh_hant a3ec5o1_e4cbdb66:

    # "Misha's voice has taken on a decidedly serious edge. This is ridiculous."
    "米莎的聲音帶上了一股明顯嚴肅的口氣。這太荒謬了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8961
translate zh_hant a3ec5o1_dc2e1ded:

    # hi "I don't know, okay? I haven't asked. Things are complicated right now."
    hi "我不知道，好嗎？我沒問。現在情況很複雜。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8966
translate zh_hant a3ec5o1_77c0a540:

    # mi "What kind of man are you? Things get a little rough and you're going to hide from them?"
    mi "你算什麼男人？事情一變得棘手你就要躲起來嗎？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8970
translate zh_hant a3ec5o1_987d6d6c:

    # "Misha's sudden retort catches me completely off guard."
    "米莎突如其來的反駁讓我完全措手不及。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8975
translate zh_hant a3ec5o1_8b3790bc:

    # mi "Shicchan would call that a cowardly act, and she'd be right too!"
    mi "小靜會說這是懦夫的行為，而且她說的也沒錯！"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8977
translate zh_hant a3ec5o1_668fc46b:

    # mi "You two were close! Happy together! And you're just going to roll over and die without a fight?"
    mi "你們兩個那麼親密！在一起那麼開心！你就準備這樣毫無反抗地躺下等死嗎？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8979
translate zh_hant a3ec5o1_ee0c1971:

    # mi "You should be willing to fight for your girlfriend, Hisao!"
    mi "你應該願意為你的女朋友奮鬥，久夫！"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8981
translate zh_hant a3ec5o1_ae4418a5:

    # "It seems that Misha is channeling Shizune at the moment. It wouldn't surprise me to find out that Shizune gave her a script to follow based on my answer."
    "米莎內心的靜音人格似乎爆發了。靜音不會是給了她一個照著讀的劇本吧……"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8983
translate zh_hant a3ec5o1_9e103630:

    # "Misha points an imperious arm at the classroom door."
    "米莎用一隻盛氣凌人的手臂指向教室門口。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8988
translate zh_hant a3ec5o1_a9759b73:

    # mi "Now you get out of the classroom and patch things up!"
    mi "現在你給我滾出教室，把事情解決好！"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8990
translate zh_hant a3ec5o1_88334556:

    # hi "Um, we've still got afternoon classes…"
    hi "嗯，我們下午還有課……"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8992
translate zh_hant a3ec5o1_9b1c04f7:

    # "This doesn't seem to dissuade Misha."
    "這似乎沒有勸退米莎。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8997
translate zh_hant a3ec5o1_a5e37d5e:

    # mi "Then after class! You'd better do it, Hicchan! It's important that you don't leave things like this!"
    mi "那就下課後！你最好去做，小久！讓事情就這樣擱著，是不行的！"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:8999
translate zh_hant a3ec5o1_7df9d21b:

    # hi "Why?"
    hi "為什麼？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9004
translate zh_hant a3ec5o1_1fc561aa:

    # "Misha regards me as one would regard an animal's droppings."
    "米莎用看著動物糞便的眼神看著我。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9006
translate zh_hant a3ec5o1_0b7b82eb:

    # mi "Didn't you care about her, Hisao? That's important, isn't it?"
    mi "你難道沒有在意過她嗎，久夫？這難道不重要嗎？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9008
translate zh_hant a3ec5o1_76557802:

    # "Huh. She's right."
    "她……說得沒錯。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9010
translate zh_hant a3ec5o1_d7e9e336:

    # "I did… I do care about her."
    "我的確在意過……也依然在意她。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9012
translate zh_hant a3ec5o1_fee0e287:

    # "Don't I?"
    "不是嗎？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9014
translate zh_hant a3ec5o1_4db780c5:

    # hi "Okay. I'll see her after class."
    hi "好吧。我下課後會去找她。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9019
translate zh_hant a3ec5o1_26925f6e:

    # mi "Great~! I'll let Shicchan know you're okay, then~!"
    mi "好極了！那我告訴小靜你沒事了~！"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9021
translate zh_hant a3ec5o1_8d774db6:

    # "The lilt returns. I guess that means that Misha isn't angry at me any more."
    "那輕快的語調又回來了。我想這代表米莎不再生我的氣了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9026
translate zh_hant a3ec5o1_8e88a84d:

    # "She waves and disappears down the hallway, and I eat my lunch."
    "她揮了揮手，消失在走廊盡頭，而我則開始吃我的午餐。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9031
translate zh_hant a3ec5o1_60fa12e0:

    # "While afternoon classes draw to a close, I prepare myself for the task ahead."
    "當下午的課程接近尾聲時，我也為眼前嚴峻的難題做好了準備。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9033
translate zh_hant a3ec5o1_0d050ce5:

    # "I have to see Emi; Misha was at least correct about that. Leaving the question of Emi and me an open issue won't work."
    "我必須去見笑美；至少米莎這點說對了。讓我和笑美之間的問題懸而未決是行不通的。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9035
translate zh_hant a3ec5o1_ac116323:

    # "At the very least, I need to apologize for what I said."
    "至少，我需要為我說的話道歉。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9037
translate zh_hant a3ec5o1_7eee68ea:

    # "I consider going to her room to find her, but she's probably still at the track."
    "我考慮過去她的房間找她，但她可能還在操場。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9042
translate zh_hant a3ec5o1_206b90a8:

    # "The steps out of the main building and down the path to the track make me feel like a doomed man."
    "走出主樓，沿著小路走向操場的每一步，都讓我感覺自己像個注定失敗的人。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9044
translate zh_hant a3ec5o1_a98979d3:

    # "I have a twisting, horrible feeling in my gut that this is all going to go horribly wrong, that I'm not going to accomplish anything."
    "我的肚子裡有一種扭曲、可怕的感覺，覺得這一切都會變得一團糟，我什麼也無法完成。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9046
translate zh_hant a3ec5o1_4f2b9f14:

    # "Except for maybe driving the final nail in the coffin of whatever it was Emi and I had."
    "除了為我和笑美之間的一切，釘上最後一根棺材釘。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9053
translate zh_hant a3ec5o1_35bce254:

    # "There she is, just as expected, running laps around the track after everyone else has gone to shower and dinner."
    "她在那裡，正如預料，在其他人都去洗澡吃飯後，還在操場上跑著步。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9055
translate zh_hant a3ec5o1_cf62423b:

    # "I don't wave, or even make my presence known. I just sit down on the bleachers and watch her run her laps."
    "我沒有揮手，甚至沒有讓她知道我的存在。我只是坐在看台上，看著她一圈圈地跑著。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9065
translate zh_hant a3ec5o1_935c3fb6:

    # "It takes her a few trips around the track before she notices me, after which she skids to a stop, eyes wide in surprise."
    "她繞著操場跑了幾圈才注意到我，之後她猛地停下腳步，驚訝地睜大了眼睛。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9073
translate zh_hant a3ec5o1_cbaf21ee:

    # "Surprise is quickly masked by anger, which in turn fades behind a mask that I already know is impenetrable."
    "驚訝很快被憤怒掩蓋，而憤怒又褪去，換上了一張我早已知道堅不可摧的面具。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9075
translate zh_hant a3ec5o1_04e355f0:

    # emi "What are you doing here?"
    emi "你來這裡做什麼？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9077
translate zh_hant a3ec5o1_b96389c2:

    # "Not quite the response I'd hoped for, but at this point I don't have much of a choice."
    "不完全是我所期望的回應，但事到如今我已別無選擇。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9079
translate zh_hant a3ec5o1_d136b5d5:

    # hi "I wanted to apologize for what I said the other day."
    hi "我想為我前幾天說的話道歉。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9084
translate zh_hant a3ec5o1_5a95d2b2:

    # emi "The other day?"
    emi "前幾天？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9089
translate zh_hant a3ec5o1_443ec210:

    # "She laughs, a curt exclamation of disbelief."
    "她笑出了聲；一種表示難以置信的，近乎感嘆的笑。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9096
translate zh_hant a3ec5o1_d7115547:

    # emi "It's been almost a week, Hisao."
    emi "快一個禮拜了，久夫。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9098
translate zh_hant a3ec5o1_522711c7:

    # hi "Yeah, well… better late than never, right?"
    hi "是啊，嗯……遲到總比不到好，對吧？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9103
translate zh_hant a3ec5o1_3a635476:

    # "Emi crosses her arms and stares at me coolly, as if sizing me up. Finally, she nods."
    "笑美雙臂交叉，冷冷地注視著我，彷彿在估測我的想法。最後，她點了點頭。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9108
translate zh_hant a3ec5o1_93ad327b:

    # emi "Hmmph. I suppose you're right. Water under the bridge, then. I forgive you."
    emi "哼。我想你說得對。那就既往不咎了。我原諒你。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9113
translate zh_hant a3ec5o1_254b33af:

    # emi "Is that all?"
    emi "再沒事了吧？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9122
translate zh_hant a3ec5o1_579d89f8:

    # "Her almost impatient question catches me so off-guard that she's halfway down the track before I think to shout after her."
    "她近乎不耐煩的問題讓我措手不及，以至於在我想到要對她大喊時，她已經跑到操場的遠端了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9124
translate zh_hant a3ec5o1_553a5543:

    # hi "No, wait!"
    hi "不，等等！"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9134
translate zh_hant a3ec5o1_1ebe26a3:

    # "Emi stops, turns, and walks back to me, breathing a little heavily and looking annoyed at my interruption."
    "笑美停下腳步，轉身走回我面前，呼吸有些急促，看起來對我的打擾感到惱火。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9136
translate zh_hant a3ec5o1_cf45f9a1:

    # emi "What?"
    emi "幹嘛？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9138
translate zh_hant a3ec5o1_95b4b928:

    # "Okay, I need to make this right, somehow. I have to know where I stand, maybe patch things up."
    "好吧，我得想辦法把這件事處理好。我必須知道我的立場，或許還能修補關係。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9140
translate zh_hant a3ec5o1_f373f499:

    # hi "Can you at least sit down?"
    hi "妳至少可以坐下來嗎？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9145
translate zh_hant a3ec5o1_6aebea97:

    # emi "I think we're okay talking here."
    emi "我覺得我們在這裡談就可以了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9147
translate zh_hant a3ec5o1_64907b4f:

    # hi "Fine, sure. Look, about us…"
    hi "好吧，隨便妳。聽著，關於我們……"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9149
translate zh_hant a3ec5o1_61d64386:

    # "I pause, trying to think of a good way to phrase what I'm about to say."
    "我停頓了一下，試圖想一個好的措辭來表達我接下來要說的話。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9151
translate zh_hant a3ec5o1_690046cd:

    # "But before I can launch into an impassioned plea for giving me another chance, Emi's already spoken."
    "但在我能展開一番慷慨激昂的懇求，希望她再給我一次機會之前，笑美已經開口了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9156
translate zh_hant a3ec5o1_313be44c:

    # emi "There's no more us, Hisao."
    emi "已經沒有我們了，久夫。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9158
translate zh_hant a3ec5o1_f5743db9:

    # hi "Why not?"
    hi "為什麼？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9163
translate zh_hant a3ec5o1_6a8bfaf3:

    # emi "We're just not right for each other."
    emi "我們只是不適合彼此。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9165
translate zh_hant a3ec5o1_a840c44d:

    # "She delivers this outrageous statement without even looking in my eyes."
    "她說出這句離譜的話時，甚至沒有看我的眼睛。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9167
translate zh_hant a3ec5o1_ae4e0c83:

    # hi "I don't believe you! We're great with one another!"
    hi "我不相信！我們明明很合得來！"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9172
translate zh_hant a3ec5o1_eae0249d:

    # emi "Says the guy apologizing for getting thrown out of my house last week."
    emi "這話從一個上週被我趕出家門，現在來道歉的人嘴裡說出來，還真是沒說服力。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9174
translate zh_hant a3ec5o1_9370a48e:

    # hi "It was a fight! I said something really, incredibly stupid and apologized for it!"
    hi "那只是一次吵架！我說了非常、非常愚蠢的話，而且我已經道歉了！"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9179
translate zh_hant a3ec5o1_835baed1:

    # emi "And how many times had we already discussed the problem that started the fight? How many times had I told you that there was a set boundary that I wouldn't cross, and how many times did you keep trying to cross it?"
    emi "而我們在吵架前，已經多少次討論過背後的問題了？我告訴過你多少次，我有著自己絕不容挑戰的底線，而你又多少次挑戰了那條底線？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9181
translate zh_hant a3ec5o1_23a95c95:

    # hi "Because your boundary was stupid!"
    hi "因為妳的底線簡直是不可理喻！"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9186
translate zh_hant a3ec5o1_8e8a9e5c:

    # "Emi rolls her eyes, folds her arm across her chest, and cocks her head to the side."
    "笑美翻了個白眼，雙臂交叉在胸前，頭歪向一邊。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9188
translate zh_hant a3ec5o1_1fab5a93:

    # emi "Do you see this, Hisao? This is why we're not right for one another!"
    emi "你看到了嗎，久夫？這就是為什麼我們不適合彼此！"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9190
translate zh_hant a3ec5o1_58117965:

    # "Her voice softens a little, and she reaches out to stroke my cheek."
    "她的聲音微微溫和了些，並伸出手來，輕撫著我的臉頰。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9195
translate zh_hant a3ec5o1_4a2a681e:

    # emi "You're a good guy, but we're not going to work."
    emi "你是個好人，但我們不會有結果的。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9197
translate zh_hant a3ec5o1_54709eb8:

    # "With a horrible lurching feeling, I realize that she's been practicing this. Maybe every day since I left her house."
    "我心中一沉，可怕地意識到她一直在練習這段話。也許從我離開她家的那天起，每天都在練習。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9199
translate zh_hant a3ec5o1_74a4655d:

    # "Even the cheek-stroke seems rehearsed, like something out of a movie."
    "就連撫摸臉頰的動作似乎都排練過，像是電影裡的情節。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9201
translate zh_hant a3ec5o1_a514d963:

    # "She never intended to give me another chance."
    "她從來就沒打算再給我一次機會。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9203
translate zh_hant a3ec5o1_78decb1f:

    # "Hell, she probably would have been fine with never seeing me again."
    "媽的，她可能巴不得再也不要見到我。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9205
translate zh_hant a3ec5o1_e184148b:

    # hi "So that's it, then? Nothing else to say but 'Gee, it was fun while it lasted, but so long?'"
    hi "所以就這樣了？除了說『唉，在一起的時候很開心，但再見了』之外，就沒別的話了？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9210
translate zh_hant a3ec5o1_641b6051:

    # "This actually seems to amuse Emi far more than I wanted it to. She gives a rather morbid sounding chuckle."
    "這似乎比我預期的更能逗樂笑美。她發出了一聲相當病態的輕笑。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9212
translate zh_hant a3ec5o1_2cab9535:

    # emi "That's how I've lived my life, Hisao. You should know that by now."
    emi "我一直都是這樣過生活的，久夫。你現在應該知道了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9217
translate zh_hant a3ec5o1_acfd39bc:

    # emi "And it was fun."
    emi "而且那段時間很開心。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9219
translate zh_hant a3ec5o1_792868d5:

    # "A sad smile. She shivers slightly, and the smile vanishes."
    "笑美臉龐上浮露出一個悲傷的微笑。身體微微一顫，那微笑也隨之消失了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9224
translate zh_hant a3ec5o1_81ad0636:

    # emi "But it's over now. It's for the best."
    emi "但現在結束了。這樣對我們兩個都好。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9226
translate zh_hant a3ec5o1_8490a4d8:

    # "I want to yell, to scream at her. Make her see reason, that this is stupid, the whole act. That she's just afraid of me, afraid of what being close to someone means."
    "我想對她發火，對她大叫，讓她恢復理智，讓她放棄這愚蠢的分手，讓她看清這不過是個鬧劇。讓她明白，她只是害怕我，害怕向一個人真正敞開心扉所包含的意義。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9228
translate zh_hant a3ec5o1_97acbdc7:

    # "I want to tell her that I love her and that I can't just give up on her at the drop of a hat."
    "我想告訴她我愛她，我不能就這樣放棄她。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9230
translate zh_hant a3ec5o1_666122cb:

    # "Except… there's no point. She's made up her mind. We're done."
    "只是……這些都沒有意義了。她已經做出自己的決定。我們結束了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9232
translate zh_hant a3ec5o1_982f52e4:

    # hi "Fine."
    hi "好吧。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9237
translate zh_hant a3ec5o1_6f7d71c6:

    # "Emi nods, satisfied. I want to hit something."
    "笑美滿意地點了點頭。我想打人。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9239
translate zh_hant a3ec5o1_481d5cf5:

    # emi "Good."
    emi "很好。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9244
translate zh_hant a3ec5o1_2e42a9bd:

    # "She brightens with a false cheeriness."
    "她戴上僞裝的活潑外表笑了起來。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9246
translate zh_hant a3ec5o1_d5427a34:

    # emi "See you around, Hisao."
    emi "回頭見，久夫。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9248
translate zh_hant a3ec5o1_4e0987bf:

    # hi "No you won't. You won't even try."
    hi "妳不會的。妳連試都不會試。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9257
translate zh_hant a3ec5o1_db767434:

    # "She shrugs, as if to say 'Have it your way,' and turns her back on me once more, quickly accelerating around the curve of the track."
    "她聳了聳肩，彷彿在說「隨便你」，然後再次背對我，迅速地沿著跑道彎道加速。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9259
translate zh_hant a3ec5o1_a6699bf2:

    # "I feel numb. This is it. The end of the road for us, whatever that was. Closure, at least."
    "我感到麻木。就這樣了。我們之間的路走到了盡頭，無論那是什麼。至少，有個了結。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9261
translate zh_hant a3ec5o1_93690a9e:

    # "Emi rounds the track again without sparing me a second glance. She's running much faster now, and I can't help but think of that first run together."
    "跑過一圈的笑美又轉了過來，連看都沒有再看我一眼。她跑得越來越快了，我的思緒忍不住回到了我們第一次一起跑步那一刻。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9263
translate zh_hant a3ec5o1_f5c23dad:

    # "I ran to catch you, to try to prove I wasn't as weak as I knew I was. But it ended badly for me, didn't it?"
    "當時，我試著追上妳，試著想自己證明我沒有所想的那麼弱。但那還是以悲劇告終了，不是嗎？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9265
translate zh_hant a3ec5o1_c35115bf:

    # "And now, you're off running too fast for me again, and I have the choice to run after you again."
    "現在，妳又在我面前努力地跑著，誘惑著我去追趕妳。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9267
translate zh_hant a3ec5o1_46b3af49:

    # "But I won't. Not this time. You'd never let me catch you."
    "但我不會。這次不會了。妳永遠不會讓我追上妳的。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9274
translate zh_hant a3ec5o1_810668f8:

    # "I don't even notice walking away from the track, or walking into my room, or pulling a book out of my bag to read."
    "我甚至沒有注意到自己離開了操場，走進了我的房間，或是從書包裡拿出一本書來讀。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9276
translate zh_hant a3ec5o1_8ce04333:

    # "Just before bed, I reset my alarm. Emi and I have had our final encounter."
    "就在睡前，我重新設定了鬧鐘。我和笑美已經沒有了最後的交集。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9281
translate zh_hant a3ec5o1_9f569e61:

    # "We don't speak again after that."
    "從那以後，我們再沒有說過一句話。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9288
translate zh_hant a3ec5o2_6270ef53:

    # "Well, I suppose someone else knowing about my problem can't hurt. Heck, maybe Misha can even offer some advice."
    "算了，多個人來嘲笑我又如何。說不定米莎還真的會有什麼好建議呢。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9290
translate zh_hant a3ec5o2_c745f9e1:

    # hi "We had a fight at her house."
    hi "我們在她家吵了一架。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9292
translate zh_hant a3ec5o2_5baa6e55:

    # hi "I keep trying to get close to her, and she won't let me get close, and…"
    hi "我總是想要接近她，可她卻總是把我推開，然後……"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9294
translate zh_hant a3ec5o2_330a09c9:

    # hi "I said something stupid, and she threw me out."
    hi "我說了一些很過分的東西，她就把我趕出去了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9299
translate zh_hant a3ec5o2_55f6f24e:

    # mi "Have you talked to her since then?"
    mi "從那以後，你就沒和她講過話嗎？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9301
translate zh_hant a3ec5o2_072256c5:

    # "Misha looks genuinely concerned. I'm surprised, as I'd almost expected her to drop the subject after finding out what the trouble was."
    "米莎看起來真的很關心。我還滿驚訝的，我本來以為她一知道是什麼麻煩事之後就會把這話題丟一邊了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9303
translate zh_hant a3ec5o2_deaf3471:

    # "Even more surprising is how quickly I find myself spilling my guts to her."
    "更令我驚訝的是，我居然如此迫不及待地向她傾訴了一切。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9305
translate zh_hant a3ec5o2_f7e46617:

    # hi "No, I haven't. I just can't bring myself to face her after that."
    hi "不，還沒。我不知道該如何面對她……"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9307
translate zh_hant a3ec5o2_d213830b:

    # hi "I made a complete fool of myself, and she probably hates me now anyway. Especially since I haven't seen her since then."
    hi "我讓自己看起來像個十足的笨蛋，她現在大概很討厭我了。尤其是我從那之後就沒再見過她。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9312
translate zh_hant a3ec5o2_7570452f:

    # mi "You're pretty slow, Hicchan."
    mi "小久，你真的很遲鈍耶。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9316
translate zh_hant a3ec5o2_56bf7896:

    # "This doesn't sound like advice."
    "這聽起來可不像建議啊。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9318
translate zh_hant a3ec5o2_0f638bea:

    # hi "Huh?"
    hi "蛤？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9323
translate zh_hant a3ec5o2_944de350:

    # "Misha places her hands on her hips and launches into a speech that would sound more plausible coming from Shizune."
    "米莎雙手插腰，開始了一段聽起來更像是靜音會說的訓話。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9325
translate zh_hant a3ec5o2_73c61884:

    # mi "The solution to your problem is simple! You have to go and apologize to her! Leaving things like this will just make things worse!"
    mi "你問題的解決方法很簡單！你必須去跟她道歉！把事情就這樣放著只會讓情況更糟！"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9327
translate zh_hant a3ec5o2_88d063bd:

    # mi "You can't know that she hates you now unless she tells you! Otherwise, there's no evidence that what you fear is true!"
    mi "除非她親口告訴你，不然你不會知道她現在是不是討厭你！否則，就沒有證據證明你害怕的事情是真的！"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9329
translate zh_hant a3ec5o2_ca2425d0:

    # mi "And if you really care about her, shouldn't you be worried about how she's taking all this?"
    mi "再說了，你要是真的在意她，你不應該擔心一下她的感受嗎？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9333
translate zh_hant a3ec5o2_365b649a:

    # "With a sudden start, I realize that she's right. I've kept waking up to an early alarm because part of me wants to meet Emi at the track for our runs."
    "一語驚醒夢中人。她說的沒錯。我每天早上都堅持被那個鬧鐘吵醒，是因為我的內心依然希望著見到笑美，希望與她一起跑步。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9335
translate zh_hant a3ec5o2_0c8cbd64:

    # "I've kept running, because I know that Emi would worry about me if I didn't stay healthy."
    "我每天傍晚還堅持跑步，是因為我知道笑美會擔心我的健康。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9337
translate zh_hant a3ec5o2_7aa84486:

    # "When I went on the roof yesterday, I was half-hoping that she would be up there, and felt disappointed when she wasn't."
    "昨天我去屋頂的時候，其實有點希望她會在那裡，當她不在時，我真的很失望。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9339
translate zh_hant a3ec5o2_44383294:

    # hi "I'm an idiot."
    hi "我是個白癡。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9344
translate zh_hant a3ec5o2_28d2e568:

    # mi "Kinda, Hicchan~!"
    mi "有點像喔，小久～！"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9349
translate zh_hant a3ec5o2_ebe286f7:

    # mi "So~! Go and apologize to her as soon as you can, okay~?"
    mi "所以～！盡快去跟她道歉，好嗎～？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9351
translate zh_hant a3ec5o2_499e3303:

    # "I open my mouth to say that I'll do it right away, but the lunch bell rings and I realize that I still have afternoon classes to attend."
    "我張開嘴想說我會馬上去，但午休鐘聲響了，我才意識到下午還有課要上。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9353
translate zh_hant a3ec5o2_4e107032:

    # hi "First thing after class is over, I'll go see her. I promise."
    hi "課一結束我就馬上去找她。我保證。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9355
translate zh_hant a3ec5o2_2525e2b1:

    # hi "And uh, thanks for the advice, I guess."
    hi "還有，呃，謝謝妳的建議，我想。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9360
translate zh_hant a3ec5o2_b0e33fa9:

    # "Misha beams at me, as if I were a child that had just learned his ABCs."
    "米莎對我笑得燦爛，好像我是一個剛學會ABC的小孩。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9362
translate zh_hant a3ec5o2_0f592a23:

    # mi "Good! I'll let Shicchan know that you're okay, then~!"
    mi "太好了！那我去告訴小靜你沒事了～！"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9364
translate zh_hant a3ec5o2_b9f050c2:

    # hi "Er, yeah. You do that."
    hi "呃，好啊。妳去吧。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9369
translate zh_hant a3ec5o2_9d9d0b68:

    # "With a wave (and completely disregarding the fact that people are starting to trickle back into the classroom, as opposed to out of it), Misha departs the classroom."
    "米莎揮了揮手（完全無視人們是開始回到教室，而不是離開教室），離開了教室。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9371
translate zh_hant a3ec5o2_a08c18fe:

    # "I suppose she and Shizune have student council business again."
    "我想她和靜音又有學生會的事要忙了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9376
translate zh_hant a3ec5o2_1f72350b:

    # "While the afternoon wears on, I find myself impatient for lessons to end. I need to see Emi now."
    "下午的時光緩慢流逝，我發現自己等不及課程結束。我現在就需要見到笑美。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9378
translate zh_hant a3ec5o2_d3ee333f:

    # "I have to try to set things right. Even if Emi hates me now, I have to at least apologize."
    "我必須修復我們的關係。就算笑美已經討厭我了，我也必須向她道歉。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9380
translate zh_hant a3ec5o2_bb6100ab:

    # "I owe her that much."
    "這是我欠她的。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9382
translate zh_hant a3ec5o2_bd2f4cda:

    # "Should I meet her in her room? No, I decide, it would delay things too much. If I know Emi, then I can find her at the track."
    "我應該去她的房間找她嗎？不，太浪費時間了。如果我沒猜錯，笑美一定還在訓練。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9384
translate zh_hant a3ec5o2_ec1b96c5:

    # "Still have no idea what I'm going to say when I get there, but I take comfort in knowing that Emi probably wouldn't have a plan for something like this either."
    "雖然還是不知道到時候要說什麼，但想到笑美大概對這種事也沒什麼計畫，我就安心了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9386
translate zh_hant a3ec5o2_82d46b6f:

    # "Play it by ear. Stop being nervous, and just get to the track. Figure the rest out when I get there."
    "隨機應變。別太擔心，只要先去找她就好了。到時候再隨其自然吧。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9391
translate zh_hant a3ec5o2_0d2cc8a7:

    # "The track looms ahead, and another jolt of nerves hits me in the gut. I resist the urge to turn and walk away, and instead note with satisfaction that I was right and Emi is still running."
    "操場就在眼前，我的肚子又是一陣緊張。我忍住轉身走開的衝動，反而滿意地注意到我猜對了，笑美還在跑步。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9393
translate zh_hant a3ec5o2_b12d8b7b:

    # "I don't make myself immediately known; I find a seat in the bleachers and watch her run instead, thinking back to earlier meetings."
    "沒有立刻讓她注意到我，而是在看臺邊坐了下來看著她的身影，想著我們以前在一起的時光。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9403
translate zh_hant a3ec5o2_6c50f029:

    # "After a few trips around the track, Emi notices me and skids to a halt, an expression of surprise that slides easily into one of anger."
    "繞了操場幾圈後，笑美注意到我，然後緊急煞住，臉上驚訝的表情很快轉為憤怒。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9408
translate zh_hant a3ec5o2_04e355f0:

    # emi "What are you doing here?"
    emi "你在這裡做什麼？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9410
translate zh_hant a3ec5o2_b96389c2:

    # "Not quite the response I'd hoped for, but at this point I don't have much of a choice."
    "這反應跟我希望的不太一樣，但事到如今我也沒什麼選擇了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9412
translate zh_hant a3ec5o2_d136b5d5:

    # hi "I wanted to apologize for what I said the other day."
    hi "我想為前幾天說的話道歉。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9417
translate zh_hant a3ec5o2_5a95d2b2:

    # emi "The other day?"
    emi "前幾天？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9422
translate zh_hant a3ec5o2_443ec210:

    # "She laughs, a curt exclamation of disbelief."
    "她笑了，一聲簡短、充滿不信的感嘆。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9427
translate zh_hant a3ec5o2_d7115547:

    # emi "It's been almost a week, Hisao."
    emi "已經快一個禮拜了，久夫。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9429
translate zh_hant a3ec5o2_522711c7:

    # hi "Yeah, well… better late than never, right?"
    hi "是啊，嗯……遲到總比不到好，對吧？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9434
translate zh_hant a3ec5o2_3a635476:

    # "Emi crosses her arms and stares at me coolly, as if sizing me up. Finally, she nods."
    "笑美雙臂交叉，冷冷地注視著我，彷彿在估測我的想法。最後，她點了點頭。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9439
translate zh_hant a3ec5o2_93ad327b:

    # emi "Hmmph. I suppose you're right. Water under the bridge, then. I forgive you."
    emi "哼。我想你說得對。那就讓它過去吧。我原諒你。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9444
translate zh_hant a3ec5o2_254b33af:

    # emi "Is that all?"
    emi "沒事了吧？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9453
translate zh_hant a3ec5o2_9eee6a70:

    # "Her almost impatient question catches me so off-guard that she's already halfway down the track before I think to shout after her."
    "她那近乎不耐煩的問題讓我措手不及，等我想到要對她大喊時，她已經跑到操場的遠端了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9455
translate zh_hant a3ec5o2_553a5543:

    # hi "No, wait!"
    hi "不，等等！"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9460
translate zh_hant a3ec5o2_77dee3a3:

    # "She doesn't seem to have heard me - or she doesn't want to hear me - and so I give chase, disregarding completely the fact that I am not dressed for it."
    "她似乎沒聽到我說話——或者她不想聽——所以我追了上去，完全不顧自己穿的根本不適合跑步。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9465
translate zh_hant a3ec5o2_06b19e7a:

    # "My feet hurt, and my shirt collar feels like a noose around my neck, but I still chase after her, because if I don't I'll lose my chance."
    "我的腳很痛，襯衫領子像絞索一樣勒著我的脖子，但我還是追著她，因為如果我不這麼做，我就會失去機會。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9467
translate zh_hant a3ec5o2_8d7ca229:

    # "Emi hasn't started to really accelerate yet, which is probably the only reason why I'm able to catch up to her, to reach out and tap her on the shoulder, just before my legs give up running in dress shoes and stumble to a stop."
    "笑美還沒有開始真正加速，所以我還勉勉強強能夠追上她的腳步，伸手拍在她的肩膀上。穿著皮鞋的雙腳再也承受不住，兩腿一軟幾乎摔倒在地上。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9472
translate zh_hant a3ec5o2_2561d850:

    # "Surprisingly (fortunately?) all that running seems to have paid off. I'm short of breath, yes, but at least my heart isn't actively trying to force its way out of my ribcage."
    "出乎意料的（幸運的？）是，我的鍛鍊看來沒有白費。是，我幾乎喘不上氣，但是至少我的心臟還沒有像以往那樣蹦出我的胸膛。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9477
translate zh_hant a3ec5o2_31a2be0e:

    # "My touch on her shoulder has stopped Emi, and while there is a flash of concern when she sees me catching my breath, it seems that she has a good idea of what I'm capable of too."
    "肩膀的觸感讓笑美停了下來。見到我大口喘著粗氣，她的臉龐浮現一絲擔憂，但她似乎也清楚我還遠遠沒有到達極限。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9479
translate zh_hant a3ec5o2_69e896af:

    # "The concern is short-lived."
    "那份關心稍縱即逝。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9484
translate zh_hant a3ec5o2_cf45f9a1:

    # emi "What?"
    emi "幹嘛？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9486
translate zh_hant a3ec5o2_3341c279:

    # "She seems so irritated by my being still there that I almost lose my nerve, but I've lost my nerve enough."
    "她似乎對我還在這裡感到很惱火，我差點又失去勇氣，但我已經膽怯夠了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9488
translate zh_hant a3ec5o2_782da3c2:

    # hi "I need to explain myself. Why I can't just let the matter rest."
    hi "我需要解釋清楚。為什麼我不能就這樣算了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9493
translate zh_hant a3ec5o2_aecaea22:

    # "Emi folds her arms and bounces one blade on the ground in an approximation of tapping her foot impatiently. Angry as she is, and as nervous as I am, she still looks beautiful."
    "笑美雙臂交叉，用一邊的義肢在地上點著，像是在不耐煩地跺腳。儘管她很生氣，我也很緊張，她看起來還是很漂亮。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9495
translate zh_hant a3ec5o2_218d656d:

    # emi "Okay, Hisao. Explain."
    emi "好吧，久夫。解釋啊。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9497
translate zh_hant a3ec5o2_d16ee548:

    # hi "The thing is, I know that you're really sensitive about the accident and about your dad."
    hi "是這樣的，我知道妳對那場意外和妳爸爸的事非常敏感。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9499
translate zh_hant a3ec5o2_3c6b19c4:

    # "I can see Emi's face twitch at the mention of the two things that have been steadily driving us apart, or at least made me feel like we're being driven apart."
    "我可以看到，當我提到這兩件一直讓我們疏遠的事情時——或者至少是讓我覺得我們正在疏遠的事情時，笑美的臉抽動了一下。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9501
translate zh_hant a3ec5o2_69b92b2e:

    # hi "But that's why I want to know about them, I think."
    hi "但是，這大概也是我如此迫切想要了解它們的原因。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9503
translate zh_hant a3ec5o2_958d0ef1:

    # hi "Because I see how much they hurt you, and I want to be there to comfort you."
    hi "因為我親眼看到了，它們讓妳多麼痛苦。我希望能夠一直在你身邊。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9505
translate zh_hant a3ec5o2_ce3516da:

    # hi "It makes me miserable, seeing you sleepless and depressed - and don't pretend you aren't, because I know, okay?"
    hi "看到妳失眠、沮喪，讓我很痛苦——別假裝妳沒有，因為我知道，好嗎？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9507
translate zh_hant a3ec5o2_e87faeca:

    # hi "I just remember that night when you fell asleep with me and had that nightmare, and that you were happy to have me there when you woke up."
    hi "我記得我們在一起的那一個晚上，妳做惡夢時突然驚醒，看到我在身邊時，表現得那麼開心。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9509
translate zh_hant a3ec5o2_d70adea0:

    # hi "I want to be able to be there for you like that whenever you need me to be."
    hi "我希望每當妳需要我的時候，我都能像那樣陪在妳身邊。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9514
translate zh_hant a3ec5o2_68cb0611:

    # "The stern face cracks, slightly. Emi interrupts before I can continue further."
    "笑美嚴肅的面孔微微動容，在我能繼續之前開口打斷了我。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9516
translate zh_hant a3ec5o2_1ac23bdd:

    # emi "Just… stop right there. We can't see each other any more, okay?"
    emi "不……不要說了。我們不能在一起了，好嗎？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9521
translate zh_hant a3ec5o2_d71133cb:

    # "She's rushing now, looking everywhere but at me. I'm surprised she doesn't bolt, she knows I can't catch her…"
    "笑美急躁不安地左右亂看，避開我的雙眼。她沒有轉身就逃，已經很令我驚訝了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9523
translate zh_hant a3ec5o2_37f63bf6:

    # emi "We're not… we're not right for one another."
    emi "我們……我們不適合對方。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9525
translate zh_hant a3ec5o2_3f7d8273:

    # hi "That's not true, and you know it."
    hi "那不是真的，妳自己也知道。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9530
translate zh_hant a3ec5o2_b8e53f76:

    # emi "No, it's true. You're too—"
    emi "不，是真的。你太——"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9532
translate zh_hant a3ec5o2_66a79efa:

    # hi "I know. I know that I've been pushy about knowing your past."
    hi "我知道。我知道我一直咄咄逼人地想知道妳的過去。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9534
translate zh_hant a3ec5o2_0cb7d29b:

    # hi "If you can't tell me yet, then at least let me be there even if I don't know the reason."
    hi "如果妳還不能告訴我，那至少讓我在妳身邊，就算我不知道理由也沒關係。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9536
translate zh_hant a3ec5o2_3b568386:

    # hi "It's okay, I promise. I won't ask why you need comfort, I'll just give it freely."
    hi "沒關係，我保證。我不會問妳為什麼需要我，只是會給妳一副可以依靠的肩膀。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9541
translate zh_hant a3ec5o2_8ab74e60:

    # "Emi's shaking her head, and tears seem to be threatening the corners of her eyes."
    "笑美搖著頭，眼淚似乎快要從眼角滑落。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9543
translate zh_hant a3ec5o2_540334db:

    # emi "Stop saying that!"
    emi "別再說了！"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9545
translate zh_hant a3ec5o2_32dc58b0:

    # hi "Why? Because you're afraid you'll take me up on it?"
    hi "為什麼？因為妳怕妳會接受嗎？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9550
translate zh_hant a3ec5o2_f44ddb25:

    # emi "I'm not afraid!"
    emi "我才不怕！"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9552
translate zh_hant a3ec5o2_4129e9aa:

    # "I can't keep the chiding tone from my voice as I respond."
    "我回答時，忍不住帶了點責備的語氣。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9554
translate zh_hant a3ec5o2_72ac50c8:

    # hi "Yes, you are. You told me so yourself, remember? That's okay, really it is."
    hi "不，妳在怕。妳親口告訴過我的，記得嗎？沒關係的，真的沒關係。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9556
translate zh_hant a3ec5o2_6a1cb71f:

    # hi "However, it seems to me that someone who'd manage to come out of that wreck and still be as energetic and cheerful as you are would be determined enough to face that fear."
    hi "我相信，在經歷過那種事後還能夠頑強地爬起來，並活得像妳一樣充滿活力的人，一定可以有決心面對自己的恐懼的。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9561
translate zh_hant a3ec5o2_29a1a2e4:

    # emi "Determination? What do you know about determination?"
    emi "決心？你懂什麼是決心？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9563
translate zh_hant a3ec5o2_bf363f42:

    # hi "I know that there's a girl so determined to take care of a total stranger that she'd steal his food at a festival."
    hi "我知道有個女孩，她下定決心要照顧一個完全陌生的人，甚至在學園祭上偷走他的食物。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9565
translate zh_hant a3ec5o2_889126a9:

    # hi "I know that there's a girl so determined to help me with my own problems that she'd draw up a complete dietary and exercise plan, and that she'd not only draw up the plans, but she'd follow them with me, even when she couldn't run."
    hi "我知道有個女孩，下定決心想要幫助我，為我規劃整套的食譜和訓練計劃，風雨無阻地跟著我，確保我好好地執行它們。即便是她連站都站不起來的時候也是。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9567
translate zh_hant a3ec5o2_2595e9e3:

    # hi "Determined enough to keep me at arm's length that she'd put herself through emotional pain if she thought it was the right thing to do."
    hi "她的決心讓她堅持著，無論自己內心承受著多大的傷痛，也不願意讓我接近她。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9569
translate zh_hant a3ec5o2_2125d8fb:

    # hi "Although, there's one thing that this determined girl didn't quite plan for, which was that I might feel that same kind of determination to keep her from being hurt."
    hi "不過這個有決心的女孩還是忘記了一件事：我也許會產生同樣的決心，想要保護她，不讓她受傷。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9571
translate zh_hant a3ec5o2_89baae77:

    # hi "I fell in love with you, and I refuse to let that be thrown away because you're afraid of losing me."
    hi "我愛上了妳，我拒絕只因為妳害怕失去我，就放棄這段感情。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9576
translate zh_hant a3ec5o2_29afdbca:

    # "What little control Emi still has at this point cracks, and I find myself suddenly enveloped in her embrace as she cries."
    "笑美所還勉強維持的自制力被我徹底破壞了，哭著投入了我的懷抱。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9578
translate zh_hant a3ec5o2_c75a78b6:

    # emi "Why are you doing this? Why can't you just leave me alone?"
    emi "你為什麼這麼做？為什麼一定要這樣對我？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9583
translate zh_hant a3ec5o2_d1bb2ed3:

    # "I hold her close and plant a kiss on the top of her head."
    "我緊緊抱著她，在她頭頂上親了一下。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9585
translate zh_hant a3ec5o2_d4ffafbf:

    # hi "I'm sorry, Emi. You helped me when I first arrived, so now I have to help you. It's only fair."
    hi "對不起，笑美。我剛來的時候妳幫了我，所以現在換我幫妳。這才公平。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9587
translate zh_hant a3ec5o2_e75dbe1d:

    # emi "You're utterly hopeless, did you know that?"
    emi "你是個無可救藥的笨蛋，你知道嗎？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9589
translate zh_hant a3ec5o2_12df97b5:

    # "She hiccups and trembles a little."
    "她哽咽的嗝了，身體也顫抖起來。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9591
translate zh_hant a3ec5o2_9c4ea2c3:

    # hi "Funny, I could say the same about you."
    hi "真巧，我對妳也是這麼想的。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9593
translate zh_hant a3ec5o2_a6330d99:

    # emi "Can you do something for me, Hisao?"
    emi "久夫，你能為我做件事嗎？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9595
translate zh_hant a3ec5o2_166a03d6:

    # hi "Anything."
    hi "什麼都行。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9601
translate zh_hant a3ec5o2_e73c3ed7:

    # emi "Can you go, now?"
    emi "你現在可以先離開嗎？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9603
translate zh_hant a3ec5o2_ec78288c:

    # "It feels like she's just shoved a knife through my chest."
    "感覺就像她拿刀刺穿了我的胸膛。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9605
translate zh_hant a3ec5o2_f2913ad5:

    # hi "Go?"
    hi "離開？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9610
translate zh_hant a3ec5o2_9a21e210:

    # emi "I need to… I need to think, okay?"
    emi "我需要……一個人冷靜一下，好嗎？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9612
translate zh_hant a3ec5o2_4b2a3357:

    # emi "I can't just tell you everything yet. I'm still scared, and when you're around, I can't think clearly."
    emi "我還不能把所有事都告訴你。我……還是會怕。而且你在這裡，我沒辦法好好思考。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9614
translate zh_hant a3ec5o2_5a01c2db:

    # emi "But do me another favor."
    emi "不過能不能再幫我一個忙？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9616
translate zh_hant a3ec5o2_111a58e1:

    # hi "What's that?"
    hi "什麼事？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9621
translate zh_hant a3ec5o2_95c5efac:

    # emi "Show up for our morning run tomorrow?"
    emi "明天早上來，我們一起晨跑？"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9623
translate zh_hant a3ec5o2_3e3afdda:

    # "I smile, feeling better than I have all week."
    "我笑了，感覺比這一整個禮拜都還要好。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9625
translate zh_hant a3ec5o2_5b0f7a1c:

    # hi "Of course. I wouldn't miss it for the world."
    hi "當然。我絕對不會錯過的。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9630
translate zh_hant a3ec5o2_5b24fe88:

    # "Emi steps back slowly, almost reluctantly. She sniffles a little and then grins at me, a real smile that lights up the track, overpowering the fading evening's light."
    "笑美緩緩地，幾乎是不情願地掙脫了我的懷抱。抽了抽鼻子，對我笑了起來。那副真摯的笑容，彷彿取代了傍晚西沉的陽光，照亮了身後的整個校園。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9635
translate zh_hant a3ec5o2_d91f8844:

    # emi "See you tomorrow, Hisao."
    emi "明天見，久夫。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9637
translate zh_hant a3ec5o2_16a7dec2:

    # hi "Okay."
    hi "好。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9645
translate zh_hant a3ec5o2_699c76bd:

    # "She darts forward suddenly, planting a soft kiss on my lips, then steps back shyly."
    "她突然猛地前衝，在我的嘴脣上留下來一個溫柔的吻，而後又羞澀地退了回去。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9654
translate zh_hant a3ec5o2_a8daa451:

    # "Spinning on her back foot, she takes off running again, and I know that our conversation's at an end."
    "她轉過身，再次邁開步伐跑了起來，我知道我們的對話結束了。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9656
translate zh_hant a3ec5o2_308fd039:

    # "My lips tingle with the warmth of that brief kiss and the memories of other, longer kisses."
    "嘴脣上還留著她那一吻的餘香，腦海裡卻飄浮著其他更長的吻的回憶。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9658
translate zh_hant a3ec5o2_adfe688b:

    # "I walk back to my room with a spring in my step."
    "我腳步輕快地走回房間。"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:9660
translate zh_hant a3ec5o2_fce2cb88:

    # "Tomorrow when my alarm goes off, I'll get up."
    "明天鬧鐘響的時候，我就會起床。"

